hadiths[770]{hadithnumber,text}:
391,"Hazrat Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : ehle-Najad mein se eik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya . uskey sar ke baal bikhrey huey they. uski aawaz ki gungunaahat suni ja rahi thi magar samajh mein na aata tha ke kya keh raha hai, yahan tak ke) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke) qarib aa gaya to wo Islam ke baarey mein poochh raha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' din aur raat mein paanch namazein hain.'' kehney laga : kya unke ilawa bhi mujh par kuch hai? aapney farmaya : '' nahin siwaey iske ke to nafl padhna chahey .'' raawi ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se Ramazan ke rozon ka zikr farmaya to usney kaha : kya mujh par uskey ilawa bhi hain? aapney farmaya : '' nahin siwaey iske ke to nafl rakhna chahey .'' raawi ne kaha : aur aapney usko sadqa ( Zakat (ka bhi bataya to usney kaha : kya mujh par uskey ilawa bhi hai? aapney farmaya : '' nahin, haan agar to nafl dena chahey .'' chunanche wo aadmi wapis hua aur keh raha tha : Allah ki qasam ! main us se ziyada karunga na kam. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kamiyab hua agar Sabit qadam raha.''"
392,"Janab abu-Sahal Naafe bin Malik bin abi Aamir ki sanad se yehi hadees marwi (bayan) hai. us mein hai ke aapney farmaya : ''kaamiyab hua, qasam uskey baap ki, agar sacha hua . aur jannat mein dakhil hua , qasam uskey baap ki agar sacha hua .''"
393,Janab Naafe bin Jubair bin Mut-im Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Jibrael Alehissalam ne Baitullah ke paas meri do baar imaamat karaai .) pehli baar ( mujhey Zohar ki Namaz padhaai us waqt jabkey Suraj dhal gaya aur saya tasmey ke barabar tha aur Asr ki Namaz padhaai jab uska saya uskey barabar ho gaya aur maghrib ki Namaz padhaai jis waqt ke roza daar roza kholta hai aur Isha ki Namaz padhaai jabke shafaq ( surkhi ( ufuq mein ghayeb ho gaee aur Fajr ki Namaz padhaai jabkey rozey daar par khana peena haram ho jata hai. jab doosra din hua to mujhey Zohar ki Namaz padhaai jabkey uska saya uskey misl tha aur Asr ki Namaz padhaai jabkey uska saya do misl tha aur maghrib ki Namaz padhaai jabkey rozey daar roza kholta hai aur Isha ki Namaz padhaai jabkey raat ka tihai hissey guzar gaya aur mujhey Fajr ki Namaz padhaai aur khoob safedi ki . phir ( Jibrael Alehissalam ( meri taraf mutawajjeh huey aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! aap se pehley anbiya ke yehi oqaat hain. aur) Namaz ke) oqaat un dono ( waqton (ke beech hain.''
394,"Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez member par bethey huey they aur namaze-Asr mein unhoney kuch takheer kar di to Urwa bin Zuber ne un se kaha : yaad rahey ke Jibrael Alehissalam ne Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko namazon ke oqaat ki khabar di hai. to umr (bin Abdul-Azeez ( ne un se kaha : apni baat par zara ghor keejiye ! to Urwa ne kaha ke maine Bashir bin abi Masood se suna hai, wo keh rahey they maine abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : '' Jibrael Alehissalam tashrif laye aur mujhey Namaz ke oqaat ki ittilaa di aur maine aap ke sath Namaz padhi , phir padhi , phir padhi , phir padhi , phir padhi . aap ye bayan kartey huey apni ungliyon par paanch namazon ko shumar bhi kar rahey they. to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap namaze-Zohar padhtey they jabkey Suraj dhal jata tha aur sakht garmi ke waqt kabhi muakhkhar bhi kar letey they. aur maine aap ko dekha ke aap Asr ki Namaz padhtey they jabkey Suraj ooncha aur safed hota tha, zardi aaney se pehley pehley . aadmi Namaz padh ke nikalta aur ghuroob se pehley pehley zal-Hulaifa maqam tak pahunch jata tha. aur maghrib ki Namaz padhtey jis waqt ke Suraj ghuroob ho jata aur Isha padhtey jabkey ufuq maghrib siyah ho jata aur kabhi muakhkhar bhi kar detey yahan tak ke log jama ho jatey aur Fajr ki Namaz aapney eik baar andherey mein padhi aur eik dafa padhi to roshan kar di magar uskey baad aap ki Namaz andherey hi mein hua karti thi yahan tak ke aap ki wafat ho gaee aur kabhi roshan na ki . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko Zohri se Maamer , Malik , ibne-Uena , Shuaib bin abi Hamza aur Leis bin Saad waghera ne riwayat kya hai magar us mein wo waqt zikr nahin kya jis mein ke aapney Namaz padhi aur na un logon ne is tarah tafsil bayan ki hai. aur aisey hi Hisham bin Urwa aur Habib bin abi Marzooq ne Urwa se Maamer aur uskey sathiyon ki manind riwayat kya hai magar Habib ne Bashir ka wastey zikr nahin kya. aur Wahab bin kaisaan ne Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se maghrib ka waqt riwayat kya hai. kaha ke phir doosrey din ( Jibrael ( maghrib ke liye aaye jabkey Suraj ghuroob ho gaya. eik hi waqt mein (yani pehley aur doosrey din ka waqt eik hi tha ( . Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se aisey hi riwayat kya hai yani : '' phir mujhey agley din namaze-Maghrib padhaai . eik hi waqt mein .'' aur usi tarah Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se b-sanad Hassaan bin Ateeya marwi (bayan) hai."
395,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik saail ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ( oqaate-namaz ke baarey mein) sawal kya, magar aapney usey koi jawab na diya yahan tak ke Bilal ko hukm diya to unhoney Fajr ki) Azan w ( iqaamat kahi jis waqt Fajr tulu hui . pas aapney Namaz padhaai jabkey aadmi ( andherey ke baais ( apney sathi ka chehra na pehchan sakta tha ya ye ke aadmi ye na pehchan sakta tha ke uskey pehlu mein kon hai, phir Bilal ko hukm diya to unhoney Zohar ki) Azan w ( iqaamat kahi us waqt jab Suraj dhal gaya yahan tak ke kehney wala kehta ke kya do-pehar ho gaee hai? aur aap waqt ko khoob janney waley they (yani Suraj dhalney hi par Namaz padhi , magar logon ko shubha ho sakta tha ( , phir Bilal ko hukm diya to unhoney Asr ke liye ( Azan w ( iqaamat kahi jabkey Suraj safed aur ooncha tha, phir Bilal ko hukm diya to unhoney maghrib ke liye ( Azan w ( iqaamat kahi jabkey Suraj doob gaya , phir Bilal ko hukm diya to unhoney Isha ke liye ( Azan w ( iqaamat kahi jabkey shafaq ( surkhi ( ghayeb ho gaee . aur jab agla din hua to aapney Fajr ki Namaz padhi aur tashrif ley gaey aur ham keh rahey they ke kya Suraj nikal aaya hai? phir Asr ke waqt mein Zohar ki iqaamat kahi (yani kal guzishta ke waqt mein) aur Asr padhi jabkey Suraj zard ho gaya tha ya kaha ke jab shaam ho gaee aur maghrib padhi us se pehley ke shafaq ( surkhi) ghayeb ho aur Isha padhi tihai raat ke qarib phir farmaya : ''kahan hai Namaz ke oqaat poochhney wala? (namaz ka ( waqt un do oqaat ke beech hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Suleman bin Musa ne Ata se unhoney Jabir se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se maghrib ke baarey mein usi ke manind bayan kya. kaha : phir Namaz Isha padhi, baaz ne kaha : tihai raat ke waqt aur baaz ne kaha : aadhi raat ke waqt. aur ibn Barida ne apney walid sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se aisey hi riwayat kya."
396,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''zohar ka waqt us waqt tak hai jab tak ke Asr shuru na ho aur Asr ka waqt us waqt tak hai jab tak ke Suraj zard na ho aur maghrib ka waqt us waqt tak hai jab tak ke shafaq ki shadeed surkhi ghayeb na ho aur Isha ka waqt aadhi raat tak hai aur Fajr ki Namaz ka waqt jab tak ke Suraj na nikley.''"
397,Janab Muhammad bin Amr (bin Hasan bin Ali bin abi Talib) kehtey hain ke ham ne Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki namazon ke oqaat puchey to unhoney kaha ke aap Zohar ki Namaz sakht garmi ke waqt mein padha kartey they (yani zawal ke baad awwal waqt mein padhtey they (aur Asr us waqt ada kartey they jabke Suraj zinda hota (yani us mein chamak aur tapish baqi hoti.) aur maghrib us waqt padhtey jab Suraj ghuroob ho jata aur Isha mein jab log pehley jama ho jatey to jaldi kartey aur jab kam hotey to takheer kar letey aur Fajr ki Namaz andherey mein padha kartey they.
398,Hazrat abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zohar ki Namaz padhtey they jab Suraj dhal jata tha aur Asr ki Namaz us waqt padhtey they ke ham mein se eik shakhs Madina se bahir ki abadi mein ja kar wapis aa jata aur Suraj abhi zinda hota (yani saaf aur numaya hota ( ) Abul-Minhaal ne kaha (aur maghrib ka waqt main bhool gaya hun aur Isha ki Namaz mein aap tihai raat tak takheer ki parwa na kartey they.... phir kaha .... aadhi raat tak. aur kaha ke aap Isha se pehley so janey aur uskey baad baaten kerney ko napasand farmatey they aur Fajr ki Namaz padhtey to ham mein se eik apney ham nasheen ko jisey wo janta hota pehchan sakta tha. aur aap us mein 60 se 100 aayaat tak qirat farmatey they.
399,Saeed bin Haris Ansari Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se raawi hain wo kehtey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Zohar ki Namaz padha karta tha to apni mutthi mein kankariyaan utha leta taake thandi ho jaeyn aur unhen apni peshani ke nichey rakh kar sajda kar sakoon aur ye sakht garmi ki wajah se hota tha.
400,Janab Aswad se riwayat hai unka bayan hai ke Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz andazan garmiyon mein teen qadam se paanch qadam ( saya ( tak aur sardiyon mein paanch se saat qadam tak hoti thi.
401,Janab Zaid bin Wahab kehtey they maine Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo kehtey they ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they ke muazzan ne Zohar ki Azan kehna chahi to aapney farmaya : '' thandak honey do .'' usney phir Azan kehna chahi to aapney farmaya : '' thandak honey do .'' do dafa ya teen dafa yehi hua yahan tak ke ham ne tilon ke saye dekh liye . phir farmaya : '' garmi ki shiddat jahannam ki lapat se hai. jab garmi shadeed ho to Namaz ko thandey waqt mein padho.''
402,Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab aur abu-Salma Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab garmi shadeed ho to Namaz thandey waqt mein padha karo. ibn mohab (yani Yazid bin Khalid) ke alfaz ( an (an) الصلاة ( ki bajaey ( بالصلاة ( they. yaqinan garmi ki shiddat jahannam ki lapat se hai.
403,Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Suraj dhal jata tha to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Zohar ki Azan kehtey they.''
404,"ibne-Shahab Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se raawi hain, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Asr ki Namaz padha kartey jabkey Suraj safed , ooncha aur zinda hota tha. aur janey wala balaey Madina ( ki abadi ( ki taraf jata aur Suraj ooncha hota tha."
405,Zohri (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke balaey Madina ki aabaadiyaan do ya teen meel tak hoti thin. aur kaha mera khayal hai ke ye bhi kaha ke ya chaar meel tak hoti thin.
406,Janab khaseema (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ''sooraj zinda honey'' ka mafhoom ye hai ke aap uski garmi w haraarat mehsoos karen.
407,Janab Urwa ne kaha mujh se Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Asr ki Namaz padhtey to dhoop unke hujrey mein hoti aur deewar par na chadhi hoti thi.
408,"Janab Yazid bin Abdur-Rehman bin Ali bin Sheban apney baap se wo uskey dada Ali bin Sheban (Raziallahu anhu) se raawi hain, wo kehtey hain ke ham Madina mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye to ( dekha ke) aap Asr ko muakhkhar kartey they jab tak ke Suraj safed aur saaf hota."
409,"Janab Muhammad bin Sirin se riwayat hai, wo Ubeda se aur wo Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khandaq waley din kaha : ''un logon ne hamen darmiyani (ya afzal) namaz, namaze-asr, se rokey rakha, Allah unke gharon aur qabron ko aag se bhar dey.''"
410,"Janab abu-Yunus Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke azad karda ghulam bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne hukm diya ke unhen Quran majeed likh dun aur farmaya ke jab tum aayat kareema : ( حَافِظُوا عَلَى الصَّلَوَاتِ وَالصَّلَاةِ الْوُسْطَى ( par pahuncho to mujhey batlaana. chunanche jab main us aayat kareema par pahuncha to unhen khabar di. to unhoney mujhey ye aayat is tarah likhwaai: ( حَافِظُوا عَلَى الصَّلَوَاتِ وَالصَّلَاةِ الْوُسْطَى . . . . وَصَلَاةِ الْعَصْرِ . . . . . وَقُومُوا لِلَّهِ قَانِتِينَ ( '' namazon ki pabandi karo aur darmiyani Namaz (ya afzal) namaze-asr ki, aur Allah ke liye baa-adab ho kar khadey ho'o.'' phir unhoney kaha ke maine ye (aayat un alfaz ke sath) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni hai."
411,"Janab Urwa bin Zuber se riwayat hai, wo Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zohar ki Namaz do-pehar ke waqt mein padha kartey they aur as-haabe-Rasul ke liye us Namaz se badh kar aur koi Namaz sakht na hoti thi. chunanche ye aayat nazil hui : ( حَافِظُوا عَلَى الصَّلَوَاتِ وَالصَّلَاةِ الْوُسْطَى ( '' namazon ki pabandi karo aur darmiyani Namaz ki.'' ( Zaid bin Sabit ne ( kaha : is se pehley do namazein hain (yani Isha aur Fajr, raat ki) aur uskey baad bhi do namazein hain (yani Asr aur maghrib, din ki) ."
412,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney Suraj ghuroob honey se pehley Asr ki eik rakat pa li, usney Namaz pa li, aur jisney Suraj tulu honey se pehley Fajr ki eik rakat pa li, usney Namaz pa li.''"
413,"Janab Ala bin Abdur-Rehman bayan kartey hain ke ham namaze-Zohar ke baad Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey, to wo uth kar namaze-Asr padhney lag gaey . jab wo Namaz se farigh huey to ham ne un se unke namaze-Asr jaldi padhney ka zikr kya ya khud unhoney zikr kya to kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna hai, farmatey they.'' ye munafiqon ki Namaz hai, ye munafiqon ki Namaz hai, ye munafiqon ki Namaz hai ke un mein se eik betha rehta hai yahan tak ke jab Suraj zard ho jata hai aur shetan ke do seengon ke darmiyan ya un seengon ke ooper hota hai, to uth kar chaar thongein maarta hai aur Allah ka zikr us mein bas baraaye naam hi karta hai.''"
414,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jiski namaze-Asr faut ho jaey, to goya us se uskey ghar waley aur maal chheen liya gaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Ubaidullah bin umr ne hadees ke lafz ( witr ( ko (atr) bayan kya aur Ayub ke shagirdon mein (is lafz ke baarey mein) ikhtilaf hai (maani dono ka eik hi hai.) aur Zohri ne سالم an Abeeh an Nabi صلى الله عليه وسلم se ( witr ( bayan kya hai."
415,abu-Amr yani Auzaai ne bayan kya ke namaze-Asr faut honey se murad itni takheer hai ke zameen par padi chizen dhoop ke baais zard nazar aaney lagen .
416,Janab Sabit Bunani ne Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya wo bayan kartey hain ke ham maghrib ki Namaz Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath padhtey they phir teer phainktey to ham mein se eik uskey girney ki jagah ko dekh raha hota tha.
417,Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Suraj ghuroob hotey hi Namaz padh liya kartey they yani jab uski tikiya ghayeb ho jati thi.
418,"Janab Yazid bin abi Habib , Marsad bin Abdullah se riwayat kartey huey kehtey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey yahan tashrif laye . wo jihad ke safar mein they aur Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) un dino Misr ke haakim they. to ( Janab Aqba ne ( namaze-Maghrib mein kuch takheer kar di. Hazrat Abu-Ayub khadey huey aur kaha : aey Aqba ! ye kya Namaz hai? kaha ke ham kaam mein they. kaha : kya aapney nahin suna, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''meri ummat us waqt tak khair mein rahegi .'' ya farmaya : '' fitrat par rahegi jab tak ke maghrib ko muakhkhar na karegi ke sitarey nikal ayen .''"
419,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main sab logon se badh kar us Namaz yani Isha ke waqt se ba-khabar hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey teesri raat ka chaand doobney ke waqt padha kartey they."
420,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke eik raat ham Namaz Isha ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka intizar kartey rahey . aap us waqt tashrif laye jab raat ka tihai hissey guzar chuka tha ya us se bhi ziyada . na maloom aap kisi kaam mein mashghool ho gaey they ya koi aur baat thi. aap jab tashrif laye to farmaya : ''kya tum us Namaz ka intizar kar rahey ho? agar meri ummat par giraan na hota to main unko ye Namaz usi waqt padhata .'' phir aapney muazzan ko hukm diya to usney iqaamat kahi ."
421,"Janab Aasim bin Humaid Sakuni se riwayat hai, unhoney Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo bayan kartey they ke) eik baar ( ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka Namaz Isha ke liye intizar kartey rahey magar aapney takheer kar di yahan tak ke baaz ne ye bhi guman kya ke shayad aap nahin aaeyngey aur kuch kehney lagey ke aapney Namaz padh li hai. beharhal ham usi haalat mein they ke aap tashrif ley aaye to as-haab kiram (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ne aap se wohi kuch kaha jo pehley keh rahey they. aapney farmaya : ''is Namaz ko khoob andherey mein padho, bila-shuba tumhen tamam ummaton par uskey zariey se fazilat di gaee hai aur tum se pehley kisi ummat ne ye Namaz nahin padhi hai.''"
422,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke) eik baar ( ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Isha ki Namaz padhna chahi magar (us roz) aap tashrif na laye yahan tak ke taqreeban aadhi raat guzar gaee .) aakhir jab aap aaye ( to farmaya : '' apni apni jagahon par bethey raho .'' to ham apni apni jagahon par bethey rahey . aapney farmaya : '' logon ne Namaz padh li aur apney apney bistaron mein ja soey hain lekin tum jis waqt se intizar kar rahey ho Namaz hi mein ho. agar kamzoron ki kamzori aur bimaron ki bimari ka khayal na hota to main is Namaz ko aadhi raat tak muakhkhar karta.''
423,"ummul-momenin Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, wo bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki Namaz padhtey (aur uskey baad) aurten apni chaadaron mein lipti laut'tin to andherey ke baais pehchani na jati thin."
424,"Janab Mehmood bin Labid , Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) se raawi hain, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' subh tulu honey par) hi ( subh ki Namaz padha karo . bila-shuba ye tumharey liye bahut ziyada sawab ka baais hai.''"
425,"Janab Abdullah bin Sunabihi se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke abu-Muhammad ( Ansari sahabi (ka khayal hai ke witr wajib hai. Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( suna to ( kaha : abu-Muhammad ne ghalat kaha hai. main gawahi deta hun ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai aap farmatey they : '' paanch namazein Allah ne farz ki hain, jo unka wuzu umda banaey aur unhen unke oqaat par ada karey, unke rukoo aur khushu kamil rakhey , to aisey shakhs ke liye Allah ka wada hai ke wo usey bakhsh dega . aur jo ye na karey to uskey liye Allah ka koi wada nahin hai agar chahey to maaf kar dey aur agar chahey to azab dey .''"
426,"Qasim bin Ghannaam apni eik maa se bayan kartey hain, wo Hazrat umme-Farwa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat karti hain wo kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya gaya , aamaal mein se kon sa amal afzal hai? aapney farmaya : '' Namaz , awwal waqt mein ada karna.'' Khuzaae ne apni riwayat mein kaha (ke Qasim bin Ghannaam ne ( apni phuphi se riwayat kya jis ka naam umme-Farwa tha aur usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se baiat ki thi. ( farmati hain ke) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya gaya. ( ye Khuzaae ki riwayat hai jabke Abdullah bin Muslima ne '' ( baaz أمهاته ( '' ka lafz riwayat kya hai) ."
427,"Janab abu-Bakar bin Umara bin Rubiya apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke ehle-Basra ke kisi shakhs ne un se kaha ke aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se jo kuch suna hai us mein se kuch mujhey bhi bayan farmaiye . to unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farmatey they : '' dozakh mein nahin jaeyga wo aadmi jisney Suraj tulu honey aur uskey ghuroob honey se pehley ki namazein padhein .'' kaha kya ye aapney un se khud suna hai? teen baar kaha . jawab diya ke haan ! aur her baar kehtey ke maine usey apney kanon se suna hai aur merey dil ne usey yaad rakha hai. to us aadmi ne kaha : maine bhi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko yehi farmatey huey suna hai."
428,Janab Abdullah bin Fazaala apney walid se raawi hain wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey sikhaya aur jo sikhaya un mein ye baat bhi thi : '' paanch namazon ki pabandi karna.'' maine arz kya ke mujhey un oqaat mein kaam hotey hain to aap mujhey koi Jaame baat irshad farmaeyn jis par amal merey liye kafi rahey . aapney farmaya : '' ( asrain ( ki pabandi karna.'' aur ye lafz hamari zaban mein istemal nahi hota tha. maine kaha ke '' ( asrain ( '' se kya murad hai? aapney farmaya : '' Suraj ke tulu aur ghuroob honey se pehley ki namazein .''
429,"Janab Khaleed Asri Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se raawi hain, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' paanch chizen hain jisney un par emaan ke sath amal kya wo jannat mein dakhil hua , jisney paanch namazon ki unke wuzu , rukoo , sujood aur oqaat samet hifazat aur pabandi ki, Ramazan ke rozey rakhey , Baitullah ka hajj kya, agar us tak pahunchney ki istataat ho, Zakat di khushi ke sath aur amanat ada ki .'' logon ne kaha : aey Abu-Darda '' ! amanat ki adaeygi'' se kya murad hai? kaha : ghusle-janabat ."
430,"Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab ne kaha ke Hazrat abu-Qatada bin Rabai (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah azz-w-jall ka irshad hai ke maine tumhari ummat par paanch namazein farz ki hain aur apney liye ye ehad kya hai ke jo shakhs is haal mein (merey paas) aaya ke unke oqaat ki muhafizat w pabandi karta raha, main usey jannat mein dakhil karunga aur jo unki muhafizat na karta raha uskey liye merey yahan koi ehad aur wada nahin hai.''"
431,"Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey abu-Zar ! us waqt tera kya haal hoga jab tujh par aisey hukkaam hongey jo namazon ko maar dalengey .'' ya ye farmaya : . . . . .'' un mein takheer karengey .'' maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap mujhey kya hukm farmatey hain? aapney farmaya : ''tum Namaz ko uskey waqt mein padh liya karna aur agar tum usey unke sath pao to unke sath bhi padh liya karna aur ye terey liye nafl hogi .''"
432,"Janab Amr bin Memun Awdi se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey yahan Yamen mein tashrif laye . wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se aamil bin kar aaye they. ( Amr ( kehtey hain ke namaze-Fajr mein , maine unki takbir suni . wo bhari aawaz waley they. unko mujh se mohabbat ho gaee to maine unhen martey dam tak nahin chhoda yahan tak ke Sham mein unhen ( apney haathon sey) dafn kya. unke baad maine logon mein sab se ziyada faqeeh aadmi par nazar dorrati to main Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aa gaya aur unke sath raha , yahan tak ke wo bhi faut ho gaey, to unhoney mujh se bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya tha : '' tumhara kya haal hoga jab tum par aisey hukkaam musallat hongey jo namazon ko be waqt karkey padhengey ?'' maine kaha : aap mujhey kya hukm farmatey hain, aey Allah ke Rasool ! agar mujhey un halaat ka samna ho? aapney farmaya : '' Namaz ko apney waqt par padh liya karna aur unke sath ki Namaz ko nafl samajhna .''"
433,"Saiyedna Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhoney bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey baad eik waqt aaeyga ke tum par aisey hukkaam musallat hongey jinhen unke deegar umur (batein) Namaz se mashghool rakhengey aur wo unhen be waqt karkey padhengey , lihaza tum Namaz ko bar-waqt ada karna.'' eik aadmi ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya main un ke sath mein Namaz padhun ? aapney farmaya : '' haan agar tum chaho .'' aur Sufiyan ke alfaz hain : agar main wo Namaz unke sath paun to unke sath mil kar padhun ? aapney farmaya : '' haan , agar tum chaho.''"
434,Hazrat Qabisa bin Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey baad tum par aisey hukkaam aaeyngey jo namazon mein takheer karengey . to aisi namazein tumharey liye baais ajr hongi jabke unke liye wabal hongi . pas tum unke sath mil kar padh liya karna jab tak ke wo qibla rukh ho kar namazein padhtey rahen.''
435,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ghazwa khaibar se wapis lot rahey they to eik raat , raat bhar chaltey rahey, yahan tak ke jab ham ko neend aaney lagi to aap aaram ke liye utar gaey aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : '' aaj raat hamara pehra dena .'' bayan kartey hain ke phir Bilal ki aankhen bhi un par ghalib aa gaeen (yani so gaey (aur wo apney oont se tek lagaey huey they, chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jaagey , na Bilal hi aur na koi aur sahabi . yahan tak ke jab unhen dhoop lagi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sab se pehley jaagney waley they aap ghabraey aur farmaya : ''aey Bilal ! '' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey bhi usi chiz ne pakad liya jisney aap ko pakda . merey maa baap aap par qurban ! phir ( Nabi Alehissalam aur Sahaba (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ( wahan se chal diye (aur kuch door ja kar utrey ( tab aapney wuzu kya aur Bilal ko hukm diya to unhoney Namaz ke liye iqaamat kahi aur aapney unhen Fajr ki Namaz padhaai . aap Namaz se farigh huey to farmaya : ''jo shakhs Namaz ko bhool jaey to jab yaad aaye usi waqt padh liya karey. beshak Allah taala ne farmaya hai ke) أَقِمِ الصَّلَاةَ لِلذِّكْرَى ( Namaz qaaim karo jab yaad aaye .'' Yunus kehtey hain ke ibne-Shahab usi tarah ( للذكرى ( (alif maqsoora ke sath ( padha kartey they. Ahmed ne b-waasta anbasaa , Yunus se ( للذكرى ( ) yaaye mutakallim ke sath ( riwayat kya hai. (yani meri yaad ke liye ya meri yaad aaney ke waqt .) Ahmed kehtey hain ke) matn hadees mein waarid lafz ( ) الكرى (ka maani '' ungh '' hai."
436,"Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se mazkura baala qissey mein bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us jagah se nikal chalo jahan tum par ghaflat taari hui hai.'' uskey baad aapney Bilal ko hukm diya to unhoney Azan aur phir iqaamat kahi aur Namaz padhi. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is riwayat ko malik, Sufiyan bin Uena , Auzaai aur abdur-Razzaaq ne Maamer aur ibne-Is-haq se naqal kya hai. magar kisi ne bhi Zohri ki is riwayat mein Azan ka zikr nahin kya. aur Maamer se Auzaai aur Aban Attaar ke siwa kisi ne bhi usko bayan nahin kya hai."
437,"Saiyedna abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney eik safar mein they to aap raah se eik taraf ko ho gaey to main bhi aap ke sath eik taraf ko ho gaya. aapney farmaya : '' zara dekho .'' to maine kaha : ye eik sawar ( aa raha ( hai. ye do hain aur wo teen hain yahan tak ke ham saat afrad ho gaey . tab aapney farmaya : '' hamari Namaz ka khayal karna.'' yani namaze-Fajr ka . lekin unke kaan band kar diye gaey (yani sotey reh gaey) pas unko Suraj ki kirnon hi ne jagaya. wo uthey aur kuch waqt chaley, phir utrey, wuzu kya aur Bilal ne Azan kahi. sab ne Fajr ki sunnatein padhein phir Fajr ki Namaz ada ki aur Sawar ho gaey. to log eik doosrey se kehney lagey ham ne apni Namaz mein bahut taqseer ki hai. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''so janey mein koi taqseer ( kotahi) nahin hai, taqseer ( kotahi ( tab hoti hai jab insan jaagta ho. lihaza jab tum mein se koi Namaz ( padhna ( bhool jaey to jab usey yaad aaye padh ley aur phir (aainda ke liye ( agley din usey bar-waqt hi ada karey.''"
438,"Janab Khalid bin Sameer raawi hain ke Madina se Abdullah bin Ribah Ansari (Rahimahullah) hamarey yahan tashrif laye aur ansaar unhen faqeeh gardaantey they. unhoney ham se bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke shehsawaar abu-Qatada Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne '' jaishul-umra '' rawana farmaya. aur ye qissa bayan kya. kaha ke hamen Suraj hi ne tulu ho kar jagaya . aur ham ghabra kar Namaz ke liye uthey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khayal sey, sanbhal kar.'' yahan tak ke jab Suraj ooncha aa gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo tum mein se sunnatein padhna chahta hai padh ley.'' to jo pehley padha karta tha usney padhein aur jo na padhta tha usney bhi padhin. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya ke Namaz ke liye Azan kahi jaey to Azan kahi gaee aur aap khadey huey aur hamen Namaz padhaai. jab farigh huey to farmaya : ''ham Allah ki hamd kartey hain ke ham duniya ke kisi kaam mein mashghool na they ke Namaz ham se reh gaee balke hamari roohen Allah ke haath mein thin to usney jab chaha unhen chhod diya, lihaza jo tum mein se kal ko sehat w salamti ke sath namaze-Fajr paaey uskey sath us Namaz ki qaza bhi dey.''"
439,"Janab ibne-abi Qatada ( apney walid ( Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se raawi hain, unhoney us khabar mein bayan kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne jab chaha tumhari roohen qabz kar lin aur jab chaha lota den, lihaza utho aur Namaz ke liye Azan kaho .'' chunanche wo uthey aur wuzu kya yahan tak ke jab Suraj buland ho gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huey aur logon ko Namaz padhaai ."
440,Janab Abdullah bin Ubai Qatada apney walid Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi ke ham-maani riwayat kartey hain kaha ke aapney wuzu farmaya jabke Suraj ooncha aa gaya phir unhen Namaz padhaai .
441,Janab Abdullah bin Ribah Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se raawi hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''neend mein qusur nahin. qusur jaagney ki haalat mein hota hai. ( wo is tarah (ke tum kisi Namaz ko us had tak muakhkhar kar do ke dusri Namaz ka waqt aa jaey.''
442,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Namaz ko bhool jaey to wo usey usi waqt ada karey jab yaad aa jaey. uskey ilawa uska koi kaffara nahin hai.''
443,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney eik safar mein they ke log subh ki Namaz ke waqt soey rahey aur Suraj ki garmi se jaagey . phir kuch chaley yahan tak ke Suraj buland ho gaya. phir aapney muazzan ko hukm diya to usney Azan kahi aur farzon se pehley do rakatein padhein . phir iqaamat hui aur namaze-Fajr padhaai ."
444,Janab Zabarqan ne apney chacha Hazrat Amr bin Umayya Zamri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey huey bayan kya ke ham eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they. aap subh ke waqt mein soey rahey yahan tak ke Suraj nikal aaya . jab aap jaagey to farmaya : '' us jagah se door ho chalo .'' phir Bilal ko hukm diya to unhoney Azan kahi. phir sab ne wuzu kya aur Fajr ki sunnatein padhin. phir Bilal ko hukm diya to unhoney iqaamat kahi aur) aapney ( unhen subh ki Namaz padhaai.
445,"Yazid bin Saleh ne Hazrat zi-Mukhbir Habshi (Raziallahu anhu) sey, aur ye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke khaadim they. us qissey mein bayan kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wuzu kya, aur mukhtasar wuzu ke us se mitti bhi achi tarah geeli na hui . phir Bilal ko hukm diya unhoney Azan kahi. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uthey aur sukoon se do rakatein padhin. phir Bilal se farmaya : ''iqaamat kaho.'' tab aapney Namaz padhaai aur aap jaldi mein na they. (Ibrahim ne apni sanad mein) kaha Hajjaj An-Yazeed ibne-Saleeh Haddasani Mukhbir. ye eik Habshi fard tha. . . . . . aur Ubaid ne sanad mein) raawi ka naam ( Yazid bin Saleh bayan kya hai."
446,Janab Yazid bin Saleeh ne Hazrat zi-Mukhbir yani Najashi ke bhatijey se us khabar mein bayan kya. kaha : to usney Azan kahi aur wo jaldi mein na they.
447,"Saiyedna Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Hudebiya ke dino mein ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath aaye to aapney farmaya : ''hamara pehra kon dega?'' Bilal ne kaha : main. chunanche baqi sab so rahey yahan tak ke Suraj nikal aaya . pas Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jaagey aur farmaya : ''usi tarah karo jis tarah ke (us se pehley) kya kartey they.'' chunanche ham ne usi tarah kya. aapney farmaya : ''jo so jaey ya bhool jaey, to aisey hi kya karey.''"
448,Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey ye hukm nahin diya gaya ke masaajid ko bahut ziyada pukhta taameer karun.'' Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha tum unhen zarur muzayyan karogey jaisey ke yahood w nasaara ne ( apney ibadat khaney ( muzayyan kiye.
449,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaaya : '' qiyamat us waqt tak nahin aaeygi jab tak ke log masaajid mein aapas mein fakhr nahin kerney lagengey .''
450,Janab Muhammad bin Abdullah bin ayaaz Hazrat Usman bin abi al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen hukm diya tha ke taaif ki masjid us jagah banai jaey jahan unke but hotey they.
451,Janab Naafe bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne unko khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein masjid nabawi kachchi einton aur khajoor ki shaakhon se bani hui thi aur uskey sutoon khajuron ki lakdi ke they. Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us mein kuch izafa na kiya jabkey Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne us mein izafa kiya magar usey wesay hi banaya jaisey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein kachchi inton aur khajoor ki shaakhon se banai gaee thi magar uskey sutoon badal diye aur lakdi ke lagaey. aur Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne us (taameer) ko badal diya aur bahut ziyada izafa kiya. aur uski diiwaarein aur sutoon munaqqash patharon aur chooney se banaey aur chhat saagwaan ki lakdi ki banai. Mujahid ke lafz hain : (وسقفه بالساج)  ''aur saagwaan se uski chhat banai . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya ke lafz hadees (القصة (ka maani (الجص) yani ''gach hai.''
452,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein masjid nabawi ke sutoon khajuron ke tanon ke they, jin par khajuron ki shaakhon se chhat dali gaee thi. phir jab ye boseedah ho gaeen to Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke daur mein tanon aur shaakhon ko badal diya gaya (aur uski sabiqa bana mein koi tabdeeli na ki gaee). ye phir boseedah ho gaeen to Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke daur mein unhoney usey pukhta inton se banwaya aur ye taa-haal us par qaaim hai. (yani ibne-Umar ne jab ye riwayat bayan ki to us waqt tak wohi taameer baqi thi ("
453,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina mein tashrif laye aur) pehley ( uski baalaai(oopri) janib qabeela banu-Amr-bin-Auf mein qiyam farmaya. unke yahan chaudah raaten ( do haftey ( muqeem rahey. phir aapney banu-najaar ko pegham bhijwaayaa to wo ( apni riwayaat ke mutabiq istaqbal ke liye tayyar ho kar) talwaarein apney galon mein hamaayel kiye (latkaye) huey aaye. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain goya ( wo manzar meri nazron ke samney hai) main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekh raha hun ke wo apni sawari par hain aur Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke peechey bethey hain aur banu-najaar ke muazzezeen aap ke ird-gird hain, yahan tak ke aapney Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ke ehatey mein nuzool farmaya. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jahan bhi Namaz ka waqt ho jata, padh liya kartey they. aap bakriyon ke baadey mein Namaz padhtey they, phir aapney masjid taameer kerney ka hukm diya aur banu-najaar ko bulwaya aur kaha : ''tum mujh se apney us baagh ka soda kar lo.''  unhoney kaha : qasam Allah ki ! ham uski qeemat sirf shan waley Allah hi se lengey. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha aur us mein wo kuch tha jo main tumhen bata raha hun yani mushrekin ki qabren , khandar aur khajuron ke darkht . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mushrekin ki qabron ke mutalliq hukm diya aur unhen ukhad diya gaya, khandar barabar kar diye gaey aur khajuren kaat di gaeen aur unke tanon ko qibla rukh qatar se rakh diya gaya. aur darwazey ke dono kinarey patharon se chuney gaey aur) Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) jo taameer mein shareek they ( pathar dhotey they aur mil kar ashaar padhtey they aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi unke sath they : ( اللَّهُمَّ لَا خَيْرَ إِلَّا خَيْرُ الْآخِرَهْ فَانْصُرِ الْأَنْصَارَ وَالْمُهَاجِرَهْ ) ''aey Allah ! khair to bas wohi hai jo aakhirat mein miley , isliye to ansaar aur muhajrin ki nusrat farma.''"
454,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke masjid nabawi ka ehata darasal bani-najaar ka baagh tha aur us mein kuch kheti , khajuren aur mushrekin ki qabren thin . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mujh se uski qeemat ley lo.'' to unhoney kaha ke ham uski qeemat nahin lengey . chunanche khajuren kaat di gaeen , kheti ko barabar kar diya gaya aur mushrekin ki qabron ko ukhad diya gaya. ... aur puri hadees bayan ki . (mazkura she'r mein) (فانصر ( ki jagah (فاغفر) ka lafz bayan kiya hai. yani ''bakhsh dey.''  Musa ( bin-Ismail ( kehtey hain ke Abdul-Waraas ne ham se uski manind bayan kiya aur Abdul-Waris (kharab)  ''khandar''  bayan kartey they ( na ke) خرث (aur kehtey they ke maine hi Hammad ko ye hadees bayan ki hai."
455,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya ke mehlon mein masjiden banai jaeyn aur unhen pakizah , saaf suthra aur mua'ttar (khusbudar) rakha jaey."
456,Janab Suleman-bin-Samura apney walid Hazrat Samra (bin-Jundub) (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Hazrat Samra ne apney beton ki taraf likha tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen taameerey-masaajid ka hukm diya kartey they ke mahalley mein unki taameer keren aur unki imarat umda banaein aur unhen pakizah rakhein.
457,"Hazrat Memuna (binte-Saad (Raziallahu anha)) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khaadima ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamein baitul-Maqdis ke mutalliq irshad farmaiye , aapney farmaya : '' wahan jao, to wahan Namaz padho . ... '' aur us zamaney mein ye ilaaqa daarul-harab tha. ... ( farmaya : ( ''agar wahan na ja sako aur Namaz na padh sako to wahan ke liye tel hi bhej do ke uskey chiraghon mein dala jaey.''"
458,Janab abul-Waleed kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se masjid mein kankariyon ke mutalliq puchha (ke bichhaai jaein ya nahin) to unhoney kaha ke hamen eik raat barish ho gaee aur zameen geeli ho gaee to har aadmi apney kapdey mein kankariyaan ley aata aur apney nichey bicha leta. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz se farigh huey to farmaya : '' kis qadr achcha kaam hai ye .''
459,Janab abu-Saaleh ka bayan hai ke kaha jata tha jab koi aadmi masjid se kankariyaan bahir nikalta hai to ye usey Allah ka wasta deti hain (ke hamein mat nikalo).
460,"Janab abu-Saaleh Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, abu-Badr (sanad ke eik raawi ( ne kaha, mera khayal hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marfoo bayan kiya hai ke aapney farmaya : ''jo aadmi kankariyon ko masjid se nikalta hai to wo usey Allah ka wasta deti hain.''"
461,"Saiyedna Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey meri ummat ke sawab (aur nekiyan ( dikhai gaeein, yahan tak ke eik tinkaa bhi jo koi masjid se nikalta hai. ( ye bhi nekiyon mein shamil tha (aur mujhey meri ummat ke gunah dikhaye gaey to maine dekha ke us se badh kar aur koi gunah nahin ke eik aadmi ko Quran majeed ki koi surat ya aayat yaad ho aur wo usey bhula dey.''"
462,Saiyedna ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar ham ye darwaza aurton ke liye chhod dein . . . . .'' (aur mard us se dakhil na hon to bahut behtar ho). Naafe kehtey hain ke (ye irshad sunney ke baad) ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) martey dam tak kabhi us darwazey se masjid mein nahin aaye. Abdul-Waris ke ilawa deegar raawiyon ne usey Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka qol bayan kiya hai aur ye ziyada sahih hai.
463,Janab Naafe ne kaha ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aur mazkura baala (ooper zikr ki gaee) hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya. . . . . . aur ye ( ziyadat yani Hazrat umr ka qol hona ( ziyada sahi hai.
464,Janab Naafe se riwayat hai wo bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) aurton waley darwazey se dakhil honey se mana kiya kartey they.
465,"Janab Abdul-Malik-bin-Saeed-bin-suwed , abu-Humed (Raziallahu anhu) se ya abu-Usaid Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se raawi hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi masjid mein dakhil ho to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par salam padhey phir kahe : ( اللَّهُمَّ ! افْتَحْ لِي أَبْوَابَ رَحْمَتِكَ ) ''aey Allah ! merey liye apni rehmat ke darwazey khol dey.'' aur jab bahir nikley to kahey : ( اللَّهُمَّ ! إِنِّي أَسْأَلُكَ مِنْ فَضْلِكَ ) ''aey Allah ! main tujh se terey fazal aur inayat ka sawal karta hun.''"
466,"Janab hewa-bin-Shureh kehtey hain ke main Aqba-bin-Muslim se mila aur un se kaha ke mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke aap Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki sanad se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aap jab masjid mein dakhil hotey to kaha kartey they : ( أَعُوذُ بِاللَّهِ الْعَظِيمِ وَبِوَجْهِهِ الْكَرِيمِ وَسُلْطَانِهِ الْقَدِيمِ مِنَ الشَّيْطَانِ الرَّجِيمِ ) ''main shetan mardud ke shar se Allah ki panah chahta hun jo intehai azmat wala hai, main uskey intehai mohtaram chehrey ki panah leta hun aur uskey sultan qadim ki panah leta hun.'' kaha bas itna hi? maine kaha : haan . ... kaha ke insan jab ye keh leta hai to iblees kehta hai ke aaj sarey din ke liye ye mujh se mehfooz ho gaya."
467,Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi masjid mein aaye to bethney se pehley do rakatein padhey .''
468,"Janab Aamir-bin-Abdullah-bin-Zubair, bani-zuraiq ke eik aadmi se, wo Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi ke manind riwayat kartey hain. us mein ye izafa hai : ''phir uskey baad betha rahey ya chahey to apney kaam ke liye chala jaey.''"
469,Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' farishtey tum mein se eik ke liye dua aur istighfar kartey rehtey hain jab tak ke wo us jagah par betha rahey jahan usney Namaz padhi ho jab tak ke be-wuzu na ho ya wahan se uth na jaey. (unki dua hoti hai : ) ( اللَّهُمَّ ! اغْفِرْ لَهُ اللَّهُمَّ ارْحَمْهُ ) ''aey Allah ! iski bakhshish farma . aey Allah ! is par rehem farma .''
470,Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tak bandey ko Namaz ( masjid mein) rokey rakhey wo ( goya ( Namaz mein hota hai) ba-sharte-ke ( usey apney ehle mein lotney se rokney wali sirf Namaz hi ho.''
471,Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' banda us waqt tak Namaz hi mein hota hai jab tak ke apney musalley par betha (dusri ( Namaz ka intizar kar raha ho. farishtey kehtey hain : aey Allah ! isko bakhsh dey . aey Allah ! is par rehem farma . yahan tak ke wo uth jaey ya be-wuzu ho jaey.'' kaha gaya : be-wuzu kaisey ho? kaha : ''phuski maarey ya gooz (paad) maarey.''
472,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs jis niyat se masjid mein aaya ho, uska wahi naseeba hai.''"
473,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna aap farmatey they : ''jo kisi ko suney ke gumshuda chiz ka masjid mein aelan kar raha hai to usey kahey : Allah karey tujhey ye na miley . masjidein is kaam ke liye nahin banai gaeen.''
474,Saiyedna Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' masjid mein thooknaa ghalati hai aur iska kaffara ye hai ke usey chupa dey.''
475,Saiyedna Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' masjid mein thookna khata hai aur uska kaffara usey dafn kar dena hai.''
476,Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khankhaar masjid mein (dalna gunah hai).'' aur mazkura baala hadees ke manind bayan kiya.
477,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs us masjid mein dakhil ho aur us mein thook dey ya balgham giraaey to chahiye ke jagah khod kar usey dafn kar dey. agar aisey na karey to apney kapdey mein thookey aur phir usey bahir ley jaey.''
478,Hazrat taariq-bin-Abdullah mahaaribi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi Namaz ke liye khada ho. . . . . . ya farmaya. . . . . tum mein se koi Namaz padh raha ho to apney aagey ya daain janib hergiz na thookey. lekin baeyn janib agar khaali ho to thook sakta hai ya apney baeyn paon ke nichey thook ley aur phir usey masal daley.''
479,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba irshad farma rahey they ke aapney qibla rukh ki deewar par dekha ke us par balgham laga hua hai to aap logon par naraz huey. phir usey khurch dala. Hazrat Abdullah kehtey hain : mera khayal hai ke phir aapney Zaafran mangwaya aur us par lagaya aur farmaney lagey : ''jab tum Namaz padhtey ho to Allah taala tumharey samney hota hai, lihaza koi shakhs apney samney na thookey . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is hadees ko Ismael aur Abdul-Waris ne Ayub se unhoney Naafe se aur Malik , Ubaidullah aur Musa-bin-Aqba ( teeno ( ne Naafe se Hammad ki manind riwayat kiya hai magar unhoney '' Zaafran '' ka zikr nahin kiya. lekin usko Maamer ne Ayub se riwayat kiya to '' Zaafran '' ka zikr kiya hai. aur Yahya-bin-sulaim ne Ubaidullah se unhoney Naafe se riwayat kiya to usney (خلوق) yani ''khushbu'' ka zikr kiya."
480,"Janab ayaaz-bin-Abdullah Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khajoor ke khoshay ki shaakh pasand thi aur hamesha koi na koi shaakh aap ke daste-mubarak mein rehti thi. ( eik baar (aap masjid mein dakhil huey aur qible ki deewar par dekha ke us par balgham laga hai to aapney usey khurch dala aur phir logon ki taraf mutawajjeh huey. aap ghussay mein they. farmaya : ''kya tum mein se koi pasand karta hai ke uskey chehrey par thooka jaey? tum mein se jab koi shakhs qibla rukh hota hai to apney Shan wale rab ki taraf rukh karta hai aur farishta uski daain janib hota hai, lihaza koi apney daain janib ya qibla rukh na thookey. agar thookna hi ho to apni baeyn janib ya paon ke nichey thookey. agar jaldi ho to aisey kar ley.''  phir ibne-ajlaan ne karkey dikhlaaya ke apney kapdey mein thook ley aur usko aapas mein masal dey."
481,"Hazrat Abu-Sahla saaib-bin-khallaad se riwayat hai, Ahmed (bin-Saleh, Imam Abu-Dawud ke ustaad) kehtey hain ke wo (saaib) eik sahabi hain. un se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs ne apni qaum ki imaamat karaai aur usney qibley ki janib thook diya jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dekh rahey they. jab wo farigh hua to aapney (us ki qaum sey) farmaya : ''(aainda) ye tumhen Namaz na padhaaey.'' iskey baad usney unhen Namaz padhaana chahi to unhoney usko rok diya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka farman sunaya. to usney ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se zikr ki to aapney farmaya : ''haan.'' aur mera khayal hai ke aapney farmaya : ''tum ne Allah aur uskey Rasool ko eza (takleef) di hai.''"
482,"Janab mutrif apney walid (Hazrat Abdullah-bin-shikhkhir (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain, wo kehtey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabkey aap Namaz padh rahey they to aapney apney baeyn qadam ke nichey thooka."
483,Janab abul-Ala ne apney walid se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kiya aur izafa kiya ke phir usey apney jootey se masal diya.
484,"Janab abu-Saeed kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat wasla-bin-Asqaa' (Raziallahu anhu) ko dimashq ki masjid mein dekha ke unhoney chatai par thooka aur phir usey paon se masal diya, to unhen kaha gaya ke aapney aisey kyon kiya? unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah ko aisey hi kartey huey dekha tha."
485,"Janab Ubaada-bin-Waleed-bin-Ubada-bin-Saamit ne kaha ham Hazrat Jabir yani Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke yahan aaye aur wo apni masjid mein they. unhoney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamari is masjid mein tashrif laye aur aap ke haath mein ibne-taab khajoor ki shaakh thi. aapney dekha to aap ki nazar qibley ki deewar par lagey balgham par padi. aap uski taraf gaey aur shaakh se usey khurch dala, phir farmaya : ''tum mein se kon pasand karta hai ke Allah us se munh pher ley?''  phir farmaya : ''tum jab Namaz ke liye khadey hotey ho to Allah taala tumharey samney hota hai, to koi shakhs apney qibla rukh ya daain taraf hergiz na thookey balke apney baeyn janib ya bayen qadam ke nichey thookey. agar jaldi ho to apney kapdey mein aisey-aisay kar liya karey.'' aapney kapda apney munh par rakha phir usey masal diya, phir farmaya : '' khushbu lao'' to qabiley ka eik naujawan utha aur daurhta hua apney ghar gaya aur apni hatheli mein khushbu ley aaya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey shaakh ke sirey par laga kar balgham wali jagah par laga diya. Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : bas yahin se tum log apni masaajid mein khushbu lagatey ho."
486,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs aaya, wo oont par tha, usney oont ko masjid (ke ehatey) mein bithaya, phir usey baandha, phir kaha : tum mein sey,  ''Muhammad'' kaun hai? jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Sahaba ke darmiyan tek lagaey bethey they, ham ne kaha ke ye jo gora-chittaa shakhs tek lagaey huey hain  (yehi Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain) to us aadmi ne aap se kaha : aey ibne-abdul-Muttalib ! aapney usey farmaya : ''jawab dey raha hun.'' usney kaha : aey Muhammad ! main aap se poochhna chahta hun. . . . . . aur hadees bayan ki."
487,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke qabeela-banu Saad-bin-Bakr ne zamaam-bin-Saulba ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf bheja , to wo aap ke paas aaya. usney aa kar apna oont darwazey ke paas bithaya, phir usey baandha aur masjid ke andar aa gaya. aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind bayan kiya. usney kaha : tum mein se ibne-abdul-Muttalib kaun hai? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main ibne-bdul-Muttalib hun.'' usney kaha : aey ibne-abdul-Muttalib ! aur hadees bayan ki."
488,"qabeela muzena ke eik aadmi ne , jabke ham Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ke paas bethey huey they, hamein Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat bayan ki ke (kuch) yahudi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye jabke aap masjid mein apney as-haab ke sath tashrif farma they, unhoney aa kar kaha : aey abul-Qaasim ! aur unke eik mard aur eik aurat ne zina kiya tha, uskey baarey mein daryaft kiya."
489,Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' zameen merey liye paak kerney wali banai gaee hai aur sajdey ki jagah bhi.''
490,"Janab abu-Saaleh ghifaari bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) babil se guzar kar ja rahey they to muazzan unke paas aaya aur unhen namaze-Asr ki ittilaa di magar jab wo us se bahir nikal gaey to unhoney muazzan ko hukm diya aur usney Namaz ki iqaamat kahi , jab farigh huey to farmaney lagey : merey Habib Alehissalam ne mujhey qabristaan aur sar zameen babil mein Namaz padhney se mana farmaya hai kyonkey ye maloon hai."
491,abu-Saaleh ghifaari Hazrat Ali ke wastey se riwayat kartey hain. Suleman-bin-Dawud ki hadees ke ham-maani marwi (bayan) hai (jo ooper zikr hui hai) magar us mein (فلما برز) ki bajaey (فلما خرج) ke lafz bayan kiye hain. (maani dono ke eik hain.)
492,Hazrat abu-Saeed (Khudri) (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya. ... aur Musa (bin-Ismaaeel) ne apni riwayat mein kaha . ... Amr (bin-Yahya) ka khayal hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' zameen sari ki sari masjid hai siwaye Hammam aur maqbare ke.''
493,"Hazrat Bara-bi- Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se oonton ke baadon mein Namaz ke mutalliq puchha gaya to aapney farmaya : ''un mein Namaz na padha karo, bila-shuba ye shayateen mein se hain.'' aur bakriyon ke baadon ke mutalliq puchha gaya to farmaya : ''un mein Namaz padh liya karo, bila-shuba ye ba-barkat hoti hain.''"
494,Abdul Malik-bin-Rabeea-bin-sabra (Hazrat sabra-bin-ma'bad Juhni (Raziallahu anhu)) kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bachcha jab saat saal ka ho jaey to usey Namaz ka hukm do aur jab das saal ka ho jaey (aur na padhey) to usey maaro.''
495,Janab Amr-bin-shoaib apney walid (shoaib) se aur wo (shoaib) apney dada (Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu)) se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney bachchon ko jab wo saat saal ke ho jaeyn to Namaz ka hukm do aur jab das saal ke ho jaeyn (aur na padhein) to unhein is par maaro aur unke bistar juda-juda kar do.''
496,Dawud-bin-sawaar Muzni ne mazkura sanad se usi ke ham-maani bayan kiya aur us mein izafa kiya : '' aur jab tum mein se koi apni kisi londi ki apney ghulam se ya naukar se shaadi kar dey to (ab) uski naaf se ghutnon ke beech ki taraf na dekhay. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain Wakee ko shaikh ke naam mein weham hua hai (dar-haqeeqat sawaar-bin-Dawud hai) Abu-Dawud Tiyalisi ne ye hadees riwayat ki hai to uska naam abu-Hamza sawaar sairfi zikr kiya hai.
497,"Muaz-bin-Abdullah-bin-khubaib Juhni se marwi (bayan) hai (Hisham-bin-Saad ne kaha ke) ham Muaz-bin-Abdullah ke yahan gaey to unhoney apni ehliya se puchha ke bachcha Kab Namaz padhey? to usney bataya ke hamarey yahan eik sahab they, wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey they ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us baarey mein puchha gaya to aapney farmaya : ''jab wo daeyn-baeyn ka farq samajhney lagey to usey Namaz ka hukm do.''"
498,"Janab abu-Umair bin Anas apney eik Ansari chacha se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) fikrmand huey ke kis tarah logon ko Namaz ke liye ( bar-waqt ( jama kya jaey, to aap se kaha gaya ke Namaz ke waqt jhanda buland kar diya karen. log jab usey dekhengey to eik-doosrey ko khabar kar diya karengey magar aap ko ye raey pasand na aai. phir nr-singhey ka zikr kya gaya jaisey ke yahood ka hota hai. ye raey bhi aap ko pasand na aai aur farmaya : ''ye yahudiyon ka amal hai.'' phir aap se naaqoos ka zikr kya gaya to aapney farmaya : ''ye nasaara ka amal hai.'' chunanche Abdullah bin Zaid bin Abde-Rabba majlis se lotey to wo usi fikr mein pareshan they jis mein ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) they, to unhen khuwab mein Azan batai gaee. chunanche wo subh ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey aur aap ko khabar di aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main soney jaagney ki keyfiyat mein tha ke merey paas eik aaney wala aaya aur mujhey Azan bata gaya. (raawi ne kaha ke) Hazrat umr ibn Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi un se pehley ye Azan khuwab mein dekh chukey they magar bees din tak khamosh rahey. phir unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya to aapney farmaya : ''hamen khabar deney se tumhen kis chiz ne roka tha? ''to unhoney kaha ke Abdullah bin Zaid mujh se sabqat ley gaey they, isliye mujhey haya aai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Bilal! khadey ho jao, dekho jo Abdullah bin Zaid tumhen bataey wo karo.'' chunanche Bilal ne Azan di. abu-Bashar kehtey hain ke abu-Umair ne mujhey bataya ke Ansariyon ka khayal tha ke Abdullah bin Zaid agar un dino bimar na hotey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhi ko muazzan muqarrar kartey."
499,"Janab Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Zaid bin Abde-Rabba kehtey hain ke mujhey merey walid Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne naaqoos bananey ka hukm diya taake usey baja kar logon ko Namaz ke liye jama kya jaey to maine khuwab mein dekha ke merey paas se eik aadmi guzar raha hai, haath mein naaqoos liye huey hai. maine us se kaha : aey Allah ke banday! kya to naaqoos bechega? usney kaha : tum uska kya karogey? maine kaha : ham us se logon ko Namaz ke liye bulaeyngey. wo kehney laga : kya main tumhen wo chiz na bata dun jo is se ziyada behtar hai. maine kaha : kyon nahin. usney kaha : tum yun kaha karo : الله أكبر الله أكبر . الله أكبر الله أكبر . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . حى على الصلاة . حى على الصلاة . حى على الفلاح . حى على الفلاح . الله أكبر الله أكبر . لا إله إلا الله ''Allah sab se bada hai. Allah sab se bada hai. Allah sab se bada hai. Allah sab se bada hai. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud nahin. mein gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud nahin. mein gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad Allah ke Rasool hain. main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad Allah ke Rasool hain. aao Namaz ki taraf . aao Namaz ki taraf . aao kamiyabi ki taraf . aao kamiyabi ki taraf . Allah sab se bada hai. Allah sab se bada hai. Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud nahin .'' phir wo mujh se kuch peechey hat gaya aur kaha jab tum Namaz ke liye khadey ho to yun kaho : الله أكبر الله أكبر . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . حى على الصلاة . حى على الفلاح . قد قامت الصلاة . قد قامت الصلاة . الله أكبر الله أكبر . لا إله إلا اللهjab subh hui to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur jo kuch khuwab mein dekha tha aap ko batlaaya. to aapney farmaya : ''ye insha-Allah sacha khuwab hai. tum Bilal ke sath khadey ho jao aur usey wo kalmaat batatey jao jo tum ne dekhay hain. wo Azan kahega kyonkey wo tum se ziyada buland aawaz wala hai.'' chunanche main Bilal ke sath khada ho gaya aur unhen wo alfaz batata gaya aur wo Azan kehtey gaey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) apney ghar mein they, unhoney usey suna to (jaldi sey) chadar ghaseet'tey huey aaye, kehney lagey : qasam us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq de-kar bheja hai, aey Allah ke Rasool! maine bhi yehi khuwab dekha hai jaisey ke usey dikhaya gaya hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tareef Allah hi ke liye hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Zohri ki Saeed bin Musaiyab se aur unki Abdullah bin Zaid se riwayat aisey hi hai. us mein ibn Is-haq ne Zohri se yehi alfaz naqal kiye hain : ( الله أكبر الله أكبر , الله أكبر الله أكبر ( jabkey Maamer aur Yunus Zohri se ( sirf ( ) الله أكبر الله أكبر ( riwayat kya hai. unhoney dohra kar zikr nahin kya."
500,"Janab Muhammad bin Abdul-Malik bin abi Mahzura apney walid ( Abdul-Malik ( se wo unke (yani Muhammad ke) dada ( Hazrat Abu-Mahzura (Raziallahu anhu)) se raawi hain, ( Abu-Mahzura) kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey Azan ka tariqa sikha dijiye . chunanche aapney merey sar ke agley hissey par haath phera aur farmaya : '' yun kaha karo : ( الله أكبر الله أكبر . الله أكبر الله أكبر (us mein tumhari aawaz khoob buland honi chahiye , phir kaho : أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله in kalmaat mein tumhari aawaz qadrey past ho. phir oonchi aawaz se kalmaat shahadat (dobara) kaho : أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . حى على الصلاة . حى على الصلاة . حى على الفلاح . حى على الفلاح agar Fajr ki Namaz ho to kaho :  الصلاة خير من النوم . الصلاة خير من النوم '' Namaz neend se behtar hai. Namaz neend se behtar hai, ( الله أكبر . الله أكبر . لا إله إلا الله ) ."
501,"Janab Usman bin Saaib apney walid ( Saaib ( sey, wo aur Umme- Abdul-Malik bin abi Mahzura (yani zauja Abu-Mahzoora ( dono Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us khabar ki manind riwayat kartey hain. us mein hai ke (الصلاة خير من النوم ، الصلاة خير من النوم) pehli yani subh ki Azan mein hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Musaddad ki hadees ziyada wazeh hai. us mein hai ke aapney mujhey iqaamat sikhai uskey kalmaat do do baar they : الله أكبر الله أكبر . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . حى على الصلاة . حى على الصلاة . حى على الفلاح . حى على الفلاح . الله أكبر . الله أكبر . لا إله إلا الله Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke abdur-Razzaaq ne kaha : jab to Namaz ki iqaamat kahe to (قد قامت الصلاة . قد قامت الصلاة) do baar keh .) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Janab Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ( ''kya tum ne sun liya?'' (yani Azan w iqaamat ko samajh liya hai?) (Saaib ne) kaha ke Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) apney maathe ke baal kaata kartey they na mang nikala kartey they, usi sabab se ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un par haath phera tha."
502,Janab ibne-Mahireez se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen Azan ke Unais aur iqaamat ke sattarah kalmaat sikhaey they. Azan ke kalmaat ye they : الله أكبر . الله أكبر . الله أكبر . الله أكبر . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . حى على الصلاة . حى على الصلاة . حى على الفلاح . حى على الفلاح . الله أكبر . الله أكبر . لا إله إلا الله aur iqaamat ke kalmaat ye they :  الله أكبر . الله أكبر . الله أكبر . الله أكبر . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . حى على الصلاة . حى على الصلاة . حى على الفلاح . حى على الفلاح . قد قامت الصلاة . قد قامت الصلاة . الله أكبر . الله أكبر . لا إله إلا الله (Hammam bin Yahya ki) kitab mein aisey hi hai.
503,Janab ibne-Mahireez Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bazaat khud mujhey Azan sikhai aapney farmaya ke kaho :  الله أكبر . الله أكبر . الله أكبر . الله أكبر . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله do do baar ... aapney farmaya : ''unhen dobara kaho aur oonchi aawaz se kaho '' أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . حى على الصلاة . حى على الصلاة . حى على الفلاح . حى على الفلاح . الله أكبر . الله أكبر . لا إله إلا الله
504,Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey Azan ka eik eik harf sikhaya : الله أكبر . الله أكبر . الله أكبر . الله أكبر . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . حى على الصلاة . حى على الصلاة . حى على الفلاح . حى على الفلاح. bayan kya ke aur wo Fajr ki Azan mein (الصلاة خير من النوم ، الصلاة خير من النوم) kaha kartey they.
505,"Janab Abdullah bin Mahizeez Jamhi Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen Azan sikhai ke yun kahen :  الله أكبر الله أكبر . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله phir ibne-Juraij (an) Abdul-Azeez bin Abdul-Malik ki hadees mein marwi (bayan) Azan ki manind aur usi ke ham-maani bayan kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Malik bin Dinar ki hadees mein hai : maine ibne-abi Mahzura se kaha ke mujhey apney walid ki Azan sunao jo wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey they, to unhoney sunai aur sirf ( الله أكبر . الله أكبر ( kaha aur aisey hi Jaafar bin Suleman ki riwayat mein hai jo wo ibne-abi Mahzura se wo apney chacha se aur wo uskey dada se bayan kartey hain. magar us mein hai ke phir aapney farmaya : ''dobara dohraao aur apni aawaz oonchi karo) الله أكبر . الله أكبر .) ''"
506,"Janab ibne-abi Leila (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Namaz teen haalaton se guzri hai. hamarey as-haab ne ham se bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey ye baat pasand hai ke musalmanon .'' ya farmaya : '' mominon ki Namaz eik ho (yani jamaat se ada keren ( yahan tak ke mera dil chaha ke kuch logon ko mehlon mein bhejun jo wahan ja kar aelan keren ke Namaz ka waqt ho gaya hai. maine yahan tak chaha ke wo unchey makaanon ya qilon ke ooper khadey ho kar musalmanon mein aelan keren ke Namaz ka waqt ho gaya hai. yahan tak ke unhoney naaqoos bajaey ya naaqoos bajaney ka irada kya. '' us ( ibne-abi Leila ( ne bayan kya ke eik Ansari aaye ( Abdullah bin Zaid bin abde-Rabba) aur kehney lagey : aey Allah ke Rasool ! jab main (aap ke yahan sey) wapis gaya tha to mujhey aap ki fikr-mandi ka khayal tha. chunanche maine ( khuwab mein) dekha ke eik aadmi hai jis par sabz (hara) rang ke do kapdey hain. wo masjid ke paas khada hua aur Azan kahi . phir thodi der ke liye beth gaya aur phir khada hua aur usi tarah kaha aur) قد قامت الصلاة (ka izafa kya. agar mujhey logon ki che-me-goiyon ka khayal na hota . ... ibne-Musanna ne kaha . ... agar mujhey tum logon ki che-me-goiyon ka khayal na hota to main kehta ke main jaag raha tha, soyaa hua na tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ibn Musanna ke lafz hain : '' tehqiq Allah ne tumhen khair dikhlaai hai.'' Amr ne ye lafz bayan nahin kiye (yani لقد أراك الله خيرا .) '' Bilal ko batlao ke wo Azan kahe '' . ... ibne-abi Leila raawi hain ke . . . . .) baad mein) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine bhi yehi kuch dekha hai jaisey ke usney dekha hai. lekin chunke ye sabqat ley gaya hai, lihaza mujhey haya aai . (doosri haalat) us (ibne-abi Leila) ne kaha : ham se hamarey as-haab ne bayan kya ke .... jab koi aadmi aata (aur jamaat ho rahi hoti ( to ( wo apney sathi sey) poochh liya karta tha aur usey bata diya jata tha ke kitni Namaz guzar chuki hai. aur) baad mein aaney waley aksar log jamaat mein shamil ho kar pehley faut shuda rakatein ada kartey aur phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath baqiya Namaz ada kartey, chunanche aap ke sath) khadey hotey huey koi qiyam mein hota, koi rukoo mein aur koi juloos mein aur koi (shuroo hi mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz mein mil jata. ibn Musanna ne kaha Amr ne kaha ke mujh se Husain ne ibne-abi Leila se bayan kya ke . yahan tak ke Muaz aaye .... Shoba ne kaha ke maine ye riwayat Husain se suni, us mein hai ke . . . . .) Muaz ne ( kaha . . . . . main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jis haal mein paaunga (wohi karunga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya :) ''tum bhi wesay hi kya karo. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke phir maine Amr bin marzooq ki hadees ki taraf maraajiat ki. (us mein hai ke) Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) aaye to logon ne unki taraf ( padhi gaee Namaz ke mutalliq ( ishara kya. Shoba ne kaha : ye jumla maine Husain se suna hai ke . . . . . us ( ibne-abi Leila ( ne kaha ke Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke main to aap Alehissalam ko) Namaz ki) jis haalat mein paaunga, wohi karunga (yani saf mein mil kar pehley faut shuda rakatein ada nahin karunga balke unko salam phirney ke baad ada karunga.) chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Muaz ne tumharey liye eik umda tariqa ikhtiyar kya hai to tum bhi aisey hi kya karo.'' (yani Imam ke sath is haal mein mil jaya karo, jis mein usey pao . teesri haalat tahweele-qibla ki hai jis ka zikr us riwayat ki bajaey agli riwayat mein hai. ab uskey baad rozon ki teen haalaton ka bayan hai. ibne-abi Leila ne kaha ke hamarey as-haab ne ham se bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Madiney mein aaye to ehle-Madina ko) her maah ( teen rozey rakhney ka hukm diya. phir Ramazan ka hukm nazil hua . log rozon ke aadi na they aur ye amal unke liye had se zyada mushkil tha, to jo roza na rakhta eik miskeen ko khana khila deta tha ( ye pehli haalat thi. ( yahan tak ke ye aayat kareema nazil hui : ( { فَمَنْ شَهِدَ مِنْكُمُ الشَّهْرَ فَلْيَصُمْهُ } ( ''tum mein se jo koi us mahiney ko paey to bil-zaroor uskey rozey rakhey .''is tarah rukhsat sirf mareez aur musafir ke liye reh gaee aur (doosron ko) rozey rakhney ka hukm diya gaya. ( ye rozey ki dusri haalat bayan hui . aagey teesri haalat ka bayan hai. ( ibne-abi Leila ne ( kaha ke hamarey as-haab ne ham se bayan kya ke) ibtida (shuruat) mein) jab aadmi iftaar kar leta tha aur khana khaney se pehley so jata to phir subh tak kuch na kha sakta tha. bayan kya ke) phir aisey hua ke) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ghar ( aaye aur apni ehliya ( se sohbat (ka qasad kya. usney jawab diya ke main eik martaba so chuki hun. magar unhoney samjha ke shayad bahana bana rahi hai lihaza wo uskey paas aaye . (yani us se ham-bistari ki . usi tarah ( eik doosra Ansari ( ghar ( aaya aur khana talab kya. unhoney kaha ke (zara intizar keren ( ham aap ke liye kuch garm kar detey hain, magar is beech mein wo khud so gaya , to jab subh hui to ye aayat utri : ( { أُحِلَّ لَكُمْ لَيْلَةَ الصِّيَامِ الرَّفَثُ إِلَى نِسَائِكُمْ } ( '' tumharey liye ( Ramazanul-mubarak mein) rozey ki raat main apni aurton ( biwiyon (ke sath ham-bistari (aur sohbat ( karna halal kar diya gaya hai.'' (aur aagey chal kar usi aayat mein sari raat tulu Fajr tak , khaney peeney ki ijazat de-di gaee .)"
507,"ibne-abi-Leila Hazrat Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain ke Namaz aur rozey ke ahwaal (halaat) mein teen-teen tabeedilyan aai hain. nasar ne tafsil se hadees bayan ki . aur ibne-Musanna ne us mein se sirf Namaz ke mutalliq bayan kiya ke log pehley baitul-Maqdis ki taraf munh karkey Namaz padhtey they (us) teesrey haal ki tafsil is tarah bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madiney mein aaye aur tehra (13) mahiney tak baitul-Maqdis ki taraf munh karkey Namaz padhtey rahey, tab Allah taala ne aayat kareema : « { قَدْ نَرَى تَقَلُّبَ وَجْهِكَ . . . . . . } » ''beshak ham aap ka aasman ki taraf baar-baar chehra uthana dekhtey hain to ham bil-zaroor aap ka rukh aap ke pasandida qibley ki taraf kar dengey , to aap apna munh masjid haram ki janib kar lijiye aur tum log jahan kahin bhi ho apna rukh usi ki taraf kiya karo.'' nazil farmaee.yani Allah taala ne aap ka rukh kaabey ki taraf pher diya. aur (ibne-Musanna ki) hadees (yahan) mukammal ho gaee. aur nasar-ban-Muhajir ne sahib khuwab ka naam zikr kiya aur kaha ke Abdullah-bin-Zaid ke paas eik aadmi aaya jo ke ansaar mein se tha, usi (nasar) ki riwayat mein hai. ... chunanche wo aadmi (khuwab mein) qibla rukh hua aur kaha : الله أكبر الله أكبر۔ أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله . حى على الصلاةdo martaba حى على الفلاحdo martaba - الله أكبر الله أكبر . لا إله إلا اللهphir kuch der thehra , phir khada hua aur usi tarah kaha, magar (حى على الفلاح) ke baad) قد قامت الصلاة . قد قامت الصلاة ( kaha . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye sab Bilal ko batao.'' chunanche Bilal ne Azan kahi. aur rozey ke baarey mein bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her mahiney teen rozey aur Aashoora  ka roza rakha kartey they. tab Allah taala ne hukm nazil farmaya : « { كُتِبَ عَلَيْكُمُ الصِّيَامُ كَمَا كُتِبَ عَلَى الَّذِينَ مِنْ قَبْلِكُم . ... } » ''tum par rozey rakhney farz kiye gaey hain jaisey ke tum se pehley logon par farz kiye gaey they taake tum muttaqi bin jao. ginti ke dinon hain, to jo tum mein se bimar ho ya safar mein to doosrey dino mein unki ginti puri karey aur jo uski taqat rakhtey hain (aur roza nahin rakhna chahtey) to un par eik miskeen ka tuaam (khana) hai.'' chunanche jo chahta roza rakh leta aur jo chahta chhod deta aur her din ke badley eik miskeen ko khana khila deta aur ye uskey liye kafi hota tha. ... ye eik haal hua . phir Allah taala ne ye hukm nazil farmaya : « { شَهْرُ رَمَضَانَ الَّذِي أُنْزِلَ فِيهِ الْقُرْآنُ } » ''Ramazan ka mahina aisa hai ke is mein Quran nazil kya gaya. logon ke liye hidayat hai (jis mein) hidayat ki roshan daleelen hain aur (haq aur batil mein) farq kerney wala hai. so tum mein se jo is mahiney ko paey to wo uskey rozey rakhey aur jo bimar ho ya musafir to doosrey dino mein uski ginti puri karey.'' is se lazim aaya ke jo is mahiney ko paey aur muqeem ho roza rakhey aur musafir qaza karey. boodha-khoosat aur budhiya jo rozey ki taqat nahin rakhtey unke zimmey khana khilana hua . . . . . chunanche Hazrat sirma (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur wo sara din kaam kartey rahey they. ... aur (nasar-bin-Muhajir ne) hadees bayan ki."
508,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya gaya ke Azan ke kalimaat do-do baar aur iqaamat ke eik-eik baar kahiye. Hammad ne apni hadees mein izafa kiya ke magar iqaamat (yani قد قامت الصلاة do baar kahiye).
509,"Janab Khalid hazaa ne abu-Qulaba sey, unhoney Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se. ... (mazkura baala ( riwayat Wuhaib ki misl (jaisi) bayan ki . Ismail ( raawi ( ne kaha : maine ye hadees Ayub ko bayan ki to kaha : '' magar iqaamat '' (yani قد قامت الصلاة )."
510,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein Azan ke kalimaat do do baar kahey jatey they aur iqaamat (takbir) ke eik eik baar . siwaye uskey ke muazzan ( قد قامت الصلاة . قد قامت الصلاة ( kaha karta tha (yani do baar ( to jab ham iqaamat suntey to wuzu karkey Namaz ke liye nikal padtey . Shoba kehtey hain ke maine abu-Jaafar se sirf yehi hadees suni hai.
511,"Janab Sheba, abu-Jaafar masjid Iryaan ke muazzan se aur wo Abu-Musanna masjid akbar ke muazzan se riwayat kartey huey kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se suna aur hadees bayan ki."
512,Janab Muhammad-bin-Abdullah apney chacha Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (shuroo mein) Azan ke mutalliq kuch chizon ka irada farmaya magar un par amal na kiya. chunanche Abdullah-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko khuwab mein Azan dikhlaai gaee : to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur aap ko khabar di. aapney farmaya : ''ye kalimaat Bilal ko batao.''  chunanche unhoney bataey aur Bilal ne Azan kahi . Abdullah ne kaha : maine ye khuwab dekha aur main iska khahish mand tha. farmaya : ''tum iqaamat keh lo.''
513,"Janab Muhammad-bin-Amr ansaar Madina ke mashaaikh mein se hain. kehtey hain ke maine Abdullah-bin-Muhammad ko suna, kehtey they ke merey dada Abdullah-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ye hadees bayan kiya kartey they. ( Abdullah-bin-Muhammad ne ( kaha : chunanche merey dada ne iqaamat (takbir) kahi."
514,"Hazrat Ziyad-bin-Haris Sadaai (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke jab subhe ki pehli Azan ka waqt hua to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya to maine Azan kahi. phir main kehney laga , aey Allah ke Rasool ! iqaamat kahun? magar aap mashriq ki janib Fajr ko dekhtey aur farmatey : ''nahin'' yahan tak ke jab Fajr (achi tarah) tulu ho gaee to aap apni sawari se utrey aur wuzu kiya, phir aap meri taraf aaye aur is beech mein aap ke Sahaba bhi aap ko aa miley (barz se murad hai), aapney wuzu kiya. Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne iqaamat kehney ka irada kiya. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Bilal se farmaya : ''us Sudaai ne Azan kahi hai aur jo Azan kahe wohi iqaamat kahe.'' chunanche maine iqaamat kahi ."
515,Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) raawi hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''muazzan ko jahan tak uski aawaz jati hai bakhsh diya jata hai. aur her khushk aur tar chiz uskey liye gawahi deti hai. aur jo jamaat mein hazir hota hai uskey liye pachchis namazon ka sawab likha jata hai aur (doosri Namaz tak ke) beech ke gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.''
516,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Namaz ke liye Azan kahi jati hai to shetan peeth pher kar paad maarta hua palat jata hai. (aur itni door chala jata hai) yahan tak ke Azan nahin sunta. jab Azan mukammal ho jati hai to lot-aata hai. phir jab iqaamat kahi jati hai to peeth pher kar chala jata hai. aur jab iqaamat ho jati hai to lot-aata hai aur namazi ke dil mein tarah tarah ke khayalat daalta hai aur kehta hai : ye yaad kar , ye yaad kar . aisi aisi baaten yaad dilata hai jo usey yaad na aati hon. yahan tak ke aadmi ko khayal hi nahin rehta ke kitni rakatein padhi hain.''"
517,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Imam zaamin aur zimmedar hai aur muazzan ameen aur qabile-aitimad hai. aey Allah ! imaamon ko) sahih ilm aur amal ki) tofiq dey aur muazzan ko bakhsh dey.''
518,Janab abu-Saaleh kehtey hain main nahin samajhta magar ye ke maine usey Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) hi se suna hai. unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya. aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kiya.
519,banu-najaar ki eik khatoon se riwayat hai unhoney kaha ke mera ghar masjid ke atraaf ke gharon mein sab se ooncha tha. Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Fajr ki Azan usi par aa kar diya kartey they. wo sahar ke waqt aa kar us par beth jatey aur subh saadiq ko dekhtey rehtey jab subh ko tulu hota dekhtey to angdaai letey aur kehtey : aey Allah ! main teri tareef karta hun aur Quraish par tujh hi se madad chahta hun ke wo terey deen ko qaaim karen. wo bayan karti hain ke phir Azan kehtey. qasam Allah ki ! mujhey nahin maloom ke Bilal ne kisi raat bhi ye kalimaat chhodey hon.
520,"Janab a'un-bin-abi-hujaifa apney walid se raawi hain wo kehtey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahuncha jabke aap Makka mein they aur eik khemey mein thehrey huey they jo ke surkh chamdey ka tha. chunanche Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) nikley aur Azan kahi aur main unka munh dekh raha tha ke daeyn, baeyn phertey they. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nikley aur aap surkh rang ka hulla pehney huey they aur ye Yamen ki qitri chadarein thin . Musa (dusri sanad ke raawi aur Imam Abu-Dawud ke ustad) ne kaha : abu-huzaifa ne kaha : maine Bilal ko dekha ke wo wadi abtah ki taraf nikley aur Azan kahi . jab (حی على الصلاة) aur (حی على الفلاح) par pahunchey to apni gardan ko daeyn, baeyn phera aur khud purey nahin ghoomey . phir andar aaye aur apna bhaala nikala aur) Musa ne baqi ( hadees bayan ki ."
521,"Saiyedna Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''azaan aur iqaamat ke beech dua radd nahin ki jati.''"
522,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum Azan suno to usi tarah kaho jaisey ke muazzan kehta hai.''"
523,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farmatey they : ''jab tum muazzan ko suno to usi tarah kaho jaisey wo kehta hai. phir mujh par durood padho. tehqiq jisney mujh par eik baar durood padha , Allah taala us par das rahmatein nazil karta hai. phir merey liye Allah se wasila talab karo. bila-shuba ye ( wasila ( jannat main eik manzil ka naam hai jo Allah ke kisi eik bandey ko milegi aur mujhey umeed hai ke wo main hi hunga . so jisney merey liye Allah se wasila talab kiya uskey liye shafaat halal ho gaee.''"
524,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! muazzan ham se fazilat ley jaeyngey , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum bhi wesay hi kaha karo jaisey ke wo kehtey hain. jab tum us se farigh ho to sawal karo aur dua maango , diye jao-gey.''"
525,"Hazrat Saad-bin-abi-waqaas (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jisney muazzan ko sun kar ye kaha :(وَأَنَا أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ , وَأَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ . رَضِيتُ بِاللَّهِ رَبًّا وَبِمُحَمَّدٍ رَسُولًا وَبِالْإِسْلَامِ دِينًا) ''aur main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud nahin hai. wo akela hai. uska koi shareek aur sajhi nahin aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain. main Allah ke rab honey , Muhammad ke Rasool honey aur Islam par bahaisiyat deen ke razi hun.''  to wo bakhsha gaya."
526,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab muazzan ko suntey aur wo shahadat ke kalmaat kehta , to aap farmatey : ''aur main bhi aur main bhi (yani shahadat deta hun).''"
527,"Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab muazzan kahe ( الله اكبر الله اكبر ( to tumhara sunney wala bhi kahe ( الله اكبر الله اكبر (aur jab wo kahe : (أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله) to sunney wala bhi kahe (أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله) phir wo kahe (أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله) aur ye bhi kahe (أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله) phir wo kahe (حى على الصلاة) aur ye kahe (لا حول wla قوة إلا بالله) phir wo kahe (حى على الفلاح) aur ye kahe (لا حول wla قوة إلا بالله) phir wo kahe  (الله اكبر الله اكبر) aur ye kahe (الله اكبر الله اكبر) phir wo kahe (لا إله إلا الله) aur ye kahe (لا إله إلا الله) ye sab kuch dil ki gehraai se kahe, to jannat mein jaeyga.''"
528,ahle-Sham ke eik fard ne shehar-bin-Hoshab se riwayat kiya unhoney abu-Umama ya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kisi doosrey sahabi se riwayat kiya ke Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne iqaamat kehna shuru ki to jab ( قد قامت الصلاة ( kaha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kaha : ( أقامها الله وأدامها ) ''Allah usey qaaim aur daaim rakhey.'' aur deegar kalimaat ke jawab mein usi tarah kaha jaisey ke mazkura baala Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees mein guzra hai.
529,Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Azan sun kar ye (nichey likhi) dua padhey to qiyamat ke roz uskey liye shafaat lazim hogi . ( اللَّهُمَّ رَبَّ هَذِهِ الدَّعْوَةِ التَّامَّةِ وَالصَّلَاةِ الْقَائِمَةِ آتِ مُحَمَّدًا الْوَسِيلَةَ وَالْفَضِيلَةَ وَابْعَثْهُ مَقَامًا مَحْمُودًا الَّذِي وَعَدْتَهُ ) ''aey Allah ! us kamil pukar aur qaaim rehney wali Namaz ke rab ! Muhammad ko manzil wasila aur fazilat se sarfaraaz farma aur unhein us maqame-Mehmood par khada kar jis ka to ne un se wada farmaya hai.''
530,"ummul-momenin Sayeda umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey taaleem di ke maghrib ki Azan ke waqt ye (nichey likhi) dua padha karun : (اللَّهُمَّ ! إِنَّ هَذَا إِقْبَالُ لَيْلِكَ وَإِدْبَارُ نَهَارِكَ ، وَأَصْوَاتُ دُعَاتِكَ ، فَاغْفِرْلِي)''aey Allah ! be-shak ye waqt hai ke teri raat aa rahi hai, tera din ja raha hai aur teri taraf pukarney walon ki sadaayein hain, lihaza to mujhey bakhsh dey.''"
531,Hazrat Usman-bin-abi-al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey apni qaum ka Imam bana dijiye. aapney farmaya : ''tum unke Imam ho aur unke zaeef tareen ki iqtidaa (riayat) karna aur muazzan aisa muqarrar karna jo apni Azan par ujrat na ley.''
532,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( eik baar ( tulu Fajr se pehley Azan keh di , to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen hukm diya ke jao aur aelan karo ke khabrdar ! be-shak banda so gaya tha. khabrdar ! be-shak banda so gaya tha. Musa ne izafa kiya, chunanche unhoney ja kar aelan kiya : khabrdar ! be-shak banda so gaya tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko Ayub se siwaye Hammad-bin-Salma ke kisi ne riwayat nahin kiya."
533,"Janab Naafe (Rahimahullah) , Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke muazzan se riwayat kartey hain, jis ka naam Masrooh tha, ke unhoney ( eik baar ( Fajr (subh-sadiq) se pehley hi Azan keh di to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hukm diya, aur mazkura baala hadees ki tarah riwayat kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Hammad-bin-Zaid ne usey Ubaidullah-bin-Umar sey, unhoney Naafe se ya kisi doosrey se naqal kiya hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka eik muazzan tha jis ka naam Masrooh ya kuch aur tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : aur Darawardi ne usey Ubaidullah se wo Naafe se wo ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kartey hain kaha ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke muazzan ka naam Masood tha. aur iskey misl (jaisa) bayan kiya aur ye us se ziyada sahih hai."
534,"Shaddad maula ayaaz-bin-Aamir Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se raawi hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhein farmaya : ''jab tak Fajr is tarah numaya na ho jaya karey, Azan na kaha karo.'' aur aapney ateraaf-arz mein apney dono haathon ko phaila kar ishara farmaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Shaddad maula ayaaz ne Hazrat Bilal ko nahin paya."
535,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-umme-maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah ke muazzan they aur na-bina they.
536,Janab Abu-Sha'a-Sa'a bayan kartey hain ke ham Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath eik masjid mein bethey they ke muazzan ne Asr ki Azan kahi to uskey baad eik shakhs masjid se nikal gaya. Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : usney Hazrat abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki nafarmani ki hai.
537,"Hazrat Jabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Azan kehtey, phir zara der rukte , jab dekhtey ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif la rahey hain to iqaamat kehtey."
538,"Janab Mujahid kehtey hain ke main (eik baar) Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath tha ke eik shakhs ne Zohar ya Asr mein tasweeb ki (yani Azan ke baad dobara aelan kiya) to unhoney farmaya : mujhey yahan se ley chalo, be-shak ye bidat hai."
539,Janab Abdullah-bin-abi-Qatada apney walid se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se raawi hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jab iqaamat keh di jaey to jab tak mujhey (aata) na dekh lo khadey na hua karo. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Ayub aur Hajjaj-al sawwaaf ne Yahya se aisey hi riwayat kiya hai. (yani segha ''عن (an)'' ke sath) aur Hisham dustwaai ne kaha  Yahya ne mujhey likha . aur usey Muaawiya-bin-salam aur Ali-bin-mubarak ne Yahya se riwayat kiya. un dono ne us riwayat mein kaha : ''(us waqt tak khadey na ho ( jab tak ke mujhey dekh na lo aur aaram aur sukoon ikhtiyar karo.''
540,Yahya ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke jaisi riwayat kiya. kaha : ''(us waqt tak khadey na ho) yahan tak ke mujhey dekh lo ke main ghar mein se nikal aaya hun. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke (قد خرجت) ke lafz sirf Maamer ne riwayat kiye hain. ibne-Uena ne Maamer se riwayat kiya to us mein (قد خرجت) ke lafz bayan nahin kiye.
541,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye Namaz ki iqaamat kahi jati aur log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke musalley par tashrif laney se pehley hi apni jaghen ley chukey hotey they. (yani safein barabar kar chukey hotey they)
542,"Janab Humaid kehtey hain ke maine Sabit Bunani se puchha ke koi aadmi iqaamat ho janey ke baad kisi se koi baat karey (to kaisa hai)? to unhoney mujhey Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadees sunai ke (eik baar) Namaz ki iqaamat kahi gaee aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney eik aadmi aa gaya aur usney aap ko (kuch der ke liye) rokey rakha , jabkey iqaamat kahi ja chuki thi."
543,"kahmas kehtey hain ke wadi Mina mein ham Namaz ke liye khadey huey aur Imam nahin pahuncha tha, to ham mein se kuch beth gaey . mujh se koofa ke eik shaikh ne kaha : tum kyon beth gaey ho? maine kaha : ibne-Barida kehtey hain ke ye kaifiyat (khadey munh uthaey dekhna) ( samood ( hai. (aur ye koi achi baat nahin) to us shaikh ne mujh se kaha : mujh se Abdur-Rehman-bin-ausja ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kiya ke ham Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein takbire-tahreema kahe janey se pehley lambi der tak khadey raha kartey they. aur Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo log pehli safon se miley huey hotey hain, shan wala Allah un par rehmat nazil karta aur farishtey unke liye duayen kartey hain aur Allah ke yahan is qadam se badh kar aur koi qadam mehboob nahin jis se wo chal kar aata aur saf ko milaataa hai.''"
544,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Namaz ke liye iqaamat keh di gaee aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid ki eik janib mein (kisi ke sath) sargoshi mein mashghool rahey aur aap Namaz ke liye aaye to logon ko neend aa rahi thi.
545,"Salim Abu-Nasar (Rahimahullah) (Taabai) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) iqaamat kahe janey ke baad masjid mein haazirin ko kam mehsoos kartey to baith jatey aur Namaz na padhatey aur jab dekhtey ke jama ho gaey hain, to Namaz padha detey."
546,"Naafe-bin-Jubair , abu-Masood zarqi se wo Hazrat Ali-bin-abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se usi ke misl (jaisi) riwayat kartey hain."
547,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, farmatey they : ''jis kisi gaanw ya basti mein teen fard bhi hon aur un mein Namaz baa-jamaa't ka ehtimam na ho, to shaitan un par musallat ho jata hai lihaza tum jamaat ko lazim pakdo . bhediya hamesha door rehney wali akeli bakri hi ko khata hai.'' Janab zaayda bayan kartey hain ke Saaib ne kaha ke '' jamaat '' se murad baa-jamaa't Namaz hai."
548,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mera ji chahta hai ke Namaz ki iqaamat ka hukm dun, phir eik aadmi ko kahun ke logon ko Namaz padhaaey aur khud aisey logon ki taraf jaun jo Namaz (ki jamaat) mein hazir nahin hotey aur merey sath kuch log hon jinkey paas lakdiyon ke gatthey hon phir main unke gharon ko aag laga dun.''"
549,"Janab Yazid-bin-asamm kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ko suna, wo kehtey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mera ji chahta hai ke apney jawaanon ko hukm dun ke lakdiyon ke gatthey ikhattey karen, phir main un logon ki taraf jaun jo apney gharon mein namazein padhtey hain, halanke unhen koi uzr nahin hai aur unke gharon ko aag laga dun.'' (Yazid-bin-Yazid ne kaha) maine (apney shaikh) Yazid-bin-asamm se kaha : aey abu-auf ! us se aap ki murad Juma(ki Namaz) thi ya kuch aur? unhoney kaha : merey kaan behrey ho jaeyn agar maine Abu-Huraira ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadees bayan kartey huey na suna ho. unhoney Juma ya dusri Namaz ka zikr nahin kiya. (yani koi takhsees (khaas) nahin, Juma samet tamam namazon ki jamaat ka masla hai.)"
550,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke un paanchon namazon ki hifazat aur pabandi ikhtiyar karo jahan kahin unke liye Azan kahi jaey. kyonkey namazon ki (baa-jamaa't) pabandi ''sunan hudi'' mein se hai. (yani haq aur hidayat ki raah hai.) aur shan waley Allah ne apney Nabi ke liye hidayat ki sunnatein mashroo'a ki hain. aur maine Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ko dekha hai ke waazeh aur khulay munafiq ke alawa koi bhi jamaat se peechey na rehta tha. aur maine Sahaba (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ko dekha hai ke eik aadmi ko do do afrad sahara de-kar latey they aur usey saf mein khada kar diya jata tha aur tum ho ke her eik ne apney ghar hi mein masjid bana rakhi hai. agar tum apney gharon mein namazein padhney lago aur masjidon ko chhod do , to apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat ko chhod betho gey . aur agar tum ne apney Nabi ki sunnat ko chhod diya to kafir ho jao gey."
551,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney muazzan ko suna aur uski ittiba kerney mein (yani masjid mein aaney sey) usey koi uzr (rukawat) na ho. ... sun-ney walon ne puchha . ... uzr se kya murad hai? farmaya : ''koi khof ya bimari. to aisey aadmi ki Namaz jo wo padheyga maqbool na hogi . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : maghra se Abu-Is'haq ne riwayat kiya hai.
552,"Hazrat Abdullah-ibne-umme-maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main naabina aadmi hun, ghar door hai aur mera qaaid (haath pakad kar laney wala) meri madad nahin karta , to kya merey liye rukhsat (chhut) hai ke apney ghar mein Namaz padh liya karun? aapney farmaya : ''kya Azan suntey ho? '' unhoney kaha : haan. aapney farmaya : ''main terey liye rukhsat (chhoot) nahin paata.''"
553,Hazrat Abdullah ibne-umme-maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Madeeney mein keedey aur darindey bahut ziyada hain. (kya merey liye rukhsat hai ke ghar mein Namaz padh liya karun ?) to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(حي على الصلاة) aur (حی على الفلاح) (ki aawaz) suntey ho to zarur aao. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Qasim jermi ne bhi Sufiyan se aisey hi riwayat kiya hai aur uski riwayat mein (حي هلا) ''zarur aao'' ke lafz nahin hain.
554,"Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein subhe ki Namaz padhaai uskey baad farmaya : ''kya falan hazir hai?''  logon ne kaha : nahin. aapney puchha : ''kya falan hazir hai?''  logon ne kaha : nahin. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba ye do namazein munafiqon par sab namazon se bhari hain (yani Isha aur Fajr) aur agar tumhen maloom ho ke un mein kya kuch ajr aur sawab hai to tum un mein zarur aao, agar-che ghutnon ke bal hi aana padey. aur pehli saf (ajr aur sawab mein) farishton ki saf ki manind hai. agar tumhen uski fazilat maloom ho to uskey liye zarur sabqat karo. insan ki Namaz eik aadmi ke sath ziyada ajr aur sawab wali hai ba-nisbat uskey ke wo akela padhey. aur uski Namaz do aadmiyon ke sath ziyada fazilat wali hai ba-nisbat uskey ke wo eik aadmi ke sath mil kar padhey . jis qadr ahle-jamaat ki tadaad ziyada hogi wo ziyada pakizah aur Allah ko bahut ziyada mehboob hai.''"
555,"Saiyedna Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney Isha ki Namaz jamaat se padhi to ye aadhi raat ke qiyam ki tarah hai aur jisney Isha aur Fajr ki namazein baa-jamaa't padhein to ye puri raat ke qiyam ki tarah hai.''"
556,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''jo shakhs jitna masjid se door hota hai utna hi ziyada sawab ka haq daar hota hai.''"
557,"Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik shakhs tha, jahan tak main janta hun, ehale-Madina mein qible ki taraf ho kar Namaz padhney walon mein uska ghar sab se door tha aur masjid mein koi Namaz bhi us se na chookti thi. maine us se kaha : agar aap eik gadhaa kharid lein, garmi aur andherey mein us par Sawar hon (to sahulat rahey) usney kaha : main ye pasand nahin karta ke mera ghar masjid ke qarib ho. uski ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko batai gaee. aapney us se puchha to usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! meri niyat ye hai ke mera masjid mein aana aur yahan se ghar wapis jana sab hi likha jaey. to aapney farmaya : ''Allah ne tumhen ye sab ata farma diya. jis ajr aur sawab ki to ne umeed ki hai Allah ne wo sab inayat farma diya.''"
558,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo aadmi apney ghar se wuzu karkey farz Namaz ke liye nikalta hai to uska ajr aur sawab aisey hai jaisey ke haaji ehram baandhey huey aaye aur jo shakhs chaasht ki Namaz ke liye nikley aur is mashaqqat ya uth khadey honey ki gharz sirf yehi Namaz ho to aisey aadmi ka sawab Umra kerney waley ki manind hai. aur eik Namaz ke baad dusri Namaz ke un dono ke darmiyan koi fuzul aur koi bekar baat na ho. illiyeen mein indraaj (darj) ka baais (wajah) hai.''"
559,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhoney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''baa-jamaa't Namaz ghar ya baazar mein akeley Namaz ( padhney ( ki ba-nisbat pachchis darjay ziyada hoti hai. wo yun ke jab tum mein se koi wuzu karey aur kamil aur achi tarah wuzu karey aur masjid mein aaye aur uski niyat sirf Namaz hi ho aur Namaz hi ne usey uthaya ho to wo jo qadam bhi uthaeyga us se uska eik darja buland hoga aur eik ghalati maaf hogi yahan tak ke masjid mein dakhil ho jaey. aur jab masjid mein dakhil ho jaey to wo Namaz mein shumar hota hai jab tak ke Namaz usey rokey rakhey . aur jab tak koi apni us jagah par betha rahey jahan usney Namaz padhi ho to farishtey uskey liye duayen kartey hain : ''aey Allah ! iski maghfirat farma. aey Allah ! is par rehem farma. aey Allah ! iski tauba qubul farma.'' aur unki ye dua (us waqt tak ( jari rehti hai jab tak ke wo wahan kisi ko eza (takleef) na dey ya be-wuzu na ho jaey.''
560,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jamaat ke sath Namaz pachchis namazon ke barabar hoti hai. aur jab koi shakhs biyaabaan mein Namaz padhta hai aur uskey rukoo aur sujood (sajdon) ko kamil karta hai to uska sawab pachas namazon tak pahunch jata hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke abdul-Waahid-bin-Ziyad ne is hadees mein kaha : '' biyaabaan mein Namaz (shehar aur abadi ke andar) jamaat ki Namaz se do gunaa hoti hai.''  aur) abdul-Waahid ne mukammal) hadees bayan ki."
561,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''khushkhabri do, qiyamat ke roz kamil Noor ki, un logon ko jo andheron mein masjidon ki taraf chal-chal ke aatey hain.''"
562,"Janab Abu-Samaama-hanat bayan kartey hain ke unhen Hazrat Kab-bin-ujra (Raziallahu anhu) miley jabkey wo masjid ko ja rahey they. dono mein se eik ne doosrey ko paya . kehtey hain ke Hazrat Kab ne mujhey paya ke main apney haathon ki ungliyon ko eik dusri mein diye huey tha, to unhoney mujhey us se mana kiya aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''jab tum mein se koi wuzu karey aur achhi tarah wuzu karey phir masjid ka irada karey to apney haathon ki ungliyon ko eik doosre mein hergiz na dey. kyonkey wo Namaz mein hai.''"
563,Janab Saeed-bin-Musaiyab bayan kartey hain ke eik Ansari ki maut ka waqt aa gaya to usney kaha : main tumhen eik hadees sunata hun aur mehaz ajr ke liye sunata hun. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : ''jab tum mein se koi wuzu karta hai aur achhi tarah karta hai phir Namaz ke liye nikalta hai to jab wo apna daayan qadam uthata hai tu Allah taala uskey liye eik neki likh deta hai aur wo baayan qadam nahin tikaataa ke shan wala Allah uski eik ghalati maaf kar deta hai. to jo chahey (masjid ke) qarib rahey ya door (tumhari marzi hai). agar wo masjid mein aa kar jamaat ke sath Namaz padhta hai to uski maghfirat kar di jati hai. agar wo masjid mein aaya aur log kuch Namaz padh chukey they aur kuch baqi the to jo usey mil gaee usney unke sath padhi aur baqi ko pura kar liya to aisey hi hoga (yani uski bhi maghfirat hogi). aur agar wo masjid mein aaya aur log Namaz padh chukey they phir usney (akeley hi) Namaz puri ki to bhi aisey hi hoga (yani bakhsha jaeyga).''
564,Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney wuzu kiya aur achhi tarah wuzu kiya (yani sunnat ke mutabiq kamil wuzu) phir (masjid ki taraf) gaya magar logon ko paya ke wo Namaz se farigh ho chukey hain to shan wala  Allah aisey bandey ko bhi itna hi ajr inayat farmata hai jitna ke usko jisney jamaat mein hazir ho kar Namaz padhi ho. aur ye unke ajron mein kisi kami ka baais nahin hota.''
565,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki bandiyon ko Allah ki masjidon se mat roko , lekin unhen chahiye ke zeb aur zeenat ke baghair niklein (yani saada keyfiyat mein ayen).''"
566,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki bandiyon ko Allah ki masaajid se mana na karo.''
567,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni aurton ko masaajid se mat roko , magar unke ghar unke liye behtar hain.''"
568,"Janab Mujahid ne kaha ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurton ko raat ke waqt masjidon mein janey ki khatir ijazat dey diya karo.'' us par unke eik sahibzadey ne un se kaha : qasam Allah ki ! ham unhein ijazat nahin dengey . wo usey (bahir nikalney ka ( eik bahana bana lengi. qasam Allah ki ! ham unhen ijazat nahin dengey. to Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne usey bahut sakht, sust kaha aur naraz ho gaey. kaha ke main tumhen bata raha hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''unko ijazat do.'' aur tum kehtey ho ke ham unhein ijazat nahin dengey."
569,Umra-binte-Abdur-Rehman se marwi (bayan) hai unhoney batlaya ke ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye soorate-haal dekh letey jo aurton ne apnai hai to unhen masjidon mein aaney se mana farma detey jaisey ke bani-Israel ki aurton ko rok diya gaya tha. Yahya kehtey hain ke maine Umra se kaha ke kya Bani-Israel ki aurton ko us se rok diya gaya tha? unhoney kaha : haan.
570,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se raawi hain ke aapney farmaya : ''aurat ki Namaz uskey apney ghar mein sehan ke bajaey kamrey ke andar ziyada afzal hai, balke kamrey ki bajaey (andruni) kothhri mein aur ziyada afzal hai.''"
571,"Janab Naafe se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar ham ye darwaza aurton ke liye chhod den (unhi ke liye makhsus kar den to bahut behtar ho). '' Naafe kehtey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) martey dam tak us darwazey se masjid mein nahin aaye. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is riwayat ko Ismail-bin-Ibrahim ne Ayub sey, unhoney Naafe se riwayat kiya hai, lekin unhoney usey Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka qol bataya hai aur yehi baat ziyada sahih hai."
572,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aapney farmaya : ''jab Namaz ki iqaamat ho jaey to tum uskey liye daurtey huey na aaya karo balke chaltey huey aao aur itminan aur sukoon ikhtiyar karo. to jo mil jaey padh lo , aur jo reh jaey usey mukammal kar lo.''  Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : zubaidi, ibne-abi-Zi'ib, Ibrahim-bin-Saad, Maamer aur shoaib-bin-abi-Hamza ne Zohri se (وما فاتكم فأتموا) ''jo tum se reh jaey usey mukammal kar lo.'' ke lafz riwayat kiye hain magar akeley ibne-Uena ne Zohri se (فاقضوا) ''qaza do'' bayan kiya hai. aur Muhammad-bin-Amr ne abu-Salma se unhoney Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se aur Jaafar-bin-Rabeea ne Aaraj sey, unhoney Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se (فأتموا) riwayat kiya hai aur ibne-Masood, abu-Qatada aur Anas (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) sabhi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se (فأتموا) ka lafz bayan kiya hai."
573,"abu-Salma, Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se raawi hain ke aapney farmaya : ''Namaz ke liye aao to itminan aur sukoon se aao. jo pa lo padh lo aur jo padhi ja chuki ho uski qaza do (yani pura kar lo).'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : isi tarah ibne-Sirin ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se (وليقض) riwayat kiya hai. aisey hi abu-Raafe ne bhi (Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) sey) riwayat kiya hai aur Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se (فأتموا) aur (اقضوا) marwi (bayan) hai. aur us mein ikhtilaf kiya gaya hai. (yani baaz un sey, ( أتمو »  ka lafz bayan kartey hain aur baaz  ( اقضوا »  ka .)"
574,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul (naqal) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dekha, eik aadmi akeley hi Namaz padh raha hai to aapney farmaya : ''kya koi aadmi us par sadqa nahin kar sakta ke uskey sath mil kar Namaz padhey? ''"
575,"Janab Jabir-bin-Yazid-bin-Aswad apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein Namaz padhi jabkey wo naujawan they. jab aap Namaz padh chukey to dekha ke do aadmi masjid ki eik janib mein mojud hain aur unhoney (jamaat ke sath) Namaz nahin padhi. aapney unhen bulwaya. unhein aap ke samney pesh kiya gaya to unki ye haalat thi ke unke putthey kaanp rahey they. aapney puchha : '' tumhen kya rukawat thi ke hamarey sath Namaz nahin padhi ?'' unhoney kaha : ham apni manzil mein Namaz padh aaye they. aapney farmaya : ''aisey na kiya karo. jab tum mein se koi apni manzil mein Namaz padh chuka ho phir Imam ko paey ke usney abhi Namaz nahin padhi hai to uskey sath bhi mil kar padhey, ye uskey liye nafl hogi.''"
576,Janab Jabir-bin-Yazid apney walid se riwayat kartey hain wo kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Mina mein Fajr ki Namaz padhi. aur ooper wali hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya.
577,"Hazrat Yazid-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main aaya aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz mein they. mein baith gaya, unke sath Namaz mein shareek nahin hua. phir aap farigh huey to hamari taraf rukh kiya aur mujhey baithey dekha to puchha : '' Yazid ! kya tum musalman nahin huey ho?'' maine kaha : kyon nahin aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine Islam qubul kar liya hai, aapney farmaya : '' to tumhein kya hua ke tum logon ke sath Namaz mein shareek nahin huey?'' maine arz kya ke main apney ghar mein Namaz padh kar aaya hun aur mera khayal tha ke shayad aap Namaz padh chukey hongey. aapney farmaya : ''jab tum Namaz ke liye aao aur logon ko Namaz mein pao to unke sath mil kar padho agar-che akeley padh chukey ho. ye tumharey liye nafl ho jaeygi aur wo (pehli Namaz) farz.''"
578,Janab Afeef-bin-Amr-bin-Musaiyab kehtey hain ke mujhey bani-Asad-bin-Khuzaima ke eik shakhs ne bataya ke usney Hazrat Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kya tha ke ham mein se eik apney ghar mein Namaz padh leta hai aur phir masjid mein aata hai aur Namaz ki iqaamat ho jati hai to main unke sath mil kar Namaz padh leta hun magar us se merey dil mein kuch khatak si hai. Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham ne is baarey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha tha to aapney farmaya : ''ye uskey liye jamaat ka eik hissey hai.'' (yani us mein koi harj nahin balke baaise-sawab hai.)
579,"Sulaiman yani maula Memuna kehtey hain ke main Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke paas unki baithak par aaya, wahan log Namaz padh rahey they (aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) Namaz mein shareek na they) maine un se kaha : kya aap unke sath Namaz nahin padhtey? unhoney kaha ke main padh chuka hun. mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sun chuka hun aap farmatey they : ''eik Namaz ko eik din mein do baar mat padho.''"
580,"Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna farmatey they : ''jo shakhs logon ki imaamat kiraaey aur bar-waqt kiraaey to ye uskey liye, aur namaaziyon ke liye baaise-ajr hai aur jisney us mein koi kami ki to uska gunah Imam par hai, namaaziyon par nahin.''"
581,"Talha umme-Ghurab, Aqeela sey, jo ke bani-fazaara ki eik khatoon thi aur unki azad karda londi thi, wo salma-binte-hur se jo kharsha-bin-hur-fazaari ki behan thi , bayan karti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna aap farma rahey they : ''(qurb) qiyamat ki alaamaat mein se (ye bhi) hai ke ehale-masjid imaamat ko eik doosrey par taalein gey aur kisi ko nahin paeyngey jo unki imaamat karaaey.''"
582,"Hazrat abu-Masood-badri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qaum ka wo shakhs imaamat kiraaey jo Quran karim ka bada aur purana qaari ho. agar wo qirat mein barabar hon to wo shakhs imaamat kiraaey jo hijrat karney mein awwal ho. agar hijrat mein barabar hon to badi umr wala imaamat karaaey. aur koi shakhs kisi doosrey ke ghar mein imaamat karaaey, na uski hukoomat ki jagah mein aur na uski khas musnad hi par baithey (jo uski izzat ki jagah ho) siwaey iske ke wo ijazat dey.'' Shoba ne bayan kiya ke maine Ismail se puchha : (تكرمته) ka kya mafhoom hai? unhoney kaha : ''uska bistar.''"
583,Janab-ibne-Muaz raawi hain ke merey walid ne Shoba se ye hadees bayan ki us mein unhoney kaha : ''koi aadmi doosrey ki hukoomat (sarbaraahi) ki jagah mein imaamat na karaaey. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : aur usi tarah Yahya-al-Qattan ne Shoba se (أقدمهم قراءة) riwayat kiya hai. (yani qirat mein puraanaa ho.)
584,Aus-bin-zamaj hizrami Hazrat abu-Masood badri (Raziallahu anhu) se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yehi hadees bayan kartey hain. kaha : ''agar qirate-Quran mein barabar hon to sunnat ka ziyada aalim imaamat karaaey. agar sunnat mein barabar hon to wo Imam baney jo hijrat mein awwal ho.'' is riwayat mein (أقدمهم قراءة) bayan nahin kiya. (yani qirat mein puraanaa honey ka zikr nahin kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Hajjaj-bin-irtaat ne Ismail se riwayat kiya : ''kisi ki musnad (izzat ki jagah) par baghair uski ijazat ke mat baitho.''
585,Hazrat Amr-bin-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham eik aisi jagah padaaw kiye huey they ke log jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aatey to hamarey yahan se guzar kar aatey aur wapsi par bhi hamarey paas se ho kar jatey aur hamein bataya kartey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisey-aisay kaha hai. aur main eik zaheen ladka tha. is tarah maine kafi sara Quran hifz kar liya. aakhir-kaar mere walid apni qaum ka eik wafad lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhein Namaz ki taaleem di aur farmaya : '' tumhara wo aadmi imaamat kiraaey jo Quran sab se ziyada padha ho.'' chunanche main hi qaum mein ziyada padha hua tha kyonkey main (bahut dinon se) Quran yaad karta raha tha. to unhoney mujhey imaamat ke liye aagey kar diya aur main unki imaamat karaney laga . aur mujh par zard rang ki eik chhoti si chadar hua karti thi. jab main sajdey mein jata to kuch be parda sa ho jata . hamari aurton mein se eik ne kaha : ham se apney qaari ka sattar to dhanp do. chunanche un logon ne mujhey eik Amaani qamis kharid kar di. us se mujhey aisi khushi hui ke Islam laney ke baad kisi aur cheez se nahin hui thi. chunanche main unki imaamat karaya karta tha aur meri umr us waqt saat ya aath saal thi.
586,Janab Aasim ahwal Hazrat Amr-bin-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se yehi hadees riwayat kartey hain us mein hai ke main unki imaamat karata aur mujh par eik pewand lagi chadar hoti thi jis main eik surakh tha. jab main sajdey mein jata to meri maqad (peeth) us se nangi ho jati thi.
587,"Janab mis'ar-bin-Habib jurmi ne Hazrat-Amr-bin-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhoney apney walid se bayan kiya ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas apna wafad lekar gaey. un logon ne jab wapsi ka irada kiya to kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamari imaamat kaun karaaey? aapney farmaya : '' jisney Quran ziyada yaad kiya ho.'' chunanche biradari mein koi aisa na tha jisey is qadr Quran aata ho jitna ke mujhey aata tha. to unhoney mujhey aagey kar diya aur main nau-umr ladka tha aur mujh par meri chadar (shamla) hoti thi. meain apni qaum bani-jurm ke jis ijtima mein bhi hota main hi unki imaamat karaya karta aur unke janaazey bhi padhata aur aaj tak padha raha hun. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Yazid-bin-Harun ne mis'ar-bin-Habib se. unhoney Amr-bin-Salma se riwayat kiya ke jab meri qaum apna wafad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein lekar aai. is sanad mein (عن أبيه) ka wasta nahin hai."
588,"Janab Naafe, Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se raawi hain ke jab muhajrin awwaleen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se pehley hijrat karkey aaye to unhon ne maqame-usba par (qubaa ke qarib) padaaw kiya, to Salim maula-abi-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) unki imaamat karaya kartey they. un logon mein unhein hi Quran sab se ziyada yaad tha. haisam ne izafa kiya ke us jamaat mein Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdul asad (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) bhi hotey they."
589,"Janab abu-Qulaba , Hazrat Malik-bin-huwairis (Raziallahu anhu) se raawi hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se ya unke sathi se farmaya : ''jab Namaz ka waqt ho jaey to Azan kaho , phir iqaamat kaho aur imaamat wo kiraaey jo tum mein umr mein bada ho.'' aur Muslima ki riwayat mein hai ke un dino ham ilm mein barabar barabar they. aur Ismael (ibne-aleh) ki riwayat mein hai ke Khalid hazaa ne kaha : maine abu-Qulaba se puchha : qirate-Quran ka masla kya hua? unhoney kaha : ye dono us mein qarib-qarib they."
590,"Janab Ikrima ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kiya, unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chahiye ke tumharey bhaley aur umda log Azan kahen aur tumharey qir'a (haafiz aur aalim) imaamat karaein.''"
591,"Hazrat umme-warqa-binte-naufil (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ghazwae-badar ke liye gaey to maine arz kiya ke aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey apney sath janey ki ijazat dijiye. main aap ke mareezon ka ilaj muaalija aur khidmat karun gi aur shayad Allah taala mujhey shahadat nasib farma de. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum apney ghar hi mein thehro, Allah taala tumhen shahadat ki maut dega.''  chunanche ye ''shaheeda'' ke laqab se pukaari janey lagi aur usney Quran paak padha tha aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se apney ghar mein muazzan rakhney ki ijazat talab ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ijazat dey di. usney eik ghulam aur londi ko mudabbir banaya tha. (yani uski maut ke baad azad hongey) ye dono eik raat uski taraf uthey aur eik chadar se uska munh band kar diya, yahan tak ke wo mar gaee aur khud bhag gaey . subhe ko Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon mein aelan kiya ke jisey unke baarey mein kuch ilm ho ya unhein dekha ho to unhein ley aaye. chunanche unke baarey mein hukm diya aur wo dono sooli chadha diye gaey aur ye Madina mein pehley aadmi they jin ko sooli di gaee."
592,Janab Abdur-Rehman-bin-khallaad se riwayat hai unhoney Hazrat umme-warqa-binte-Abdullah-bin-Haris (Raziallahu anha) se yehi hadees bayan ki hai. aur pehli riwayat ziyada kamil hai. us mein hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey yahaan uskey ghar mein milney ke liye aaya kartey they aur uskey liye eik muazzan muqarrar kiya tha jo uskey liye Azan deta tha aur aapney usey (umme-warqa ko) hukm diya tha ke apney ghar walon ki imaamat karaya karey. Abdur-Rehman kehtey hain ke maine uskey muazzan ko dekha tha jo bahut boodha tha.
593,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''teen shakhson ki Namaz Allah ke yahan maqbool nahin hoti : (eik) wo shakhs jo kisi qaum ke aagey hua aur wo usey napasand kartey hon, (doosra) wo shakhs jo Namaz ke liye jamaat nikal janey ke baad der se aata ho. aur (teesra) wo shakhs jisney kisi azad shakhs ko apna ghulam bana liya ho.''"
594,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''farz Namaz her musalman ke peechey wajib hai chahey nek ho ya bad , agar-che wo badey gunahon ka mujrim ho.''"
595,Saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (apney safar ghazwe ke mauqe par) Hazrat Abdullah-ibne-umme-maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) ko apna ja-nashin banaya tha aur yehi logon ko imaamat karatey they aur ye na-bina they.
596,"Janab Abu-atiya ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat Malik-bin-huwairis (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey yahan usi jagah , jahan ham Namaz padhtey hain, aaya kartey they. chunanche Namaz ki iqaamat kahi gaee to ham ne un se kaha : aagey badhein aur Namaz padhaein . unhoney kaha : koi apna aadmi aagey karo jo tumhen Namaz padhaaey. main tumhein batata hun ke main is waqt kyon Namaz nahin padhata? maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai aap farma rahey they : ''jo shakhs kisi qaum ko milney ke liye jaey to unki imaamat na kiraaey balke un hi mein ka koi shakhs imaamat karaaey.''"
597,"Janab Hammam se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) madaain main eik chabootrey par khadey ho kar logon ki imaamat kara rahey they ke Hazrat abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko qamis se pakad kar khinch liya. jab wo Namaz se farigh huey to kaha : kya tumhen maloom nahin ke logon ko is se mana kiya jata tha. unhoney jawab diya : kyon nahin, jab aapney mujhey khincha to mujhey bhi yaad aa gaya."
598,"Janab Adi-bin-Sabit Ansari kehtey hain ke mujh se eik aadmi ne bayan kiya ke wo madaain mein Hazrat Ammar-bin-Yasir (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath tha ke Namaz ki iqaamat kahi gaee to Ammar aagey badhey aur eik chabootrey par khadey ho kar Namaz padhaaney lagey jabkey doosrey log un se nichey they. Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) aagey badhey aur unke dono haath pakad liye. Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unke sath peechhey hat'te aaye , yahan tak ke Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko nichey utaar diya. jab Ammar apni Namaz se farigh huey to Huzefa ne un se kaha : kya aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se nahin suna aap farmaya kartey they : ''jab koi imaamat kiraaey to doosrey logon se ooncha khada na ho.'' ya kuch aisey hi farmaya. Ammar ne jawab diya : isi liye to main aap ke sath peechhey hat aaya tha jab aapney merey haath pakdey they."
599,Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Isha ki Namaz padha kartey they. phir apni qaum ke paas aatey aur unhein wohi Namaz padhatey.
600,Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhtey aur phir wapis ja kar apni qaum ki imaamat karatey.
601,Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke (eik baar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghodey par Sawar huey aur us se gir padey . us se aap ka daayan pehlu chhil gaya to aapney eik Namaz baith kar padhi. ham ne bhi aap ke peechey baith kar Namaz padhi . jab aap farigh huey to farmaya : '' Imam is liye banaya jata hai ke uski iqtidaa (pairwi) ki jaey. wo jab khada ho kar Namaz padhey to khadey ho kar padho. jab wo rukoo karey to rukoo karo aur jab (سمع الله لمن حمده) sun liya Allah ne usko jisney uski tareef ki.''  kahe to kaho ( ربنا ولك الحمد ( ''aey hamarey rab aur teri hi tareef hai.'' aur jab wo baith kar Namaz padhey to tum sab baith kar Namaz padho.''
602,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madiney main eik ghodey par Sawar huye, usney aap ko khajoor ke eik taney par gira diya. us se aap ke paon mein moch aa gaee (ya apney jod se nikal gaya) ham aap ki iyaadat ke liye hazir huey to aap ko Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke kamre mein paya. aap baith kar nafl padh rahey they. chunanche ham aap ke peechey khadey ho gaey . aap hamari baabat khamosh rahey. ham phir dobara iyaadat ke liye aaye to aapney farz Namaz baith kar padhi aur ham aap ke peechey khadey ho gaey . aapney hamein ishara kiya to ham baith gaey. raawi ne kaha jab aapney Namaz puri ki to farmaya : ''jab Imam baith kar Namaz padhey to baith kar padha karo aur jab wo khadey ho kar padhey to khadey ho kar padho aur is tarah na karo jaisey Faaris waley apney badon ke sath kartey hain.''"
603,"Janab abu-Saaleh Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se raawi hain, unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Imam is liye hota hai ke uski pairwi ki jaey. wo jab takbir kahe to tum bhi takbir kaho . aur jab tak wo takbir na keh ley tum takbir na kaho . aur jab wo rukoo mein jaey to tum bhi rukoo mein jao . aur us waqt tak rukoo mein na jao jab tak ke wo rukoo ke liye jhuk na jaey aur jab wo (سمع الله لمن حمده) kahiye , to tum kaho ( اللهم ربنا لك الحمد ( muslim) bin-Ibrahim (ke lafz hain : ( ولك الحمد ( wo jab sajda karey to tum bhi sajda karo aur us waqt tak sajdey ke liye na jhuko jab tak ke wo sajdey mein chala na jaey, aur jab wo khadey ho kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi khadey ho kar padho aur jab baith kar padhey to tum bhi baith kar padho . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ( اللهم ربنا لك الحمد (ke alfaz hamarey baaz sathiyon ne ( ustaad ( Sulaiman-bin-Harab se mujhey samjhaaye ."
604,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : '' Imam is liye banaya jata hai ke uski pairwi ki jaey.'' aur is riwayat mein izafa kiya : ''aur jab wo qirat karey to tum khamosh raho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye izafa ( وإذا قرأ فأنصتوا ( yani jab Imam qirat karey to tum khamosh raho. mehfooz nahin hai aur hamarey nazdik ye abu-Khalid ka weham hai.
605,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney ghar mein Namaz padhi aur aap bethey huey they aur logon ne aap ke peechey khadey ho kar Namaz padhi to aapney ishara farmaya ke baith jao . jab aap farigh huey to farmaya : '' Imam is liye banaya jata hai ke uski pairwi ki jaey, chunanche jab wo rukoo karey to rukoo karo aur jab sar uthaey to tum bhi uthao aur jab wo baith kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi baith kar padho.''"
606,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bimar ho gaey to ham ne aap ke peechey Namaz padhi jabkey aap baithey huey they aur Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) takbir kehtey they taake logon ko aap ki takbir sunwaayein. phir hadees bayan ki.
607,"Janab Husain , ye Saad-bin-Muaz ki aulad mein se they, Hazrat Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke wo apni qaum ki imaamat karaya kartey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unki iyaadat ke liye tashrif laye to logon ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamara Imam bimar hai, to aapney farmaya : ''jab wo baith kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi baith kar Namaz padha karo . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : ye hadees muttasil nahin hai."
608,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( unki khaala ( umme-haram (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan tashrif ley gaey to unhoney aap ko ghi aur khajurein pesh kin. aapney farmaya : '' khajuron ko unke bartan mein aur ghi ko uskey mishkeezey mein dal do . main rozey se hun.'' phir aap khadey huey aur hamein do rakaat nafl padhaaey to umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anha) ( Hazrat Anas ki walida (aur Umme-Haram hamarey peechey khadi huin . ... Sabit (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya ke main yehi samajhta hun ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tha : aapney mujhey apni daain janib chatai par khada kiya tha.
609,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unki aur un mein se eik khatoon ki imaamat karaai thi. isliye aapney Anas ko apni daain janib aur aurat ko peechey khada kiya tha.
610,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke maine ( eik baar ( apni khaala ummul-momenin Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein raat guzari. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko uthey, aapney mishkeeza khola aur us se wuzu kiya, phir uska munh band kar diya, phir aap Namaz padhney khadey ho gaey . tab main bhi utha aur usi tarah wuzu kiya jaisey ke aapney kiya tha aur aa kar aap ke sath baeyn janib khada ho gaya. to aapney mujhey merey daain haath se pakad kar apney peechey se ghumaayaa aur apni daain janib khada kiya aur maine aap ke sath mil kar Namaz (tahajjud) padhi."
611,Janab Saeed-bin-Jubair Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se us qissey mein bayan kartey hain ke aapney mujhey merey sar se pakda ya merey baal pakdey aur mujhey apni dayen janib khada kar liya.
612,"Saiyedna Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke unki naani Mulaika (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khaney par bulaya . aapney khana khaya (khaya) phir kaha : '' khadey ho jao main tumhen Namaz padhaaun .'' Anas kehtey hain ke main eik chatai ley aaya jo taweel istimal se kaali ho gaee thi. maine us par pani chhidak diya. (taake kuch naram ho jaey .) aap us par khadey ho gaey . maine aur yateem ( ibne-abi zameera , maula Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( ne aap ke peechey saf banai aur budhiya ( Mulaika (Raziallahu anha) ( hamarey peechey khadi huin . aapney do rakatein padhaein phir aap tashrif ley gaey ."
613,Janab Abdur-Rehman-bin-Aswad apney walid se raawi hain. unhoney kaha ke Janab Alqama aur Aswad ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se (unke ghar mein milney ki) ijazat chahi. aur hamein unke darwazey par kafi der bethna pada tha. bil-aakhir eik londi aai jisney hamarey liye ijazat talab ki to aapney hamein bulwa liya . phir aap Namaz ke liye uthey to mere aur unke darmiyan khadey huey (aur hamein Namaz padhaai ( phir kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey hi dekha tha.
614,Janab Jabir-bin-Yazid-bin-Aswad apney walid se naqal kartey hain. kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechey Namaz padhi to ( dekha ke) aap jab Namaz se farigh hotey to qibley ki taraf se (muqtadiyon ki taraf) phir jaya kartey they.
615,Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke ham jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechey Namaz padhtey to pasand kartey ke aap ki dayen janib khadey hon ke aap (salam ke baad) hamari taraf rukh karengey .
616,"Ata khurasani Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Imam ne jis jagah Namaz padhaai ho, usi jagah (sunnat ya nafl) na padhey , yahan tak ke wahan se hatt jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Ata khurasani ne Mughira-bin-Shoba ko nahin paya."
617,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Imam ne jab Namaz puri kar li ho aur (aakhiri) q'ada mein baith gaya ho aur kalam kerney (yani salam pherney) se pehley hi be-wuzu ho jaey to uski Namaz ho gaee aur uskey muqtadiyon ki bhi jinhon ne Namaz puri padhi ho, Namaz kamil hogi.''"
618,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Namaz ki miftaah (chaabi) wuzu hai. iski tahreem, takbir aur tahleel salam hai.''"
619,"Hazrat Muaawiya-bin-abi-Sufiyan (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' rukoo aur sujood (sajdey) mein tum mujh se aagey badhney ki koshish na kiya karo, kyonkey main rukoo kerney mein tum se jis qadr aagey hunga, mere sar uthaney par tumhari ye bharpaye ho jaeygi (ke tum itna hi takheer se sar uthao gey) bila-shuba main kisi qadr bhari ho gaya hun.''"
620,Janab Abdullah-bin-Yazid khitmi logon ko khutba dey rahey they. unhoney kaha ke hamein Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya. . . . . aur wo jhootey nahin they. . . . . ke Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu  Anhum) jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rukoo se sar uthatey to khadey rehtey . jab dekhtey ke aap sajdey mein chaley gaey hain tab sajdey ke liye jhuktey.
621,"Janab Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Laila , Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain ke ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padha kartey they aur ham mein se koi apni peeth na jhukaataa tha jab tak ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko na dekh leta ke unhoney apni peshani zameen par rakh di hai."
622,"Janab mahaarib-bin-dassaar riwayat kartey hain ke Abdullah-bin-Yazid ne member par khutba detey huey kaha : mujh se Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Sahaba kiram Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padha kartey they, jab aap rukoo kartey to wo rukoo kartey jab aap (سمع الله لمن حمده) kehtey (to wo sar uthatey) aur phir khadey rehtey yahan tak ke aap ko dekh letey ke aapney apni peshani zameen par rakh di hai. phir wo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki perwi kartey. (yani sajda kartey.)"
623,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ( Imam se pehley ( apna sar uthata hai jabkey wo Imam sajdey mein ho, usey darna chahiye ke kahin Allah taala uska sar gadhey ke sar jaisa na bana dey ya uski shakal gadhey ki shakal na bana dey.''"
624,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sahaba kiram ko Namaz ki targheeb di aur unhein mana farmaya ke aap ke uth kar janey se pehley uth kar jayen.
625,Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se eik kapdey mein Namaz ke mutalliq puchha gaya to aapney farmaya : ''kya tum mein se her eik ke paas do do kapdey hain ?''
626,Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs eik kapdey mein Namaz na padhey is haal mein ke us mein se kuch uskey kandhon par na ho.''
627,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi, eik kapdey mein Namaz padhey to is chadar ke dono palluon mein se dayen pallu ko bayen kandhey par aur bayen pallu ko dahiney kandhey par dal ley.''"
628,Saiyedna Umar-bin-abi-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap eik kapda lapetey Namaz padh rahey they aur aapney uskey dono palluon ( kinaron ( ko eik doosrey ki mukhalif simt se apney kandhon par dala hua tha.
629,"Hazrat Qais-bin-Talq apney walid se raawi hain, unhoney bayan kiya ke ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. isi beech main eik aadmi aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke Nabi ! eik kapdey mein Namaz ke baarey mein aap ka kya irshad hai? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna tehband khola aur us par ooper wali chadar ko lapetaa (is tarah dono eik hi chadar bin gaeen (aur usey apney ooper lapet liya , phir aap khadey huey aur hamein Namaz padhaai . Namaz se farigh huey to farmaya : ''kya tum sab ko do do kapdey muyassar hain?''"
630,Hazrat sahal-bin-Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine logon ko dekha ke kapdon ki tangi ke baais unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechey Namaz mein apney teh-bandon ke palluon ko apni gardanon mein gireh lagai hoti thi jaisey ke bachchon ki hoti hai to eik shakhs ne kaha : aey aurton ! tum mardon se pehley apney sar na uthaya karo. (kahein kisi ke sattar par nazar na pad jaey.)
631,Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik kapdey mein Namaz padhi aur uska kuch hissey mujh par bhi tha.
632,Hazrat-Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main shikari aadmi hun. kya main sirf eik qamis mein Namaz padh liya karun? aapney farmaya : '' haan aur usey batan laga liya karo chahey (chahein) kaantay hi ke hon.''
633,Janab Muhammad-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Bakr (Mulaiki) apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne eik qamis mein hamein Namaz padhaai aur un par chadar na thi. jab wo farigh huey to kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha tha ke aapney eik hi qamis mein Namaz padhaai thi.
634,Janab Ubaada-bin-Waleed-bin-Ubada-bin-Saamit kehtey hain ke ham Hazrat Jabir-ibne-Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke yahan aaye to unhoney bataya ke main eik ghazwey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath chala . aap uth kar Namaz padhney lagey aur mujh par eik chadar thi. maine uskey palluon ko uskey mukhalif aitraaf se lapetney ki koshish ki (yani daayan pallu bayen kandhey par aur baayan pallu dayen kandhey par dalney laga) magar us mein gunjaaish nahin thi aur uskey kinaron par jhaalar si lagi thi. maine unhein ulta kiya aur uskey kinaron mein ikhtilaf karkey apni gardan par baandh liya aur gardan ko jhuka liya ke kahein gir na jaey. phir main aa kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath aap ki bayen janib khada ho gaya to aapney mera haath pakda aur mujhey ghumaa kar apni dayen janib khada kar diya. phir ibne-sakhr aaye aur wo aap ki bayen janib khadey ho gaey. aapney ham dono ko apney dono haathon se pakda yahan tak ke apney peechhey khada kar diya. aap mujhey kankhiyon se dekh rahey they magar main na samajh saka . phir main samajh gaya aur aapney ishara kiya ke usey teh band bana lun . jab aap farigh huey to farmaya : ''aey Jabir !'' maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool mein hazir hun ! aapney farmaya : ''jab kapda khula ho to uskey kinaron mein ikhtilaf kar liya karo (aur kandhon par dal liya karo (aur agar tang ho to apni kamar par baandh liya karo.'' (yani sirf teh band baandh liya karo.)
635,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya. ... ya ye kaha ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha . ... ''jab tum mein se kisi ke paas do kapdey hon to un mein Namaz padhey. agar eik hi ho to usey teh band bana ley aur yahudiyon ki tarah na lapetey.''
636,Janab Abdullah-bin-Barida apney walid ( Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu)) se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai ke aadmi chadar mein aisey Namaz padhey ke usey lapetaa na ho. doosrey ye ke sirf paajamey mein Namaz padhey aur us par chadar na ho.
637,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna aap farmatey they : '' jisney Namaz mein takabbur kartey huey apna tehband takhnon ke nichey latkaayaa , Allah uskey gunah maaf nahin farmaeyga , na burey kamon se usey bachaey ga .'' (ya uskey liye jannat ko halal aur jahannam ko haram nahin farmaeyga ya jab wo Allah ki taraf se kisi halal kaam mein nahin to uskey liye bhi koi ehtiraam na hoga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke muhaddeseen ki eik jamaat maslan Hammad-bin-Salma, Hammad-bin-Zaid, aur abu-Muaawiya (reh.) ne is hadees ko Aasim se ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) par moquf riwayat kiya hai."
638,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik dafa eik aadmi Namaz padh raha tha aur wo apna tehband takhnon se nichey latkaaey huey tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (dekha to) usey farmaya : '' jao aur wuzu karkey aao .'' chunanche wo gaya aur wuzu karkey aaya . aapney usey dobara farmaya : '' jao aur wuzu karkey aao .'' chunanche wo gaya aur wuzu karkey aaya . to eik aadmi ne aap se kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kis wajeh se aapney usey wuzu kerney ka hukm diya, phir aap us se khamosh hi rahey? aapney farmaya : ''ye shakhs apna teh band latka kar Namaz padh raha tha aur Allah taala aisey bandey ki Namaz qubul nahin karta jo apna tehband latka kar Namaz padh raha ho.''"
639,ummul-momenin Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kiya gaya ke aurat kin kapdon mein Namaz padhey? to unhoney kaha : ''odhni aur puri qamis mein Namaz padhey jo uskey paon tak ko dhanp ley.''
640,"Janab Muhammad-bin-Zaid se riwayat hai, yehi hadees unhoney Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha ke kya aurat eik qamis aur odhni mein Namaz padh ley jabkey usney teh band na baandha ho? aapney farmaya : ''(haan) jab qamis puri tarah dhaanpney wali ho ke uskey paon ki pusht ko bhi dhak ley.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is hadees ko Malik-bin-Anas , Bakr-bin-Muzar , Hafs-bin-Ghiyas , Ismaaeel-bin-Jaafar , ibne-abi Zi'ib aur ibn-Is-haq ne Muhammad-bin-Zaid sey, unhoney apni walida sey, unhoney Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kiya hai. un mein se kisi ne bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka zikr nahin kiya balke sirf umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) par iqtisaar kiya hai. (yani moquf bayan kartey hain.)"
641,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala kisi baligh aurat ki Namaz odhni ke baghair qubul nahin farmata .''Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is hadees ko Saeed yani ibne-abi-arooba ne Qatada se unhoney Hasan se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya hai.
642,Imam Muhammad-bin-Sirin bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) safiya-umme-Talha talhaat ki mehman huin. unki betiyon ko dekha to farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye jabkey merey hujrey main eik nau-umr ladki thi. aapney apna tehband meri taraf phenka aur farmaya : ''isey do hisson mein pahaadon aur eik hissey us ladki ko dey do aur doosra usko jo umme-Salma ke yahan hai. main samajhta hun ke ye baligh (jawan) ho gaee hai. ya ( farmaya ke) mein samajhta hun ke ye dono jawan ho gaee hain.'' Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Hisham ne bhi ibne-Sirin se aisey hi riwayat kiya hai.
643,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz mein sadal se mana farmaya hai aur is se bhi ke insan munh dhanp kar (dhaataa baandh kar) Namaz padhey . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke isey asl ne Ata sey, unhoney Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz ke dauran mein sadal se mana farmaya hai."
644,ibne-Juraij kehtey hain ke maine Janab Ata (ibne-abi-Ribah . . . . . Taabai ( ko baarhaa dekha ke wo sadal kiye huey Namaz padhtey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Ata ka ye qaul (goya) mazkura baala hadees (abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu)) ko zaeef Sabit karta hai.
645,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey (yani iwiyon ke istimal kiye huey) kapdon mein ya hamarey lihaafon mein Namaz na padha kartey they. Ubaidullah ne kaha ke) شعرنا أو لحفنا (ke alfaz mein merey walid ko shak hua hai (is liye lafz (أو) se riwayat kiya hai).
646,"Janab Saeed-bin-abi-Saeed-Maqbari apney walid se bayan kartey hain, unhoney Hazrat abu-Raafe (maula Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( ko dekha ke wo Hazrat Hasan-bin-Ali (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke paas se guzrey jabkey wo khadey Namaz padh rahey they aur unhoney apni guddi mein apney baalon ki choti dhansa rakhi thi. isliye abu-Raafe ne unke baal khol diye . Hazrat Hasan ne ghussey se unki taraf dekha, to abu-Raafe ne kaha : apni Namaz padhiye aur naraz mat hoiye . bila-shuba maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai ke joodey ka ye maqam shaitan ki baithak hai."
647,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne dekha ke Abdullah-bin-Haris Namaz padh rahey they aur unke baal peechhey se bandhey huey they, to wo unke peechhey khadey ho kar unke baal kholney lagey . unhoney (yani Abdullah-bin-Haris ne daurane-namaz mein) us par koi inkar na kiya. Namaz ke baad wo ibne-Abbas ki taraf mutawajjeh huey aur kaha : aap ko merey sar se kya kaam? (yani aapney merey baal kyon kholey ? ( unhoney jawab diya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : '' baalon ka jooda bana lena aisey hai jaisey koi Namaz padhey aur uskey haath peechhey bandhey hon.''"
648,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-saaib (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko fatah-makka waley din dekha ke aap Namaz padh rahey they aur aap ke jootey aap ki bayen janib rakhey huey they.
649,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-saaib (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein makkey mein subh ki Namaz padhaai, (is Namaz mein) aapney Sura mominoon ki tilawat shuru ki . jab Hazrat Musa aur Hazrat Harun (ale.)  ya yun kaha ke Hazrat Musa aur Hazrat Esa (ale.) ka zikr aaya . ... . ibne-ibaad ko shak hai ya logon ne ikhtilaf kiya hai. ... to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khaansi aa gaee to aapney qirat ko mukhtasar kar diya aur rukoo kar liya aur Abdullah-bin-saaib is mein hazir they."
650,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney Sahaba ko Namaz padha rahey they ke aapney (daurane-namaz mein) apney jootey utaar kar apni bayen janib rakh liy . jab Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ne aap ko dekha to unhoney bhi apney jootey utaar diye . jab aap Namaz se farigh huey to farmaya : ''tum logon ne apney jootey kyon utarey? '' unhoney kaha ke ham ne aap ko dekha ke aapney apney jootey utarey hain to ham ne bhi utaar diye . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Jibrael Alehissalam merey paas aaye aur bataya ke aap ke jootey mein gandagi lagi hai.'' (lafz  (قذر) tha ya (أذى)) aapney farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi masjid mein aaye to apney jooton ko ba-ghaur dekh liya karey. agar un mein koi gandagi ya gandagi nazar aaye to usey ponchh daley aur phir un mein Namaz padh ley.''
651,Janab Bakr-bin-Abdullah (Rahimahullah) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye mazkura hadees bayan ki to unhoney us mein jahan lafz (قذر) aaya hai wahan dono jagah ( خبث ( istimal kiya. (aur maani in sab ka ''gandagi'' hai.)
652,Hazrat Shaddad-bin-Aus (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yahood ki mukhalifat karo . ye log apney jooton ya mozon mein Namaz nahin padhtey hain.''
653,Janab Amr-bin-shoaib (عن أبیه an جدہ) ke wastey se marwi (bayan) hai wo riwayat kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap jootey utaar kar bhi Namaz padhtey they aur pehan kar bhi.
654,Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi Namaz padhey to apney jooton ko apni dayen janib na rakha karey aur na bayen janib ke is tarah wo kisi doosrey ki dayen janib hongey. haan agar uski bayen janib koi aur na ho to us taraf rakh ley warna unhein apney dono qadmon ke darmiyan mein rakhey.''
655,Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jab koi Namaz padhney lagey aur apney jootey utarey to un se kisi doosrey ko eza (takleef) na dey . (yani uskey aagey ya dayen taraf na rakhey ya kisi aur tarah se bhi aziyat ka baais na baney.) chahiye ke unhein apney qadmon ke darmiyan mein rakhey ya pehney huey hi Namaz padh ley.''
656,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Memuna binte-Haris (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padhtey to main aap ke qarib barabar hi mein hoti , aur dinon se hoti . aap sajdey ko jatey to baaz-oqaat aap ka kapda bhi mujhey lagta aur aap chhoti-chatai par Namaz padha kartey they."
657,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke eik Ansari ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main bhari jism wala hun. ... aur wo waqae mota tha. . . . . . main aap ke sath mein Namaz ada nahin kar sakta. ... aur usney aap ke liye khana tayyar karwaya aur aap ko apney ghar dawat di. ... to aap (mere yahan ghar mein) Namaz padhein , yahan tak ke aap ko dekhun ke aap kaisey Namaz padhtey hain, lihaza main bhi aap ki tarah kiya karun. (chunanche aap uskey ghar tashrif ley gaey) to un logon ne aap ke liye chatai ke eik tukdey par pani chhidkaa (taake wo naram ho jaey) aapney us par khadey ho kar do rakaat Namaz padhi.jarood ke betey falan ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke kya aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chaasht ke waqt ki Namaz padha kartey they? unhoney kaha : maine aap ko sirf isi din ye Namaz padhtey dekha tha."
658,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anha) ki mulaqat ke liye jaya kartey they to kabhi-kabhi unke yahan Namaz ka waqt bhi ho jata . isliye aap hamari eik chatai par Namaz padha kartey they, wo is chatai par pani chhidak diya karti thin."
659,Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chatai aur rangey huey chamdey par Namaz padhtey they.
660,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke sakht garmi ke mausam mein ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padha kartey they to jab koi ham mein se apni peshani zameen par na tikaa sakta , to apna kapda bicha leta phir us par sajda karta."
661,Hazrat Jabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum safein wesey kyon nahin banatey jaisey ke farishtey apney rab ke yahan banatey hain? ''  ham ne kaha : farishtey apney rab ke yahan kaisey safein banatey hain? aapney farmaya : '' wo pehley ibtidaai (shuruati) safein mukammal kartey hain aur aapas mein jud kar khadey hotey hain.'' (unke beech koi khala (khali jagah) nahin rehta.)
662,"Hazrat Nauman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne logon ki taraf apna rukh kiya aur farmaya : ''apni safein barabar kar lo.'' aapney ye teen baar farmaya : ''qasam Allah ki ! (zarur aisa hoga ke) ya to tum apni safon ko barabar rakho gey ya Allah taala tumharey dilon mein mukhalifat paida kar dega.'' Hazrat Nauman (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke phir maine dekha ke eik aadmi apney kandhey ko apney sathi ke kandhey ke sath , apney ghutney ko apney sathi ke ghutney ke sath aur apney takhney ko apney sathi ke takhney ke sath mila kar aur jod kar khada hota tha."
663,"Hazrat Nauman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein safon mein aisey barabar aur sidha kiya kartey they jaisey ke teer ko sidha kiya jata hai. yahan tak ke jab aap ko yaqeen ho gaya ke ham ne aap se ye dars ley liya aur usey khoob samajh liya hai, to eik din aap hamari taraf mutawajjeh huey aur dekha ke eik aadmi apna seena saf se aagey nikaley huey hai. aapney farmaya : ''(qasam Allah ki !) tum log ya to safon ko barabar karogey ya Allah taala tumharey chehron ke beech mukhalifat paida kar dega.''"
664,"Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) safon ke darmiyan eik taraf se dusri taraf ko chaltey jatey. (is beech mein) aap hamarey seenon aur kandhon par haath phertey aur farmatey : ''aagey peechhey mat hon, warna tumharey dilon mein bhi ikhtilaf aa jaeyga .''  aur aap farmaya kartey they : ''Shan wala Allah pehli safon mein aaney walon par rehmat nazil karta hai aur farishtey unke liye duayen kartey hain.''"
665,Hazrat Nauman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab ham Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamari safon ko barabar kartey. jab ham durust ho jatey to aap takbir kehtey .
666,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''safon ko durust kar lo, kandhon ko barabar rakho, darmiyan mein fasla na rehney do aur apney bhaiyon ke haathon mein naram bin jao.'' . ... raawi hadees Esa-bin-Ibrahim ne ( بأيدي إخوانكم ( apney bhaiyon ke haathon mein.'' ke lafz bayan nahin kiye. ... ''aur shaitan ke liye khalaa (khali jagah) na chhodo. jisney saf ko milaaya, Allah usey milaaey aur jisney saf ko kaata Allah usey kaatey.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke (raawi hadees) ''Abu-Shajara'' se murad Kaseer-bin-Murra hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke  ''apney bhaiyon ke haathon mein naram ho jao .'' ka maani ye hai ke jab koi saf mein dakhil hona chahey to (saff mein pehley se mojud) her shakhs ko apney kandhey naram kar deney chaahiyen taake wo saf mein dakhil ho sakey."
667,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul (naqal ki) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni safon mein khoob mil kar khadey hua karo. unhein qarib-qarib banao aur gardanon ko bhi barabar rakho. qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai, main shaitan ko dekhta hun ke khaali jagahon mein se tumhari safon mein ghus aata hai goya wo bakri ka bacha ho.''"
668,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''safon ko sidha aur barabar karo. bila-shuba safon ko barabar karna Namaz ki takmil ka hissa hai.''
669,"Janab Muhammad-bin-Muslim-bin-saaib sahab maqsoora ka bayan hai ke maine eik din Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke pehlu mein Namaz padhi to unhoney kaha : kya aap ko maloom hai ke ye lakdi kyon rakhi hui hai? maine kaha : nahin, qasam Allah ki ! unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is par haath rakha kartey they (yani apney haath mein pakda kartey they) aur farmatey they : '' barabar ho jao aur apni safon ko sidha kar lo.''"
670,"Janab Muhammad-bin-Muslim ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se mazkura hadees bayan ki aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to is lakdi ko dayen haath se pakad letey phir (dayen saf ki taraf) mutawajjeh ho kar kehtey : ''sidhey khadey ho jao, apni safon ko barabar kar lo.'' phir apney bayen haath se pakadtey (aur bayen janib mutawajjeh hotey) aur farmatey : ''sidhey khadey ho jao aur apni safon ko barabar kar lo.''"
671,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(pehley) pehli saf ko pura karo phir jo saf uskey baad ho. aur jo kami ho to wo aakhiri saf mein ho.''
672,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein behtareen log wo hain jinkey kandhey Namaz mein naram hon. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke raawi hadees Jaafar-bin-Yahya ehale-makka mein se hain.
673,Janab abdul-hameed-bin-Mehmood bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Jume ke din Namaz padhi to (azdahaam (bheedh) ki wajeh sey) hamein sutonon ki taraf dhakel diya gaya. chunanche ham (sutonon sey) aagey peechhey ho gaey (yani sutonon ke darmiyan khadey nahin huey) is par Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein ham is se bacha kartey they. (yani sutonon ke darmiyan safein nahin banatey they.)
674,Hazrat abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chahiye ke tumharey ehale-aql aur danish mere qarib khadey huan karein. phir wo jo unke qarib hain. unke baad wo jo unke qarib hain.''
675,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi ke misl (jaisi) riwayat kiya aur mazeed bayan kiya : ''aagey peechhey mat ho, warna tumharey dilon mein ikhtilaf aa jaeyga aur bazaron ke shor aur shaghabi se bacho.''"
676,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah taala safon ke dayen taraf walon par apni rehmat (khaas) nazil farmata hai aur farishtey unke liye duayen kartey hain.''
677,"Janab Abdur-Rehman-bin-ghanam ne kaha ke Hazrat abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya main tumharey samney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz na bayan karun? chunanche unhoney bataya ke aapney iqaamat kahi , phir mardon ki saf banai aur phir bachchon ki saf unke peechhey banai aur unhein Namaz padhaai. aur abu-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap ki puri Namaz bayan ki, phir farmaya : aisey hi hai Namaz ! . ... abdul-a'alaa ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke aapney farmaya tha : ''aisey hi hai Namaz meri ummat ki.''"
678,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mardon ki behtareen saf (ajr aur fazilat mein) pehli saf hai aur kam tar aakhiri saf hai. aur aurton ki behtareen saf wo hai jo sab se aakhir mein ho aur (ajr aur fazilat mein) kam tar wo hai jo sab se pehli ho.''
679,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo log saf awwal se peechhey rehtey (aur usey apni aadat bana letey) hain Allah unhein jahannam mein bhi peechhey kar dega.''
680,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney (baaz) Sahaba mein ye baat dekhi ke wo peechhtey rehtey hain, to aapney farmaya : ''aagey badho aur meri iqtida (pairwi) karo. tumharey baad waley tumhari pairwi karein. aur jo log peechhey rehney ko apni aadat bana letey hain unka anjam ye hoga ke Shan wala Allah unhein peechhey kar dega.'' (yani apni rehmat se. ... jannat mein dakhil kerney mein. ... ya jahannam mein peechhey kar dega ya jahannam se der se nikalega.)"
681,"Janab Yahya-bin-basheer-bin-khallaad apni walida se raawi hain ke wo Muhammad-bin-Kab qurzi ke paas ayen to unhein suna, wo keh rahey they ke mujh se Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Imam ko (saff se aagey) darmiyan mein khada karo aur saf ke khalaa (khali jagah) ko pura karo.''"
682,Hazrat wabisa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik shakhs ko dekha ke wo saf ke peechhey khada akela hi Namaz padh raha tha to aapney usey dohraaney ka hukm diya. Sulaiman-bin-Harab ne lafz (الصلاة) bhi bayan kiya yani (فأمره أن يعيد الصلاة) ''ke Namaz dohraaey.''
683,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke wo masjid mein dakhil huey aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rukoo mein they, kaha chunanche main saf mein milney se pehley hi rukoo mein ho gaya. ( Namaz ke baad) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala teri hirs aur ziyada karey, aainda aisey na karna.''"
684,"Janab Hasan Basri se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rukoo mein they, to unhoney saf mein milney se pehley hi rukoo kar liya aur phir (usi haalat mein) chaltey huey saf mein ja miley. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz mukammal ki to puchha : ''tum mein se kis ne saf mein milney se pehley rukoo kiya tha phir wo chaltey huey saf mein mila?  ''Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : wo main tha. aapney farmaya : ''Allah taala teri (neki ki) hirs aur badhaey , phir aisey na karna. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Ziyad aalim ka naam Ziyad-bin-fulan-bin-qurra hai aur ye Yunus-bin-Ubaid ka khaala-zaad hai."
685,Hazrat Talha-bin-Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul (naqal ki) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum apney samney paalaan ki pichhli lakdi ke barabar koi chiz rakh lo to tumhein koi nuqsan nahin ke kaun tumharey aagey se guzarta hai. ''
686,"Janab ibne-Juraij , Ata se bayan kartey hain unhoney kaha : paalaan ki pichhli lakdi eik zaraa'a (haath) ya us se kuch zayed hoti hai."
687,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab eid padhney ke liye nikaltey to hukm detey ke neza sath ley liya jaey. usey aap ke aagey gaad diya jata phir aap uski taraf Namaz padhtey aur log aap ke peechhey hotey. safar mein bhi aap ka ye mamool hota tha. chunanche ameeron ne yahin se ye amal liya hai.
688,Janab a'un-bin-abi-Juhaifa apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhein (makka ke qarib) wadi Bat'haa mein Namaz padhaai aur aap ke samney chhota neza tha. (aapney hamein) Zohar aur Asr ki do-do rakatein padhaeen. is neze ke aagey se aurat bhi guzarti thi aur gadhaa bhi.
689,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi Namaz padhney lagey to apney samney koi chiz rakh ley. agar kuchh na miley to koi lathi khadi kar ley. agar uskey paas aasa (lathi) na ho to khat hi khinch ley. phir uskey aagey se jo bhi guzrey usey nuqsan na hoga.''"
690,"Janab abu-Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-hurriyat apney dada Hurais se jo bani-azra ke aadmi they, wo Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) sey, wo Hazrat abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain aur lakeer khinchney wali hadees bayan ki. Sufiyan-bin-Uena kehtey hain ke hamein aisi koi daleel nahin mili jis se ham is hadees ko taqwiyat dey sakein aur ye sirf isi sanad se marwi (bayan) hai. (ibne-madini ne kaha) maine Sufiyan-bin-Uena se kaha ke muhaddeseen iskey raawi mein ikhtilaf kartey hain (aaya ye abu-Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-hurriyat hai ya koi aur) to unhoney kuchh socha aur phir kaha : mujhey abu-Muhammad-bin-Amr hi yaad hai. Sufiyan ne kaha ke Ismaaeel-bin-Umayya ki wafat ke baad eik aadmi aaya aur us (aaney waley) shaikh ne abu-Muhammad ko talab kiya, wo mil gaya aur is hadees ke mutalliq puchha magar usey ishtabah ho gaya (yani wo isey sahih tareeqey se bayan nahin kar saka). Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : maine Imam Ahmed-bin-Hanbal (Rahimahullah) se suna, unhoney kaee baar khat khinchney ka wasf bayan kiya to kaha ke is tarah arz mein khincha jaey jaisey ke Hilal hota hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : maine Musaddad se suna unhoney kaha ke ibne-Dawud (khuraibi)  ne kaha ke ye khat tool (lambaai) mein khincha jaey. Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : maine Imam Ahmed-bin-Hanbal (Rahimahullah) se suna unhoney kaee baar is khat ki sift ye batai ke ye arz mein ho aur Hilal ki manind golai mein ho."
691,Janab Sufiyan-bin-Uena kehtey hain ke maine shareek (bin-Abdullah-bin-abi-namr. . . . . . ya shareek-bin-Abdullah Nakhai koofi) ko dekha ke unhoney hamein eik janaze ke ijtima mein Asr ki Namaz padhaai to apney samney apni topi rakh li. yani eik farize mein jis ka waqt ho chuka tha.
692,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney oont ko sutrah bana kar uski taraf Namaz padh liya kartey they.
693,"Hazrat zaba'a-binte-Miqdad-bin-Aswad apney walid (Hazrat Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat karti hain, unhoney kaha, maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab bhi kisi lakdi , sutoon ya darkht ki taraf (munh karkey) Namaz padhtey to usey hamesha apney dayen ya bayen ki taraf rakhtey, bilkul aen samney na rakhtey they."
694,"Janab Muhammad-bin-Kab-qurzi ne bayan kiya ke maine un se yani Umar-bin-Abdul-Azeez se kaha ke mujh se Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''soney waley ke peechhey (khadey ho kar) Namaz padho , na baaton mein mashghool shakhs ke peechhey.''"
695,"Hazrat sahal-bin-abi-hasma (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marfooan bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi kisi sutrah ki taraf Namaz padhey to uskey qarib khada ho, kahin shaitan is par uski Namaz na qaat de. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : waaqid-bin-Muhammad ne is hadees ko Safwan sey, unhoney Muhammad-bin-sahal se, unhoney apney walid se ya Muhammad-bin-sahal se, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya hai, jabkey baaz ne Naafe-bin-Jubair se, usney sahal-bin-Saad se kaha hai. aur iski sanad mein ikhtilaf kiya gaya hai."
696,Hazrat Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke qibley (yani sutrey) ke darmiyan itna fasla hota ke us se eik bakri guzar sakti thi. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : ye hadees (merey shaikh) nufaili ki bayan karda hai (Qa'nabi ki nahin).
697,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi Namaz padh raha ho to kisi ko na chhodey ke uskey aagey se guzrey. jahan tak ho sakey usko rokey. agar wo inkar aur israr karey to chahiye ke uskey sath ladaai karey, beshak wo shaitan hai.''"
698,Janab Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Saeed Khudri apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi Namaz padhney lagey to chahiye ke sutrah rakh kar padhey aur uskey qarib khada ho.'' aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya.
699,Janab abu-Ubaida haajib Sulaiman kehtey hain ke maine Ata-bin-Yazid-laisi ko Namaz mein khadey dekha aur main unke aagey se guzarney laga to unhoney mujhey roka -phir (Namaz ke baad) mujh se kaha ke mujhey Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi ye kar sakta ho ke kisi ko apney aur qibley ke darmiyan mein se na guzarney dey to chahiye ke wo aisa karey.''
700,"Janab abu-Saaleh ne kaha : maine Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se jo dekha suna hai tumhein batata hun. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) Marwan ke paas gaey aur bayan kiya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahey they : ''jab tum mein se koi kisi chiz ki taraf Namaz padh raha ho, jo uskey liye logon se sutrah ho aur koi uskey aagey se guzarney ki koshish karey to uskey seeney ke aagey haath karkey usey rok dey. agar wo inkar karey to us se ladaai karey, bila-shuba wo shaitan hai.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya ke Sufiyan Sauri ne kaha : eik aadmi takabbur kartey huey merey aagey se Namaz ki haalat mein guzarta hai to main usey rok leta hun aur kabhi koi zaeef insan hota hai to usey mana nahin karta."
701,"Janab Zaid-bin-Khalid-Juhni ne unhein (basar-bin-Saeed ko) Hazrat abu-jahim (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bheja aur puchhwaya ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se namazi ke aagey se guzarney waley ke mutalliq kiya suna hai? to Hazrat abu-jahim (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''namazi ke aagey se guzarney waley ko agar maloom ho jaey ke us par kitna gunah aur azab hai to (uskey badley) usey chaalis. . . . . . khada rehna , uskey aagey se guzarney se achchha lagey.'' abu-Nazar ne kaha : na maloom aapney chaalis ke lafz ke sath din , mahina ya saal , kya farmaya?"
702,"hafs-bin-Umar ki sanad se Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aadmi ki Namaz ko tod deta hai.'' aur un dono (Abdussalam-bin-mutah'hir aur ibne-kaseer) ne Sulaiman-bin-Mughira se riwayat kartey huey kaha ke Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aadmi ki Namaz ko kaat deta hai jabke uskey samney paalaan ki pichhli lakdi ke barabar kuchh na rakha ho, gadhaa, kaalaa kutta aur aurat. mein (yani Abdullah-bin-saamat) ne kaha : kaley kuttey ki kya khasusiyat hai, surkh ho ya zard ya safed? unhoney kaha : bhatijey ! maine bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha tha jaisey ke tum ne mujh se puchha hai, to aapney farmaya tha : '' kala kutta shaitan hai.''"
703,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, usey Shoba ne marfoo zikr kiya : ''Namaz ko tod deti hai baaligha aurat aur kutta. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : usey Saeed , Hisham aur Hammam ne Qatada se, unhoney Jabir-bin-Zaid se riwayat kartey huey ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) par mauquf kiya hai."
704,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, kisi raawi ne kaha mera khayal hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kiya, farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs baghair sutrey ke Namaz padhey to kutta , khinzir , yahudi , majusi aur aurat uski Namaz tod detey hain. magar jab ye eik pathar phainkney ke fasley se guzrein to Namaz ke tootney se kifaayat rehti hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : merey dil mein is riwayat ke baarey mein kuch ( taraddud/sankoch ( sa hai. maine Ibrahim waghaira se uska muzaakira kiya to kisi ne usey Hisham se riwayat nahin kiya, na usko pahchanta tha. aur na maine kisi ko dekha jo usey Hisham se bayan karta ho. aur mera khayal hai ke ye ibne-abi Sameena ka weham hai. aur is mein munkir hissey ''majusi, pathar phainkney ka fasla aur khinzir'' ka bayan hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : maine ye hadees sirf Muhammad-bin-Ismaaeel Basri se suni hai aur mera khayal hai ke usey weham hua hai kyonkey wo apney hifz se bayan karta tha."
705,"Janab Yazid-bin-namraan ne bayan kiya ke maine tabuk main eik aadmi dekha jo lunja tha. (yani chal phir na sakta tha.) usney bataya ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke aagey se guzra tha, mein gadhey par Sawar tha aur aap Namaz padh rahey they. aapney kaha : ''aey Allah ! uskey qadam kaat dey.'' chunanche uskey baad se main apney qadmon par nahin chal saka hun."
706,"Saeed ne mazkura sanad ke sath usi ke ham-maani bayan kiya aur mazeed kaha : ''isney hamari Namaz tod di, Allah uskey qadam tod dey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : abu-Mushir ne Saeed se riwayat kiya to usney sirf is qadr kaha : ''isney hamari Namaz tod di.''"
707,"Saeed-bin-ghazawaan apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney hajj ko jatey huey tabuk mein padaaw kiya. usney eik lunja aadmi dekha ( jo chal na sakta tha ( usney uski kaifiyat poochhi to usney kaha mein tumhein batata hun magar jab tak tujhey ye maloom rahey ke main zinda hun kisi ko batana nahin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tabuk main eik khajoor taley padaaw kiye huey they. aapney farmaya : ''ye hamara qibla hai.'' phir aap uski taraf Namaz padhney lagey , chunanche main bhaagtaa hua aaya jabke main ladka hi tha, yahan tak ke aap ke aur aap ke sutrey ke darmiyan mein se guzar gaya. aapney kaha : ''usney hamari Namaz todi, Allah uskey qadam tod dey.'' chunanche us din se aaj tak main in par khada nahin ho saka hun."
708,"عَمْرِو بْنِ شُعَيْبٍ عَنْ أَبِيهِ عَنْ جَدِّهِ ke wastey se marwi (bayan) hai ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath maqam ''saniya azaakhir'' mein padaaw kiya. Namaz ka waqt ho gaya to aapney eik deewar ki taraf munh karkey Namaz padhi aur ham aap ke peechhey they. bakri ka eik bachcha aaya aur aap ke aagey se guzarney laga magar aap usey roktey rahey, yahan tak ke aap ka pet deewar se ja laga aur wo bachcha aap ke peechhey se guzar gaya. Musaddad ke alfaz yehi they ya isi tarah ke qarib ."
709,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padh rahey they ke bheed ka eik bachcha aap ke aagey se guzarney laga magar aap usey hataatey rahey.
710,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke qibley ke darmiyan hua karti thi, Shoba ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke unhoney kaha : aur main haiz se hoti thi. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is hadees ko Zohri , Ata , abu-Bakar-bin-hafs, Hisham-bin-Urwa, iraak-bin-Malik, Abul-Aswad aur Tameem-bin-Salma ne riwayat kiya hai. aur ye sab Urwa se wo Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se bayan kartey hain jabkey Ibrahim ba-waasta Aswad Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se aur Abul-Zuha b-waasta Masruq Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se aur Qasim-bin-Muhammad aur abu-Salma (barahe-rast) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se bayan kartey hain. in hazraat ne ye jumla zikr nahin kiya, aur main haiz se hoti thi.''"
711,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko apni Namaz padhtey aur wo aap ke aur qibley ke darmiyan bistar par hoti thin jis par ke aap sotay they, yahan tak ke jab aap witr padhna chahtey to unhen jagaa detey. tab wo (bhi uth kar) witr padh letin ."
712,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke tum logon ne bura kiya ke hamein (yani aurton ko) gadhey aur kuttey ke barabar kar diya hai. bila-shuba maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padhtey aur main aap ke samney leti hui hoti thi. aap jab sajda karna chahtey to merey paon ko daba detey, main apney paon samet leti phir aap sajda kartey."
713,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main soi hui hoti aur merey paon Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney hotey jabkey aap raat ko Namaz padh rahey hotey they. jab aap sajda karna chahtey to merey paon par maartey, main unhen samet leti phir aap sajda kartey."
714,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke main soti aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qibla rukh arz mein leti hui hoti thi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padhtey rehtey aur main aap ke samney hoti. jab aap witr padhna chahtey. ... Usman ne izafa kiya. ... aap mujhey daba detey, phir (Qaanabi aur Usman ( dono riwayat mein muttafiq hain ke aap farmatey : ''(Aaisha !) eik taraf ho jao.''"
715,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke main eik gadhey par Sawar ho kar aaya. (doosri sanad sey) ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney kaha ke main eik gadhi par Sawar ho kar aaya aur main un dino baligh hone ke qarib tha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Mina mein logon ko Namaz padha rahey they, chunanche main saf ke kuch hissey ke aagey se guzra, phir main utra aur gadhi ko chhod diya. wo charney lagi aur main saf mein shamil ho gaya aur kisi ne mujh par aetraz na kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : ye alfaz (ustaad) Qaanabi ke hain aur (ustaad Usman-bin-abi-Sheba ke alfaz sey) ziyada kamil hain. Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke main is masley mein dheel chhodna samajhta hun jabkey Namaz khadi ho chuki ho."
716,"Janab Abul-Sahba'a bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki majlis mein hamara muzaakra hua ke kis chiz se Namaz toot'ti hai to aan-janaab ne bayan kiya ke main aur bani-abdul-Muttalib ka eik ladka gadhey par Sawar ho kar aaye jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padha rahey they, chunanche wo utra aur main bhi aur ham ne gadhey ko saf ke aagey chhod diya, to aapney uski koi parwa na ki . aur bani-abdul-Muttalib ki do bachchiyaan aayin aur saf mein dakhil ho gaeen aapney unki bhi koi parwa na ki ."
717,Mansoor ne yehi hadees apni sanad se riwayat ki . kaha ke bani-abdul-Muttalib ki do ladkiyan ladti hui aayin to aapney un dono ko pakad liya . ... Usman ne kaha : aapney un dono ko juda kar diya. ... aur Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha unhein eik dusri se chhuda diya aur uski koi parwa na ki.
718,Hazrat fazal-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye aur ham bahir apney dehat mein they aur aap ke sath Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. aapney sehra mein Namaz padhi aap ke samney sutrah na tha. hamari gadhi aur kutiyaa aap ke samney khel rahi thin aur aapney uski koi parwa na ki.
719,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Namaz ko koi chiz nahin todti aur jahan tak mumkin ho (aagey se guzarney wali cheez ko) hataao, bila-shuba wo shaitan hai.''"
720,"Janab Abul-Wadaak bayan kartey hain ke Quraish ka eik naujawan Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke aagey se guzarney laga , jabke wo Namaz padh rahey they, to unhoney usko roka . wo phir aaya, to unhoney usey roka . teen dafa aisa hi hua . jab wo Namaz se farigh huye, to farmaya : Namaz ko koi cheez nahin todti magar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''(guzarney waley ko) jahan tak ho sakey roko , bila-shuba wo shaitan hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se do hadisein eik doosrey ke khilaf manqul hon to dekha jata hai ke aap ke as-haab kiram (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ne aap ke baad kya amal ikhtiyar kiya tha?"
721,"Janab Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke jab aap Namaz shuru kartey to apney dono haathon ko uthatey yahan tak ke aap ke kandhon ke barabar aa jatey aur jab rukoo karna chahtey (to apney dono haath uthatey) aur aisey hi rukoo se sar uthaney ke baad kartey. aur Sufiyan ne eik baar kaha : aur jab apna sar uthatey. aur aksar oqaat unke lafz hotey they : (وبعد يرفع رأسه من الركوع) ''yani rukoo se sar uthaney ke baad kartey.'' aur sajdon ke darmiyan haath na uthaya kartey they."
722,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to apney dono haath buland kartey yahan tak ke wo kandhon ke barabar aa jatey. phir (الله اكبر) kehtey aur unhein wesay hi uthatey aur rukoo kartey phir jab apni kamar uthana chahtey to apney haathon ko buland kartey , yahan tak ke aap ke kandhon ke barabar aa jatey phir kehtey : (سمع الله لمن حمده) aur sajdon mein apney haath na uthatey aur rukoo se pehley her takbir mein apney haath uthatey, yahan tak ke aap ki Namaz puri ho jati."
723,"Janab abdul-jabbaar-bin-wayal-bin-hajar bayan kartey hain ke main nau-umr ladka tha, apney walid ki Namaz ko na samajhta tha, to mujhey wayel-bin-Alqama ne merey walid-wayal-bin-hajar (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kiya, unhoney kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi to aap jab takbir kehtey to apney dono haath uthatey . . . . . bataya ke . . . . . phir aapney apna kapda lapet liya , phir apney bayen haath ko apney dayen se pakda aur apney haathon ko apney kapdey mein kar liya . . . . . kaha ke . ... jab rukoo karna chahtey to apney dono haathon ko (kapdey se bahir) nikaltey phir unhein ooper uthatey . aur jab rukoo se apna sar uthana chahtey to apney dono haathon ko usi tarah uthatey. phir aapney sajda kiya aur apney chehrey ko apni hatheliyon ke darmiyan mein rakha . aur jab sajdon se sar uthatey to bhi apney dono haath uthatey, yahan tak ke aap apni Namaz se farigh ho gaey. Muhammad (bin-jahaara) ne kaha ke maine ye hadees Hasan-bin-abi-abul-hasan (Basri) se zikr ki to unhoney kaha : yehi hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz , jisney usey ikhtiyar kiya, ikhtiyar kiya aur jisney usey chhod diya, chhod diya. Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is hadees ko Hammam ne ibne-juhada se riwayat kiya to us mein sajdon se uth kar raful-yadain ka zikr nahin kiya."
724,"Janab abdul-jabbaar-bin-wayal apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke jab aap Namaz ke liye khadey huey to aapney apney dono haath uthaey yahan tak ke wo kandhon ke muqabil ho gaey aur angoothey kanon ke barabar aagey. phir  ''الله اكبر'' kaha ."
725,"Janab abdul-jabbaar-bin-wayal ne kaha ke mujh se merey ehale-khana ne merey walid (waial-bin-hajar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kiya, merey walid ne un se bayan kiya ke usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha tha ke wo takbir ke sath haath uthatey they."
726,"Hazrat wayal-bin-hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine kaha : main bil-zaroor Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz dekhun ga ke aap kaisey padhtey hain. unhoney bayan kiya : chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huye, qibley ki taraf rukh kiya aur (الله اكبر) kaha, phir apney dono haath uthaey yahan tak ke aap ke kanon ke barabar aa gaey, phir aapney apney bayen haath ko apney dayen haath se pakad liya , jab rukoo karna chaha to apney dono haath pehley ki tarah uthaey aur phir unhein apney ghutnon par rakha . jab rukoo se sar uthaya to dono haathon ko usi tarah uthaya (yani raful-yadain kiya). jab sajda kiya to apna sar zameen par apney haathon ke darmiyan usi maqam par rakha (yani sar aur haathon ka fasla itna hi tha jitna ke raful-yadain ke waqt tha). phir baithey aur apney bayen paon ko bicha liya aur apna baayan haath apni baain raan par rakha aur dayen haath ki kohni ko daain raan se alehda aur ooncha rakha . apni do ungliyon (chhanguli aur sath wali) ko band kar liya aur baqi se halqa bana liya . (Musaddad kehtey hain ke) maine apney shaikh Bishr ko dekha ke unhoney angoothey aur darmiyani ungli se halqa banaya aur shahadat ki ungli se ishara kiya."
727,"Janab Aasim-bin-Kulaib ne isi sanad se uska ham-maani bayan kiya aur is mein (tafsil sey) kaha ke phir apna daayan haath apney bayen haath ki pusht par rakha , yun ke wo pahunchey aur kalaai par bhi aa gaya. is riwayat mein mazeed kaha ke main uskey baad sakht sardi ke mausam mein bhi aap ke yahan aaya . maine logon ko dekha ke wo bahut kapdey odhey huey they. unke haath (raful-yadain kartey huey) kapdon ke nichey se harkat kartey they."
728,Hazrat wayal-bin-hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aapney jab Namaz shuru ki to apney dono haathon ko kanon ke barabar tak uthaya. kaha ke main phir un (Sahaba) ke paas aaya maine Sahaba kiram ko dekha ke wo Namaz shuru kartey huey apney haathon ko seenon tak uthatey they aur wo jubbey aur kambal odhey huey they.
729,"Hazrat wayal-bin-hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua , sardi ka mausam tha, maine Sahaba kiram ko dekha ke wo kapdon ke andar se Namaz mein apney haath uthatey they. (yani raful-yadain kartey they.)"
730,"Janab Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-Ata bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ko suna, unhoney as-haabe-Rasul (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mein se das afrad ki jamaat mein kaha . ... aur un mein abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. ... ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ke mutalliq tum sab se ziyada ba-khabar hun, unhoney kaha : kaisey? qasam Allah ki ! tum koi ham se ziyada Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ittiba kerney waley to nahin ho ya hamari nisbat ziyada purani sohbat waley to nahin ho. unhoney kaha : kyon nahin. Sahaba ne kaha : achha to bayan karo. (abu-Hameed ne) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Namaz ke liye khadey hotey apney dono haathon ko uthatey , yahan tak ke wo aap ke kandhon ke barabar aa jatey , phir (الله اكبر) kehtey, yahan tak ke her haddi apni-apni jagah par theek tarah se tik jati. phir aap qirat farmatey. phir (الله اكبر) kehtey aur apney dono haath uthatey, yahan tak ke dono kandhon ke barabar aa jatey. phir rukoo kartey aur apni hatheliyon ko ghutnon par rakhtey aur aetidaal aur sukoon se rukoo kartey, na sar ko jhukaatey aur na ooper uthaey hotey , phir rukoo se sar uthatey , to ( سمع الله لمن حمده) kehtey, phir apney haath uthatey , yahan tak ke kandhon ke barabar aa jatey. ... aur khoob aetidaal aur sukoon se khadey hotey. phir (الله اكبر) kehtey aur zameen ki taraf jhuktey aur (sajdey mein) apney haathon ko apney pahluon se door rakhtay. phir apna sar uthatey aur apna baayan paon mod letey aur uskey ooper baith jatey. aur sajdey mein apney paon ki ungliyan (qibla rukh) mod letey , phir (doosra) sajda kartey , phir (الله اكبر) keh kar apna sar uthatey aur apna baayan paon mod kar us par baith jatey , yahan tak ke her haddi apni-apni jagah par lot aati. phir dusri rakaat mein bhi aisey hi kartey. phir jab do rakaaton se (teesri ke liye) uthtey to apney haathon ko uthatey, yahan tak ke aap ke kandhon ke barabar aa jatey jaisey ke Namaz shuru kartey waqt uthaey they. (yani raful-yadain kartey) phir baqiya Namaz mein usi tarah kartey yahan tak ke jab is sajde mein hotey jis mein salam kehna hota (to tashahud mein) apney bayen paon ko aagey kar detey aur bayen peeth ke hissey par baith jatey. un sab Sahaba ne kaha : aapney sach farmaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisey hi Namaz padha kartey they."
731,"Janab Muhammad-bin-Amr-aamiri bayan kartey hain ke main as-haabe Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki eik majlis mein tha, to wahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ka zikr shuru ho gaya. Hazrat abu-Humed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha . ... aur mazkura hadees ka kuch hissey bayan kiya. is mein kaha : aap jab rukoo kartey to apni hatheliyon se apney ghutnon ko pakad letey aur apni ungliyon ko khol letey aur apni kamar ko dohra kartey. sar na to uthaya hota aur na apney rukhsaar ko idhar-udhar moda hota (balke sidha qibla rukh hota) . ... mazeed kaha . ... aur jab do rakaaton ke baad baithtey to apney bayen paon ke talwey par baithtey aur dayen ko khada kar letey. aur jab chauthi rakaat mein baithtey to apni baain raan ko zameen par tikaa detey aur apney dono paon ko eik janib mein nikal letey."
732,"Janab Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-Ata se usi ki manind riwayat hai, kaha : aur jab sajda kartey to apney dono haathon ko rakhtey , us haalat mein ke zameen par bichey huey na hotey aur na simte huey . aur ungliyon ka rukh sidha qibley ki taraf hota."
733,"Janab Abbas ya Ayash-bin-Sahal Saaidi se riwayat hai ke wo eik majlis mein hazir they jis mein unke walid bhi maujud they aur wo sahabi Rasool they aur usi tarah us majlis mein Hazrat Abu-Huraira , abu-Humaid Saaidi aur abu-Usaid (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) bhi they. ( Esa-bin-Abdullah ne ( yehi khabar bayan ki, kisi qadr kami beshi ke sath . aur is mein kaha : phir aapney apna sar uthaya yani rukoo sey, to kaha : ( سَمِعَ اللَّهُ لِمَنْ حَمِدَهُ , اللَّهُمَّ رَبَّنَا لَكَ الْحَمْدُ (aur apney dono haath uthaey . phir kaha : ( الله اكبر ( phir sajda kiya aur apni hatheliyon , ghutnon aur panjon ko zameen par tikaaya , phir ( الله اكبر ( kaha aur baith gaey aur peeth par baithey (tawruk kiya) aur doosrey qadam ko khada kiya, phir (الله اكبر) kaha aur (doosra) sajda kiya, phir (الله اكبر) kaha aur khadey ho gaey magar tawruk nahin kiya (yani peeth par na bethey) . ... aur hadees bayan ki . kaha ke do rakaat ke baad baith gaey, yahan tak ke jab qiyam ke liye uthney ka irada kiya to takbir keh kar khadey ho gaey aur dusri do rakatein padhein aur tashahud mein tawruk ka zikr nahin kiya."
734,"Janab Abbas-bin-Sahal ne kaha ke hazraat abu-Humed , abu-Usaid , Sahal-bin-Saad aur Muhammad-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) jama they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ka zikr aa gaya to Hazrat abu-Humed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ke baarey mein tum sab se ziyada aagah hun. aur is hadees mein se kuch hissey bayan kiya. kaha : phir rukoo kiya aur apney haathon ko apney ghutnon par rakha goya unhen pakdey huey hon aur apney haathon ko taant banaya ( jo ke kamaan par hota hai) aur apney haathon ko apney pahluon se door rakha . ... bayan kiya ke . ... phir sajda kiya to apni naak aur peshani ko zameen par tikaaya aur apney haathon ko apney pahluon se door rakha aur apney dono haathon ko apney kandhon ke barabar rakha . phir apna sar uthaya yahan tak ke her haddi apni jagah par aa gaee , yahan tak ke (sajdon sey) farigh ho gaey. phir baithey aur apney bayen paon ko bichha liya aur apney dayen paon ki ungliyon ka rukh qible ki taraf kar diya aur apni daain hatheli ko apney dayen ghutney par rakha aur baain ko bayen ghutney par , aur apni ungli se ishara kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is hadees ko utba-bin-abi-hakim ne Abdullah-bin-Eisa se unhoney Abbas-bin-Sahal se riwayat kiya magar tawruk ( peeth par bethney (ka zikr nahin kiya aur hadees fulaih ki manind riwayat ki jabkey Hasan-bin-hur ne baithney ka andaz fulaih aur Utba ki hadees ki tarah bayan kiya."
735,"Janab Abbas-bin-Sahal-saaidi ne Hazrat abu-Humed (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadees riwayat ki aur kaha : jab sajda kiya to apni raanon ko kushada rakha aur pet ko raanon se na lagaya. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : aur is hadees ko ibne-mubarak ne riwayat kiya to kaha : (اخبرنا Fuleh : سمعت عباس ابن سهل يحدث) magar main isko yaad nahin rakh saka , isliye usney mujhey ye hadees bayan ki, mera (ibne-mubarak ka ( khayal hai ke unhoney apney shaikh ka naam Eisa-bin-Abdullah bataya aur unhoney Abbas-bin-Sahal se suna . unhoney kaha ke main abu-Humaid Saaidi ke paas hazir tha. ... aur ye hadees bayan ki."
736,Janab abdul-jabbaar-bin-wayal apney walid se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se raawi hain. is hadees mein bayan kiya ke . ... jab sajda kiya to aap ke dono ghutney zameen par dono hatheliyon ke padney se pehley padey aur jab sajda kiya to apni peshani ko dono haathon ke darmiyan rakha aur apni baghlon se bhi door kiya.  Hajjaj ne kaha ke Hammam ne kaha : «(حدثنا شقيق حدثني عاصم بن كليب an Abeeh an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم)» usi ke misl (jaisi) riwayat ki . Muhammad-bin-juhada aur Shaqiq mein se kisi eik ki riwayat mein hai. ... aur mera ghalib guman hai ke Muhammad-bin-juhada ki hadees hai ke aap jab uthtey to apney ghutnon par uthtey aur apni raanon par tek lagatey.
737,Janab abdul-jabbaar-bi-wayal ! apney walid se riwayat kartey hain. kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap Namaz mein apney anguthon ko kanon ki lo tak ooncha kartey they.
738,"Janab abu-Bakar-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Haris-bin-Hisham Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Namaz ke liye takbir kehtey to apney dono haathon ko kandhon ke barabar ley jatey aur jab rukoo kartey to isi tarah kartey. aur jab (rukoo sey) sajdey ke liye sar uthatey to isi tarah kartey aur jab do rakaaton ke baad (teesri ke liye) uthtey to isi tarah kartey. (yani raful-yadain kartey.)"
739,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed apni sanad se Memun makki se raawi hai ke unhoney Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhoney logon ko Namaz padhaai ke wo apney haathon se isharay kartey they (yani raful-yadain kartey). jab wo Namaz ke liye khadey hotey, jab rukoo kartey , jab sajda kartey aur jab qiyam ke liye uthtey aur qiyam kartey to apney haathon se isharay kartey they. chunanche main Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke paas gaya aur un se kaha ke maine ibne-Zubair ko is-is tarah Namaz padhtey dekha hai ke unki tarah kisi aur ko Namaz padhtey huey nahin dekha aur unhein un isharon (raful-yadain) ki tafsil batai to Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne jawaaban kaha : agar tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz dekhna pasand kartey ho, to Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ki Namaz ki iqtidaa karo."
740,"Janab nazar-bin-Kasir yani sa'di ne bayan kiya ke Janab Abdullah-bin-taaoos (Taabai) ne masjide-khaif mein merey pehlu mein Namaz padhi. wo jab pehla sajda kar letey aur us se apna sar uthatey to apney dono haathon ko apney chehrey ke samney uthatey. mujhey unka ye amal munkir (ajeeb aur ghalat) mehsoos hua, to maine Wuhaib-bin-Khalid ko unka ye amal bataya. Janab Wuhaib ne un se kaha ke aap aisa kartey hain jo maine kisi ko kartey nahin dekha. to Abdullah-bin-taaoos ne kaha : maine apney walid ko ye kartey dekha aur merey walid ne kaha ke maine Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko ye kartey dekha aur main nahin janta magar unhoney kaha ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke wo ye kartey they."
741,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke wo jab Namaz shuru kartey to ( الله اكبر ( kehtey aur apney dono haathon ko uthatey (yani raful-yadain kartey (aur ( aisey hi ( jab rukoo ko jatey aur jab ( rukoo se uthtey aur )(سمع الله لمن حمده) kehtey . aur jab do rakaaton se (teesri ke liye) uthtey to apney dono haath uthatey. aur wo apna ye amal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf mansoob kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : sahih ye hai ke ye Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka qaul hai, marfoo hadees nahin. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : aur baqiya ne is hadees ka pehla hissey Ubaidullah se bayan kiya to usey marfoo zikr kiya (baghair iskey ke aapney do rakaaton se uth kar raful-yadain kiya) magar abdul-wahaab Saqafi ne Ubaidullah se riwayat kiya to usey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) par moquf kiya aur is mein kaha : jab do rakatein padh kar uthtey to apney haathon ko apni chhaatiyon tak uthatey. aur yehi sahih hai. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha ke usey Leis-bin-Saad , Malik , Ayub aur ibne-Juraij ne moquf hi riwayat kiya hai. sirf Hammad-bin-Salma ne ba-waasta Ayub marfoo bayan kiya. Ayub aur Malik ne do sajdon (yani rakaaton ( se uth kar raful-yadain ka zikr nahin kiya, sirf Leis ne zikr kiya hai. ibne-Juraij ne is mein kaha ke maine Naafe se puchha : kya Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) pehli baar raful-yadain mein apney haath ziyada unchey uthatey they? unhoney kaha : nahin, sab mein barabar hi uthatey they. maine kaha : mujhey karkey dikhao , to unhoney chhaatiyon tak uthaey ya is se zara kam hi ."
742,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke jab wo Namaz shuru kartey to apney haathon ko kandhon ke barabar tak ooncha kartey. aur jab rukoo se sar uthatey to unhein zara kam ooncha kartey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : jahan tak mujhey maloom hai, haathon ko zara kam ooncha uthaney ka zikr Malik ke ilawa kisi aur ne nahin kiya."
743,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab do rakatein padh kar uthtey to (الله اكبر) kehtey aur apney dono haathon ko uthatey.
744,"Saiyedna Ali-bin-abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aap jab farz Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to (الله اكبر) kehtey aur apney dono haathon ko kandhon tak uthatey . aur jab apni qirat puri kar letey aur rukoo karna chahtey to isi tarah haath uthatey aur jab rukoo se uthtey to isi tarah kartey. aur Namaz mein baithey huey honey ki haalat mein aap raful-yadain na kartey they aur jab do rakatein padh kar uthtey to apney haath uthatey aur (الله اكبر) kehtey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Hazrat abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ki wo hadees , jis mein unhoney Namaz nabawi ki tafsil bayan farmai hai, us mein hai ke aap jab do rakaaton ke baad uthtey to (الله اكبر) kehtey aur apney dono haath uthatey, yahan tak ke aap ke kandhon ke barabar aa jatey jaisey ke shuru Namaz ke waqt takbir kehtey they."
745,"Hazrat Malik-bin-huwairis (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke jab aap takbir (tahreema) kehtey to raful-yadain kartey, aur jab rukoo ko jatey aur jab rukoo se sar uthatey to bhi apney haath uthatey aur wo aap ki kanon ki luon tak pahunch jatey. ( . . . . . ya . . . . . kanon ke ooper ke hissey tak pahunch jatey they.)"
746,"Janab basheer-bin-nuhaik kehtey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke aagey hota to main aap ki baghlein dekh sakta tha. (yani aap ke haath raful-yadain ke waqt numaya taur par baghlon se alehda , door aur unchey hotey they.) ibne-Muaz ne kaha ke laahiq ne kaha : bhala Abu-Huraira Namaz mein hotey huey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se aagey kyon kar ho saktey they? Musa ne ye izafa kiya hai : (maqsad ye hai ke) jab aap takbir kehtey to haath unchey kartey they. (yani numaya taur par unchey kartey they.)"
747,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein Namaz sikhai to aapney ( الله أكبر ( kaha aur apney dono haath uthaey . jab rukoo kiya to dono haathon ko jod kar ghutnon mein rakh liya . (yani tatbeeq ki.) Hazrat Saad-bin-abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye khabar pahunchi to kaha : merey bhai ne sach kaha . ham ye amal kiya kartey they, phir hamein iska hukm diya gaya. yani ghutney pakadney ka."
748,"Janab Alqama se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha, Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya main tumhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz na padh kar dikhaon? chunanche unhoney Namaz padhi aur apney haath sirf eik hi baar uthaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : ye hadees eik lambi hadees se mukhtasar hai aur un alfaz mein sahih nahin hai."
749,"Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Namaz shuru kartey to apney dono haath apney kanon tak uthatey , phir dobara na uthatey."
750,"Abdullah-bin-Muhammad Zohri ki sanad sey, Yazid se shareek ki manind marwi (bayan) hai aur (ثم لا يعود) ke lafz zikr nahin kiye. (yani ''phir dobara na uthatey'' ke lafz naqal nahin kiye.) Sufiyan ne kaha : baad mein koofa mein ham ko (ثم لا يعود) ke lafz bayan kiye. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is hadees ko hasheem , Khalid aur ibne-Idrees ne Yazid se riwayat kiya hai magar un hazraat ne  (لا يعود) ka lafz riwayat nahin kiya hai."
751,Janab Sufiyan ne isi sanad se is hadees ko bayan kiya kaha isliye aapney pehli hi baar apney haath uthaey. aur baaz ne kaha : eik hi baar uthaey.
752,Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aapney Namaz shuru kartey huey apney haath uthaey . phir farigh honey tak nahin uthaey. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : ye hadees sahih nahin hai.
753,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Namaz mein dakhil hotey to apney haath lambey karkey uthatey.
754,Hazrat ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke) Namaz mein) qadmon ko barabar rakhna aur haath par haath rakhna sunnat hai.
755,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke wo Namaz padh rahey they aur apney bayen haath ko dayen par rakhey huey they, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dekha to unke dayen haath ko bayen ke ooper kar diya."
756,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Namaz mein hatheli ko hatheli par naaf ke nichey rakhna sunnat hai.
757,"Janab-ibne-Jarir zabi apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, wo kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhoney apney bayen haath ko dayen haath se pahunchey (kalaai) ke paas se (yani jod ke paas sey) pakad rakha tha aur wo naaf se ooper they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Janab Saeed-bin-Jubair sey, ''naaf se ooper'' marwi (bayan) hai. aur abu-Mujliz ne ''naaf se neeche'' kaha hai. aur Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi ''naaf se neechey'' hi riwayat ki gaee hai. magar qawi nahin hai."
758,"Janab abu-Wayal ne kaha ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Namaz mein hatheliyon ko hatheliyon se naaf ke nichey se pakadna hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke maine Imam Ahmed-bin-Hanbal (Rahimahullah) ko suna, wo (mazkura asar ke eik raawi) Abdur-Rehman koofi ko zaeef kehtey they."
759,"Janab Taaus (bin-kaisaan yamaani, (Taabai)) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz ke dauran mein apna daayan haath bayen ke ooper rakhtey aur unhein apney seeney par baandha kartey they."
760,"Saiyedna Ali-bin-Abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to ( الله أكبر ( kehtey phir ye dua padhtey : (وَجَّهْتُ وَجْهِيَ لِلَّذِي فَطَرَ السَّمَوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضَ . .  الخ) ''maine apna chehra us zaat ki taraf kar liya hai jisney aasmano aur zameen ko paida kiya hai. main usi ki taraf yaksoo hun, usi ka Mutee farman hun, aur main mushrikon mein se nahin hun. bila-shuba meri Namaz , meri qurbani , mera jeena aur marna Allah-Rabbul-Aalameen hi ke liye hai. uska koi sajhi nahin hai. mujhey isi ka hukm diya gaya hai aur main awwaleen itaat guzaaron mein se hun. aey Allah ! to hi badshah hai, terey siwa koi aur mabud nahin. to mera paalanhaar hai aur main tera banda hun. maine apni jaan par ziyadti ki hai. mujhey apney gunahon ka aetraaf hai. isliye merey sab gunah maaf farma dey. terey siwa gunahon ko aur koi maaf nahin kar sakta. meri umda akhlaq aur aadaat ki taraf rehnumai farma . achhey akhlaq aur aadaat ki taufiq tujhi se mil sakti hai. burey akhlaq aur aadaat mujh se door farma dey . buri aadaton ko to hi pher sakta hai. main terey darbar mein hazir hun. phir hazir hun. tera Mutee farman hun phir tera Mutee farman hun. khair aur bhalai sari ki sari terey hi haath mein hai aur kisi shar ki nisbat teri taraf nahin hai. main tera hun aur mera thikana teri hi taraf hai. to badi barkaton wala aur raf'aton wala hai aur main tujh se maghfirat chahta hun aur teri janib tauba kar raha hun.'' aur jab rukoo kartey to yun kehtey : ( اللَّهُمَّ لَكَ رَكَعْتُ . . . . . الخ ) ''aey Allah ! main terey liye jhuk gaya hun, tujh par emaan laya hun aur tera Mutee hun. merey kaan , meri aankhen , meri haddiyan , goodaa aur putthey sab hi terey samney aajizi ka mazahar hain.'' aur jab rukoo se sar uthatey to farmatey : (سَمِعَ اللَّهُ لِمَنْ حَمِدَهُ رَبَّنَا وَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ . . . . الخ ) ''Allah ne uski baat sun li jisney uski hamd ki. aey hamarey Rab ! aur teri hi tareef hai aasmano aur zameen bhar , aur unka beech bhar kar aur uskey baad is chiz ke bharaaw ke barabar jo to chahey.'' aur jab sajda kartey to yun kehtey :(اللَّهُمَّ لَكَ سَجَدْتُ . . . . الخ) ''aey Allah ! main terey huzur sajda rez hun, tujh par emaan laya hun aur tera Mutee farman hun. merey chehrey ne us zaat ke liye sajda kiya jisney isko paida kiya, isey shakal di aur behtareen shakal di aur is mein kaan aur aankhen banaeen. badi barkaton wala hai Allah jo behtareen paida kerney wala hai.'' aur jab Namaz se salam phertey , to ye dua kartey : (اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْلِي maa قَدَّمْتُ . . . . الخ) ''aey Allah ! merey sab gunah aur meri tamam taqseerein (kamiyan) maaf farma dey , jo main pehley kar chuka aur jo maine baad mein kin , jo chupey huey kin aur jo zahir mein kin aur jo main had se badha raha aur jin ka to mujh se ziyada ba-khabar hai. to hi (neki aur khair mein) aagey kerney wala aur peechhey kerney wala hai. terey siwa koi mabud nahin.''"
761,"Hazrat Ali-bin-Abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap jab farz Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to ( الله أكبر ( kehtey aur apney dono haathon ko kandhon ke barabar ooncha kartey (raful-yadain kartey (aur qirat mukammal kar leney par jab rukoo ko jatey to aisey hi (raful-yadain) kartey aur rukoo se uth kar bhi aisey hi (raful-yadain) kartey. aur aap apni Namaz mein jab baithey huey hotey to haath na uthatey aur jab do rakaaton se uthtey to isi tarah raful-yadain kartey aur) الله أكبر ( kehtey aur dua kartey jaisey ke Abdul-Azeez ki) sabiqa ( hadees mein bayan hua hai. us mein alfaz ki kuch kami beshi hai aur ye alfaz zikr nahin kiye yani ( والخير كله في يديك والشر ليس إليك (aur us riwayat par izafa kartey huey ye kaha ke jab Namaz se phirtey to ye dua kartey : ( اللهم اغفرلي قدمت وأخرت w أسررت وأعلنت أنت إلهي la إله إلا أنت ) ''aey Allah ! merey gunah maaf farma dey jo maine pehley kiye , jo baad mein kiye , jo poshida kiye jo zahir kiye , to mera mabud hai, terey siwa aur koi mabud nahin.''"
762,Shoaib-bin-abi-Hamza bayan kartey hain ke mujhey ibne-Mankadr aur ibne-abi Farwa waghaira Madina ke faqihon ne kaha ke jab tum ye dua : ( وجهت وجهي . ... الخ ( padho to ( وأنا أول المسلمين ( ki bajaey (وأنا من المسلمين) kaha karo.
763,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik aadmi Namaz ke liye aaya aur uski saans chadhi hui thi. usney kaha : (الله أكبر الحمد لله حمدا كثيرا طيبا مباركا فيه) ''Allah sab se bada hai. hamd aur sanaa Allah hi ke liye hai, bahut si hamd, paak, pakizah aur ba-barkat.'' jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz mukammal kar li to puchha : ''tum mein se kis ne ye kalimaat kahein they aur usney koi buri baat nahin kahi.'' to eik shakhs bola : main hun, aey Allah ke Rasool ! main aaya aur meri saans phooli hui thi to maine ye alfaz keh diye. aapney farmaya : ''bila-shuba maine baara (12) farishton ko dekha hai ke wo un kalimaat ki taraf jaldi-jaldi badh rahey hain ke kaun unko lekar Allah ke huzur pahunchta hai.'' Humaid ne is riwayat mein is qadr mazeed kaha ke (aapney farmaya :) ''aur jab tum mein se koi Namaz ke liye aaye to usi tarah chalta aaye jaisey ke chala karta hai. jo pa ley wo padh ley aur jo guzar jaey uski qaza kar ley.''"
764,"Janab ibne-Jubair-bin-Mut'im apney walid (Jubair-bin-Mut'im ( se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik Namaz padhtey dekha, Amr ne kaha : mujhey nahin maloom ke ye kaun si Namaz thi. ... to aapney teen baar kaha : ( الله أكبر كبيرا , الله أكبر كبيرا , الله أكبر كبيرا , والحمد لله كثيرا , والحمد لله كثيرا , والحمد لله كثيرا , وسبحان الله بكرة وأصيلا ) ''Allah sab se bada aur bahut bada hai, Allah sab se bada aur bahut bada hai, Allah sab se bada hai aur bahut bada hai aur hamd Allah hi ki hai, bahut ziyada , hamd Allah hi ki hai bahut ziyada , hamd Allah hi ki hai bahut ziyada. aur wo sab kamiyon se paak hai. subah aur shaam uski ye taaref hai.''  aur baad mein ye kalmaat bhi padhtey :) (أعوذ بالله من الشيطان من نفخه ونفثه وهمزه) ''main Allah ki panah chahta hun shaitan ke dam , phunk aur jinnon se.'' (Janab Amr-bin-Murra ne in alfaz ki shrah mein) kaha ke (نفث) se murad fizul aue bekar qism ki she'r aur shaeyri hai. (نفخ) ka mafhoom takabbur ki angekhat hai aur (همز) ka maani junoon hai."
765,"Janab Naafe-bin-Jubair apney walid (Jubair-bin Mut'im) se bayan kartey hain, kaha ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap nafl Namaz mein mazkura baala dua padhtey they."
766,"Janab Aasim-bin-Humaid kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apna qiyam (tahajjud) kis chiz se shuru farmaya kartey they? unhoney kaha : tum ne mujh se wo baat poochhi hai jo tum se pehley kisi ne nahin poochhi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ( Namaz ke liye ( khadey hotey to kehtey ( الله اكبر ( das baar ( الحمد الله ( das baar , phir (سبحان الله) das baar (لا إله إلا اللہ) das baar (استغفر الله) das baar aur (ye dua) padhtey : ( اللهم اغفرلي واهدني وارزقني وعافني ) ''aey Allah ! mujhey bakhsh dey , mujhey hidayat dey , mujhey rizq inayat farma aur mujhey aaram aur rahat se behrawar farma.'' aur aap qiyamat ke roz (maidane-hashr mein) khadey honey ki tangi se panah maangtey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : is hadees ko Khalid-bin-Ma'daan ne Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se ba-waasta Rabeea Jarshi , mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kiya hai."
767,"Janab abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko uthtey to apni Namaz kis chiz se shuru farmatey they? unhoney bataya ke aap jab raat ko uthtey aur apni Namaz shuru kartey to kehtey : ( اللَّهُمَّ رَبَّ جِبْرِيلَ وَمِيكَائِيلَ وَإِسْرَافِيلَ . ... الخ ) ''aey Allah ! Jibrael , Mekael aur Israafeel ke Rab ! aasmano aur zameen ke paida kerney waley ! sab zahir aur poshida ke janney waley ! terey bandon ke beech jo ikhtilaf hota hai to hi uska faisla karta hai. to apni khas taufiq se meri haq ki taraf rehnumai farma . be-shak to hi jisey chahey , usey sidhi raah ki rehnumai farmata hai.''"
768,Janab Ikrima (bin-Ammar Ajlii ( ne apni sanad se ( حدثني ( ki saraahat ke baghair aur is hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko qiyam farmatey to ( pehley ( ) الله أكبر ( kehtey aur phir ye dua padhtey.
769,"Janab Qaanabi Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) se bayan kartey hain ke Namaz ke shuru mein , darmiyan aur aakhir mein dua kerney mein koi harj nahin. Namaz chahey farz ho ya ghair farz."
770,"Rifa'a-bin-Raafe Zarqi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham log eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padh rahey they jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rukoo se sar uthaya aur (سمع الله لمن حمده) kaha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey eik aadmi ne kaha : ( اللهم ! ربنا ولك الحمد حمدا كثيرا طيبا مباركا فيه ) ''aey Allah ! aey hamarey Rab ! aur teri hi tareef hai, bahut sari hamd , pakizah aur ba-barkat .'' jab aap Namaz se farigh huey to puchha : ''abhi abhi kis ne ye kalimaat kahe hain? '' us aadmi ne kaha : maine aey Allah ke Rasool ! to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tehqiq maine tees se kuch ooper farishton ko dekha hai jo un kalimaat ki taraf sabqat kar rahey they ke kaun unko pehley likhtaa hai.''"
771,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to yun kehtey : ( اللَّهُمَّ لَكَ الْحَمْدُ أَنْتَ نُورُ السَّمَوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضِ . ... ) ''aey Allah ! teri hi tareef hai. to aasmano aur zameen ka Noor hai. teri hi tareef hai ke to aasmano aur zameen ki tadbeer kerney wala hai. teri hi tareef hai ke to aasmano , zameen aur jo kuch un mein hai sab ka Rab hai. to haq hai. tera farman haq hai. tera wada haq hai, tujh se mulaqat bar-haq hai. jannat bar-haq hai. dozakh bar-haq hai. qiyamat bar-haq hai. aey Allah ! main tera Mutee farman hun. tujh par emaan laya hun. mera aitimaad tujhi par hai. main teri taraf ruju kerney wala hun. (mukhalfeen haq sey) teri hi madad se jhagadta hun aur tujh hi ko apna faisal banata hun. to merey sab gunah maaf farma dey , jo maine pehley kiye , baad mein kiye , chup ke kiye aur zaahiran kiye. to hi mera mabud hai. terey siwa aur koi mabud nahin.''"
772,Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tahajjud mein) الله اكبر ( yani ( takbire-tahreema ( kehney ke baad kaha kartey they. ... aur phir mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kiya.
773,"Janab Muaz-bin-Rifa'a-bin-Raafe apney walid se bayan kartey hain, unhoney kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechey Namaz padhi to Rifaa ko chheenk aa gaee . ... (ustaad) Quteba ne Rifaa ka naam nahin liya . . . . . to maine kaha : ( الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ حَمْدًا كَثِيرًا طَيِّبًا مُبَارَكًا فِيهِ مُبَارَكًا عَلَيْهِ كَمَا يُحِبُّ رَبُّنَا وَيَرْضَی ) '' tareef Allah ki hai bahut ziyada tareef , pakizah aur ba-barkat (yani baqi rehney wali) jaisey ke hamara Rab pasand farmaai aur jis par razi aur khush ho.'' jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz se farigh huey to puchha : '' Namaz mein kaun bol raha tha?'' phir Malik ki hadees ki manind bayan kiya aur us se kamil tar bayan kiya."
774,"Janab Abdullah-bin-Aamir-bin-Rabeea apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz main eik Ansari jawan ne chheenk maari , to usney kaha : ( الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ حَمْدًا كَثِيرًا طَيِّبًا مُبَارَكًا فِيهِ حَتَّى يَرْضَى رَبُّنَا وَبَعْدَمَا يَرْضَى مِنْ أَمْرِ الدُّنْيَا وَالْآخِرَةِ ) ''tareef Allah ki, bahut sari tareef , pakizah , ba-barkat , yahan tak ke hamara Rab razi ho jaey aur duniya aur aakhirat ke maamley ke baad jis par wo razi ho.'' jab aap Namaz se farigh huey to puchha : ''kis ne kalimaat kahe hain? '' to wo naujawan khamosh raha. phir aapney farmaya : ''kis ne kalimaat kahe hain? usney koi harj ki baat nahin kahi.'' tab wo bola : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine kahe hain aur maine bhalai hi ka irada kiya hai. aapney farmaya : ''ye kalimaat Arshe-Rahmaan se warey kahin nahin rukey. (balke barahe-rast sidhey arsh tak ja pahunchey hain.) buland hai zikr uska.''"
775,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko qiyam farmatey to ( الله أكبر ( kehtey phir yun kehtey : ( سُبْحَانَكَ اللَّهُمَّ وَبِحَمْدِكَ وَتَبَارَكَ اسْمُكَ وَتَعَالَى جَدُّكَ وَلَا إِلَهَ غَيْرَكَ ) ''paak hai to aey Allah ! apni hamd ke sath tera naam badi barkat wala hai. teri shaan bahut buland hai aur terey siwa koi mabud nahin.''phir kehtey : (لا إله إلا الله) teen baar ''Allah ke siwa koi mabud nahin.'' phir kehtey : (لا إله إلا الله) teen baar ''Allah sab se bada aur bahut bada hai.'' ( أَعُوذُ بِاللَّهِ السَّمِيعِ الْعَلِيمِ مِنْ الشَّيْطَانِ الرَّجِيمِ مِنْ هَمْزِهِ وَنَفْخِهِ وَنَفْثِهِ ) ''main, Allah sunney waley janney waley ki panah chahta hun ke shaitan mardud mujh par koi Junoon ka asar daley ya mujhey takabbur par aamada karey ghalat she'r aur shaeyri ki taraf ley aaye.'' iskey baad aap qirat farmatey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya ke is hadees ke baarey mein ehale-hadees kehtey hain ke ye Ali-bin-Ali an Hasan ki sanad se mursal hai aur ye weham Jaafar ko hua hai."
776,Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye hadees Abdussalam-bin-Harab se mash'hoor nahin hai. usey sirf Talq-bin-Ghannaam ne riwayat kiya hai. budail se eik jamaat ne Namaz ki tafsil riwayat ki hai magar un mein se kisi ne bhi usey zikr nahin kiya.
777,Hazrat Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Namaz mein do saktey (thehraw) yaad hain. eik to jab Imam takbir kehta hai to qirat shuru kerney tak. aur doosra jab wo Fatiha aur surat ki qirat se farigh ho kar rukoo karna chahta hai. kaha ke Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne un (Samra) par uska inkar kiya. chunanche unhoney ye masla Madina mein Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf likh bheja to unhoney Hazrat Samra ki tasdeeq farmaee. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke is hadees ki riwayat mein Hameedut-Taweel ne bhi aisey hi kaha hai ke ''doosra sakta us waqt hai jab wo qirat se farigh ho.''
778,Hazrat Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aap do saktey farmaya kartey they. eik Namaz shuru kartey huey (qirat se pehley) aur doosrey jab puri qirat se farigh ho jatey. aur Yunus ki riwayat ke ham-maani zikr kiya.
779,"Hazrat Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke unhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se do saktey yaad hain, eik sakta jab aap takbir kehtey aur doosra sakta jab aap (غير المغضوب عليهم wla الضالين) padh kar farigh hotey. Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye yaad tha magar Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne uska inkar kya to un dono ne ye masla Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ki janib likh bheja . unhoney unke jawab mein likha ke Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye masla sahih yaad rakha hai."
780,Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke do saktey hain jo mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yaad hain. Saeed kehtey hain ke ham ne Qatada se puchha ke ye do saktey kya hain? unhoney kaha : jab Namaz shuru kartey aur jab qirat se farigh hotey . phir uskey baad kaha : aur jab (غير المغضوب عليهم wla الضالين) kehtey.
781,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Namaz ke liye takbir keh letey to takbir aur qirat shuru kerney ke darmiyan kisi had tak khamosh rehtey. maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya : merey maa baap aap par qurban ! takbir aur qirat ke darmiyan apney sukoot ke mutalliq irshad farmaeyn ke us mein aap kya padhtey hain? farmaya : ( اللَّهُمَّ بَاعِدْ بَيْنِي وَبَيْنَ خَطَايَايَ . ... الخ) ''aey Allah ! merey aur merey gunahon ke darmiyan doori kar dey , jaisey ke to ne mashriq aur maghrib ke darmiyan doori aur fasla rakha hai. aey Allah ! mujhey merey gunahon se aisey saaf farma dey jaisey ke safed kapda mail se saaf kiya jata hai. aey Allah ! mujhey barf , pani aur olon se dho dey.''"
782,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Abu-Bakar, umr aur Usman (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) qirat ki ibtida (shuruat) (الحمد لله رب العالمين) se kiya kartey they."
783,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz ki ibtida (shuruat) ( الله اكبر ( se aur qirat ki ibtida (shuruat) (الحمد لله رب العالمين) se kartey they. aur jab rukoo kartey to apna sar na ooncha rakhtey aur na jhukaatey balke unke dikhnewaley dikhnewaley hota . aur jab rukoo se sar uthatey to us waqt tak sajda na kartey jab tak ke sahih sidhey khadey na ho jatey. aur jab sajdey se sar uthatey to doosra sajda us waqt tak na kartey jab tak ke durust andaz mein baith na jatey aur her do rakaat ke baad) التحيات ( ) tashahud ( padhtey . aur jab baithtey to apna baayan paon bicha letey aur dayen ko khada kartey. aur shaitan ki chaukdi aur darindey ki manind baithney se mana farmatey. aur Namaz ko salam par khatam kartey.
784,Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujh par abhi-abhi eik surat nazil hui hai.'' aapney (بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم . إنا أعطيناك الكوثر ( puri surat padh kar sunai. aapney puchha : ''jantey ho kausar kya hai?'' Sahaba (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ne kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool hi behtar jantey hain. aapney farmaya : ''ye eik nehar hai jis ka mere Shan waley Rab ne mujh se jannat mein wada farmaya hai.''
785,"Janab Urwa ke wastey se Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai. . . . . aur Urwa ne qissa ifk ka zikr kiya. Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baithey aur apney chehrey se kapda hataya aur kaha : (أعوذ بالسميع العليم من الشيطان الرجيم) ( إِنَّ الَّذِينَ جَاءُوا بِالْإِفْكِ عُصْبَةٌ مِنْكُمْ , . ... .) Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya ke ye hadees munkar hai. usey Zohri se muhaddeseen ki jamaat ne riwayat kiya hai magar unhoney ye kalam (yani ta'aw'wuz) is tareeqey se (yani yahan par) zikr nahin kiya aur mujhey andesha hai ke shaitan se (ta'aw'wuz) ka bayan Humaid ka kalam hoga."
786,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : kya baat hui ke aapney Sura-Bara'at , jo (sau (100) aayaton wali surton) mein se hai, aur Sura-Anfaal ko , jo masani mein se hai, mila kar saat lambi soorton mein shamil kar diya hai aur in dono ke darmiyan '' ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( '' ki line nahin likhi hai. Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par jab Quran ki aayaat nazil hoti thin to aap kisi kaatib ko bula letey aur farmatey : ''is aayat ko us surat mein likh do jis mein falan-falan bayan hai.'' phir eik do aayaat utarteen to isi tarah farmatey. aur Sura-Anfaal un soorton mein se hai jo aap ki aamad Madina ke shuru dinon mein utri thi aur Sura-Bara'at nuzool Quran ke aakhiri daur ki soorton mein se hai aur inka mazmoon aapas mein mushabeh hai lihaza maine samjha ke ye Sura-Bara'at , Sura-Anfaal ka hissa hai aur yahin se maine in dono ko lambi soorton mein darj kar diya aur inke darmiyan ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( ki line nahin likhi."
787,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne mazkura hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya aur is mein kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee aur aapney hamarey liye ye wazeh nahin farmaya ke ye (Sura-Bara'at) , Sura-Anfaal mein se hai (ya) nahin. Imam Abu-Dawud ne farmaya ke Shobi , Abu-Malik , Qatada aur Sabit-bin- Imaara ne kaha hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( apney maktoobaat waghaira mein ) ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( likhni shuru nahin ke yahan tak ke Sura-Naml nazil ho gaee. ye is riwayat ka mafhoom hai."
788,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) soorton ka farq na pehchantey they yahan tak ke) بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( nazil ki jati . ye ibne-Sarah ke alfaz hain.
789,"Janab Abdullah-bin-abi-Qatada apney walid ( Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu)) se bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main Namaz ke liye khada hota hun aur mera irada hota hai ke usey lamba karunga magar main bachchey ka ronaa sunta hun to usey mukhtasar kar deta hun taake uski maa be-chain na ho.''"
790,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Hazrat Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhtey aur phir wapis aa kar hamari imaamat karatey they, Amr-bin-Dinar ne eik baar yun kaha ke phir wapis aa kar apni qaum ko Namaz padhatey they. ... eik raat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne takheer se Namaz padhaai . . . . . aur eik baar riwayat kiya ke Isha ki Namaz aapney takheer se padhaai aur Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi phir aa kar apni qaum ki imaamat ki aur Sura-Baqara padhni shuru kar di. to qaum mein se eik aadmi alehda ho gaya aur usney alag hi apni Namaz padhi , to usey kaha gaya : kya to munafiq ho gaya hai aey falan? usney kaha : main munafiq nahin hua hun. chunanche wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke sath Namaz padhtey hain, phir wapis ja kar hamari imaamat karatey hain, aey Allah ke Rasool ! aur ham aab-paashi ki oontniyon waley hain, apney haathon se kaam kartey hain, (guzishta raat) wo aaye aur hamari imaamat karaai aur Sura-Baqara padhney lagey . to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Muaz ! kya to fitney mein dalney wala hai? kya to fitney mein dalney wala hai? wo padho aur wo padho.'' Abu-Zubair ne naam lekar kaha ke (سبح اسم ربك الأعلى) aur) والليل إذا يغشى ( padho aur ham ne Amr se iska zikr kiya to unhoney kaha ke mera bhi khayal hai ke aapney soorton ke naam zikr kiye they."
791,"Janab Hazam-bin-Ubai-bin-Kab ka bayan hai ke wo Hazrat Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan aaye aur wo qaum ko maghrib ki Namaz padha rahey they. usi mazkura khabar mein bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Muaz ! fitney mein dalney waley na bano , be-shak tumharey peechhey badi umr waley, kamzor , kaam kaaj waley aur musafir log Namaz padhtey hain.''"
792,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke eik sahabi se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik shakhs se puchha : ''tum Namaz mein kya kehtey ho? '' usney kaha : main tashahud padhta hun phir yun kehta hun, aey Allah ! main tujh se jannat ka sawal karta aur jahannam se panah maangta hun, aur main aap ki aur Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki gungunaahat ko achhi tarah nahin samajhta (yani aap aur Muaz kya dua maangtey hain? aawaz to sunta hun, lekin wazeh alfaz samajh mein nahin aatey.) to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ham bhi un (jannat aur dozakh) ke gird hi gungunaatey hain.'' (yani jannat ka sawal aur dozakh se panah maangtey hain.)"
793,"Ubaidullah-bin-Muqsim , Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ka qissa zikr kiya, aur bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us jawan se farmaya : '' bhatijey ! jab Namaz padhtey ho to kaisey kartey ho? , (yani kya padhtey ho?) usney kaha : Fatiha padhta hun aur Allah se jannat maangta hun aur aag se panah chahta hun. aur mujhey nahin maloom ke aap ki gungunaahat kya hai aur na Muaz ke mutalliq maloom hai ke unki gungunaahat kya hai, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main aur Muaz un hi ke gird gungunaatey hain.'' ya uski manind kuch farmaya."
794,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs logon ko Namaz padhaaey to halki Namaz padhaaey . kyonkey un mein kamzor , bimar aur badi umr ke log hotey hain. aur jab apni akeley Namaz padhey , to jitni chahey lambi kar ley.''"
795,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi logon ko Namaz padhaaey to halki Namaz padhaaey , kyonkey un mein bimar , badi umr ke aur kaam kaaj waley hotey hain.''"
796,"Hazrat Ammar-bin-Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''insan Namaz se farigh hota hai aur uskey liye uski Namaz se sirf daswaan, nawan , aathwan , saatwan , chhata , paanchwan , chautha , teesra , aur aadha hissey hi likha jata hai.''"
797,"Janab Ata-bin-abi-Ribah se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : '' har Namaz mein qirat ki jati hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo hamein sunaya , ham tumhen sunwaate hain aur aapney jo ham se makhfi (chhipa hua) rakha ham tum se makhfi rakhtey hain.''"
798,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein Namaz padhatey to Zohar aur Asr ki pehli do rakaaton mein Fatiha aur do suratein padhtey. aap kabhi-kabhi hamein koi aayat snuwa bhi diya kartey they, aap Zohar ki pehli rakaat ko taweel kartey aur dusri ko mukhtasar , aur aisey hi Fajr mein hota. Imam Abu-Dawud ne farmaya : Shaikh Musaddad ne Fatiha aur surat ka zikr nahin kiya."
799,Janab Abdullah-bin-abi-Qatada ne apney walid se us mazkura hadees ka kuch hissey bayan kiya aur izafa kiya ke aakhiri do rakaaton mein Fatiha padhtey. (Yazid-bin-Harun ne) Hammam se ye mazeed bayan kiya ke aap pehli rakaat is qadr lambi kartey ke dusri itni lambi na kartey aur aisey hi Asr aur Fajr mein bhi.
800,"Janab Abdullah-bin-abi Qatada apney walid ( Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu)) se bayan kartey hain ke ham ne (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mamool sey) ye samjha , aap chahtey they ke log pehli rakaat pa lein."
801,"Janab abu-Ma'mar se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke ham ne Hazrat Khabbab (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zohar aur Asr mein qirat farmaya kartey they? unhoney kaha : haan. ham ne kaha : aap ko kaisey maloom hota tha? unhoney kaha : aap ki dadhi ke hilney se."
802,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-abi-aufi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zohar ki Namaz ki pehli rakaat mein itni der tak khadey rehtey ke qadmon ki aawazen na suntey they.
803,"Hazrat Jabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Saad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) (ameer koofa) se kaha ke logon ne aap ki her baat mein shikayat ki hai, yahan tak ke Namaz ke baarey mein bhi , to unhoney kaha : main to pehli do rakaaton ko lamba aur pichli do ko mukhtasar karta hun aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wali Namaz ki perwi kerney mein koi taqseer (kami) nahin karta. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap ke mutalliq yehi guman hai."
804,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham ne Zohar aur Asr ki namazon mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qiyam ka andaza lagaya to wo ye tha ke aap Zohar ki pehli do rakaaton mein Sura Sajda ki taqreeban tees aayaat ke barabar qiyam farmatey . aur ham ne aakhiri do rakaaton mein aap ke qiyam ka andaza unke nisf ke barabar kiya. aur ham ne Asr ki pehli do rakaaton mein aap ke qiyam ka andaza lagaya to ye Zohar ki pichli do rakaaton ke barabar tha. aur Asr ki pichli do rakaaton mein aap ke qiyam ka andaza unke bhi nisf barabar ka tha.
805,Hazrat Jabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zohar aur Asr mein Sura-Tariq aur Sura-Buruj aur unki misl suraten padha kartey they.
806,"Hazrat Jabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Suraj dhal jata to Zohar ki Namaz padhtey aur sura ( والليل إذا يغشى ( jaisi suraten padhtey they. Asr aur baqi namazon mein bhi aisey hi qirat hoti thi , siwaye subh ke. us mein aap lambi qirat kya kartey they."
807,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne namaze-Zohar mein sajda (tilawat) kiya, phir khadey ho gaey phir rukoo kiya, to hamein maloom hua ke aapney Alif-Lam-Mim Tanzeel Sajda tilawat ki thi. ibne-Esa kehtey hain Umayya ka zikr sirf Moatamir hi ne kiya hai."
808,"Janab Abdullah-bin-Ubaidullah kehtey hain ke main bani haashim ke chand jawaanon ke sath mein Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke yahan gaya. ham ne apney eik sathi se kaha ke ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se poochho ke kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zohar aur Asr mein qirat kartey they? unhoney farmaya : nahin. unhein kaha gaya. shayad aap apney dil mein padhtey they. kaha : tera bhala ho ! ye soorat pehli se bhi badtar hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( Allah ke) maamoor bandey they. aap ko jis chiz ke sath bheja gaya aapney usey pahuncha diya. aapney hamein logon se alag kisi chiz ke sath khas nahin kiya. siwaye teen baaton ke . ye ke wuzu kamil karen, sadqa na khaeyn aur gadhey ko ghodi se jufti na karaein ."
809,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : mujhey nahin maloom ke aaya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zohar aur Asr mein qirat kartey they ya nahin.
810,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke (unki walida) Umme-Fazal-binte-al-Haaris ne unko suna ke wo Sura-Murslat ki tilawat kar rahey they, to unhoney kaha : bete ! tum ne is surat ki qirat se mujhey yaad dilaayaa hai ke ye aakhiri chiz thi jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni . aap isey maghrib mein padh rahey they."
811,"Janab Muhammad-bin-Jubair-bin-Mut'im apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap maghrib (ki Namaz) mein sura ''والطور'' ki qirat kar rahey they."
812,Marwan-bin-Hakam se riwayat hai unhoney kaha ke Hazrat Zaid-bin-Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se kaha kya wajeh hai ke tum maghrib mein qasar tafseeli (aakhiri chhoti suraten hi ( padhtey ho halanke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna hai ke aap maghrib mein do lambi-lambi soorton mein se lambi surat padhtey they. (ibne-abi Mulaika ne ( kaha : do lambi suraten kaun si hain? kaha Aaraf aur Anaam . aur main ( ibne-Juraij ( ne ibne-abi Mulaika se puchha to mujhey unhoney apni taraf se kaha ke Maayda aur Aaraf .
813,Janab Hisham-bin-Urwa ka bayan hai ke unke walid (Urwa-bin-Zubair) maghrib mein usi tarah ki suraten padhtey they jaisi tum log padhtey ho yani '' والعاديات '' waghaira . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ye daleel hai ke maghrib mein taweel qirat mansookh hai. aur Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha ke yehi ziyada sahih hai.
814,"Hazrat Amr-bin-shoaib apney walid (shoaib) se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke '' mufassal '' ki koi chhoti badi surat nahin jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se na suni ho, aap usey farz namazon ki imaamat karatey huey padhtey they."
815,Janab Abu-Usman Nahdi se marwi (bayan) hai ke unhoney Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechey maghrib ki Namaz padhi to unhoney ( قل هو الله أحد ( tilawat ki .
816,Janab Muaz-bin-Abdullah Juhni ka bayan hai ke Banu-Juhaina ke eik shakhs ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna ke aap Fajr ki Namaz mein dono rak'aat mein) إذا زلزلت الأرض ( padh rahey they. mujhey nahin maloom ke aap bhool gaey they ya janbujh kar uski qirat ki thi.
817,Hazrat Amr-bin-Hurriyat (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke goya main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aawaz sun raha hun aap Fajr ki Namaz mein) فلا أقسم بالخنس ( * ( الجوار الكنس ( ) Sura-Takweer) padh rahey they.
818,Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamein hukm diya gaya ke ham ( Namaz mein) Fatiha aur jo muyassar ho (yani Quran mein sey) padha karen.
819,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jao aur Madiney mein aelan kar do ke Quran ( ki qirat (ke baghair Namaz nahin chahey (chahey) Fatiha Al-Kitab ho aur kuchh ziyada . khuwah (chahey) Fatiha Al-Kitab ho aur kuchh ziyada.''
820,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya ke main aelan kar dun ke qirat Fatiha aur kuchh mazeed ke baghair Namaz nahin.
821,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs koi Namaz padhey aur us mein Ummul-Quran (Sura-Faatiha) na padhey to aisi Namaz naqis hai, naqis hai, naqis hai, kamil nahin hai.''  (Abu-Saaib ne kaha) maine kaha : aey Abu-Huraira ! main kabhi-kabhi Imam ke peechhey hota hun. to unhoney meri kalaai dabaai aur kaha : aey Farsi ! isey apney nafs mein padha karo, bila-shuba maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap kehtey they : ''Shan wala Allah farmata hai : maine Namaz ko apney aur bandey ke darmiyan aadhey-aadha taqseem kar diya hai, nisf merey liye hai aur nisf mere bandey ke liye aur mere bandey ke liye wo sab kuchh hai jo usney manga .'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' padha karo.'' banda kehta hai (الحمد لله رب العالمين) Shan wala Allah farmata hai : merey bandey ne meri tareef ki . banda kehta hai : (الرحمن الرحيم ( Shan wala Allah farmata hai : merey bandey ne meri sanaa ki . banda kehta hai : (مالك يوم الدين) Shan wala Allah farmata hai : merey bandey ne meri buzurgi bayan ki . banda kehta hai : ( إياك نعبد وإياك نستعين ( ) Allah farmata hai : ( ye mere aur bandey ke beech hai aur mere bandey ke liye wo sab kuchh hai jo usney manga . banda kehta hai : (اهدنا الصراط المستقيم) (صراط الذين أنعمت عليهم غير المغضوب عليهم wla الضالين) (Shan wala Allah farmata hai : ( ye sab mere bandey ke liye hai aur mere bandey ke liye wo sab kuchh hai jo usney manga.''"
822,Hazrat Ubada-bin-Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf nisbat kartey huey bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jo shakhs Sura-Faatiha aur kuchh mazeed na padhey uski Namaz nahin.'' Janab Sufiyan ne kaha is se murad ye hai ke jab koi shakhs akela padh raha ho (to ye hukm hai).
823,"Hazrat Ubada-bin-Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham Namaze-Fajr mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey they. aapney qirat shuru farmaee magar wo aap par bhari ho gaee . (yani aap us mein rawan na reh sakey.) jab aap farigh huey to kaha : ''shayad ke tum log apney Imam ke peechhey padhtey ho?'' ham ne kaha : haan , aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham jaldi-jaldi padhtey hain. aapney farmaya : ''na padha karo magar Faatiha, kyonkey jo usey (Faatiha ko) na padhey uski Namaz nahin.''"
824,"Janab Naafe-bin-Mehmood-bin-Rabeea Ansari ne bayan kiya ke (eik baar) Hazrat Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) Fajr ki Namaz mein takheer se aaye to Abu-Nuaim muazzan ne takbir kahi aur Namaz padhana shuru kar di. Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur main bhi aap ke sath tha ham ne Abu-Nuaim ke peechhey saf banai.  Abu-Nuaim jahri qirat kar rahey they aur Hazrat Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne Sura-Faatiha padhni shuru kar di. jab wo farigh huye, to maine Ubada se kaha : maine aap ko suna hai ke aap Sura-Faatiha padh rahey they halanke (Imam) Abu-Nuaim jahri (aawaz ke saath) qirat kar rahey they. (Hazrat Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( kaha haan . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein Namaz padhaai jis mein aapney jahri qirat ki, magar aap qirat mein ulajh gaey . jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farigh huey to hamari taraf chehra kiya aur farmaya : ''kya tum log qirat kartey ho, jab main oonchi aawaz se qirat kar raha hota hun? '' ham mein se baaz ne kaha : ham aisa kartey hain. aapney farmaya : ''na kiya karo . main keh raha tha mujhey kya hua hai ke Quran padhney mein uljhan ho rahi hai. jab main jahr (aawaz) se padh raha hun to Quran se kuch na padho , magar Ummul-Quran (Faatiha).''"
825,"Makhool ne Hazrat Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) se Rabeea-bin-Sulaiman ki (mazkura baala) riwayat ki manind bayan kiya. (Makhool ke shagird ne) bayan kiya ke Janab Makhool Maghrib , Isha aur Fajr ki Namazon mein her rakaat mein khamoshi ke sath Sura-Faatiha padha kartey they. Makhool ne kaha : jab Imam jahri (aawaz ke sath) qirat kar raha ho aur saktey karey to (us beech mein) khamoshi se Fatiha padh lo agar saktey na karey to us se pehley padh lo ya uskey sath sath padhtey jao ya uskey baad padh lo. kisi haal mein chhodo nahin."
826,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz se phirey , jis mein aapney jahri (aawaz ke sath) qirat ki thi aur farmaya : ''kya tum mein se kisi ne abhi merey sath qirat ki hai? '' eik aadmi ne kaha haan , aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney farmaya : ''main bhi keh raha tha mujhey kya hua ke Qirate-Quran mein ulajh raha hun.'' raawi ne kaha : isliye log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath padhney se ruk gaey un namazon mein jin mein aap jahri (aawaz ke sath) kar rahey hotey jabkey unhoney aap se ye farman suna . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : ibne-Akmiya ki ye riwayat Maamer , Yunus aur Usaama-bin-Zaid ne Zohri se Malik ki riwayat ke ham-maani riwayat ki hai."
827,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein Namaz padhaai , khayal hai ke ye subh ki Namaz thi. ... aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani (مالي أنازع القرآن) ''mujhey kiya hua ke Qirate-Quran mein ulajh raha hun.''  tak bayan kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : Musaddad ne apni hadees mein kaha ke Maamer ne bayan kiya : isliye log in Namazon mein qirat se ruk gaey jin mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jahri (aawaz ke saath) qirat kartey they. aur ibn-Sarah ne apni riwayat mein kaha : Maamer ne Zohri ke wastey bayan kiya ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : '' isliye log ruk gaey.'' aur un mein se Abdullah-bin-Muhammad Zohri ne bayan kiya ke Sufiyan ne kaha ke Zohri ne koi kalma kaha jo main na sun saka , to Maamer ne bataya ke unhoney kaha hai : '' isliye log ruk gaey.'' Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : aur is hadees ko Abdur-Rehman-bin-Is-haq ne Zohri se riwayat kiya hai jo ke (مالي أنازع القرآن) ke alfaz tak hai. aur Auzaai ne isey Zohri se riwayat kartey huey kaha ke Zohri ne kaha : isliye musalman is par mutanabbeh (aagah) ho gaey to jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jahri (aawaz ke saath) kartey to wo aap ke sath qirat na kiya kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke maine Muhammad -bin-Yahya-bin-Faaris se suna ke) فانتهى Naas ( ''yani log ruk gaey.'' Zohri ka kalam hai."
828,"Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zohar ki Namaz padhaai , eik aadmi aaya aur usney aap ke peechhey (سبح اسم ربك الأعلى) padhi. jab Aap farigh huey to farmaya : ''tum mein se kis ne qirat ki hai? '' unhoney kaha : eik aadmi ne qirat ki hai. aapney farmaya : ''main jaan gaya tha ke tum mein se kisi ne mujhey qirat mein uljhaya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya hai ke Abul-Waleed ne apni riwayat mein Shoba se naqal kiya ke maine Qatada se kaha : kya Saeed ka ye qaul nahin hai ke ''Quran ke liye khamosh raho?'' kaha : ye tab hai jab wo jahri (aawaz ke saath) padhey. ibne-kaseer ne apni riwayat mein kaha : maine Qatada se kaha : goya aapney usey (yani padhney ko) makruh jana . kaha : agar makruh jantey to rok detey."
829,"Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhein Zohar ki Namaz padhaai , jab farigh huey to puchha : ''tum mein se kis ne ( سَبِّحْ اسْمَ رَبِّكَ الْأَعْلَى ( ki qirat ki hai?'' eik aadmi ne kaha : maine , aapney farmaya : ''main jaan gaya tha ke tum mein se koi mujhey (qirat mein) uljhaa raha hai.''"
830,"Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamari majlis mein tashrif laye jabke ham Quran padh rahey they, ham mein dehati bhi they, aur ghair arab bhi . aapney farmaya : ''padhey jao, sab hi behtar hai. an-qareeb aisey log aaeyngey jo isey (Qirate-Quran ko) aisey sidha karengey jaisey ke teer sidha kiya jata hai. uska ajr (duniya mein) jald hi lena chahengey aur (aakhirat tak) muakhkhar (der) nahin karengey.''"
831,"Hazrat Sahal-bin-Saad-Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamari majlis mein tashrif laye jabke ham Quran padh padha rahey they. aapney farmaya : '' Alhamdulillah ! Allah ki kitab eik hai aur tum ( padhney walon ( mein surkh , safed aur kalay sabhi log hain. isey padhey jao ! qabl iskey ke wo log iski qirat shuru kar den jo isey aisey sidha karengey jaisey ke teer sidha kiya jata hai aur iska ajr jald hi ( duniya mein) lena chahengey , isey (aakhirat tak) muakhkhar (der) na karengey .''"
832,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kehney laga ke main Quran se kuch yaad nahin kar sakta , mujhey kuch sikha dijiye jo merey liye (Quran ki qirat sey) kifaayat karey. aapney farmaya : ''tum (سبحان الله والحمد لله wla إله إلا الله والله أكبر wla حول wla قوة إلا بالله الْعَلِيِّ الْعَظِيمِ) padha karo.''Allah paak hai, usi ki tareef hai, uskey alawa aur koi mabud nahin, aur Allah sab se bada hai. buraiyon se bachna aur neki ki taufiq milna , Allah ke siwa kisi se mumkin nahin. wo aali (unchaa) hai azmat wala hai.'' kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye tu Allah ke liye hua , merey liye kya hai? aapney farmaya : ''kaha karo : ( اللهم ! ارحَمْنِي وارزُقْنِي وعَافِني واهدِنِي ) ''aey Allah ! mujh par rehem farma, mujhey rizq dey , rahat aur aafiyat se nawaz aur hidayat se sarfaraaz farma.'' chunanche jab wo khada hua to apney haathon se aisey ishara kiya. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usney apney haath khair se bhar liye hain.''"
833,Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke ham nafl padha kartey to qiyam aur baithne mein dua kiya kartey they aur rukoo aur sajdey mein tasbeehaat.
834,Janab Humaid ne mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kiya aur nafl ka zikr nahin kiya. ye bhi kaha ke Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) Zohar aur Asr mein Imam hotey huey ya Imam ke peechhey bhi Sura-Faatiha padhtey aur (سبحان اللہ ، اللہ أکبر اور لا إله الّا اللہ) kehtey aur Sura Qaaf aur zaariyat ke jitna kehtey.
835,"Janab Mutrif bayan kartey hain ke maine aur Imran-bin-Husain ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey Namaz padhi. to wo jab sajda kartey to (الله أكبر ( kehtey, rukoo kartey to (الله أكبر ( kehtey do rakaaton se uthtey to ( الله أكبر ( kehtey. jab ham farigh huey to Imran ne mera haath pakda aur kaha : unhoney hamein pehley wali Namaz padhaai ya kaha : hamein is tarah Namaz padhaai jo ham pehley Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath padha kartey they."
836,"Janab abu-Bakar-bin-Abdur-Rehman aur Abu-Salma se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) har farz aur ghair farz Namaz mein takbeerein kaha kartey they, jab khadey hotey to takbir kehtey, phir jab rukoo kartey to takbir kehtey. phir ( rukoo se uthtey to ( (سمع الله لمن حمده) kehtey, uskey baad) ربنا ولك الحمد ( kehtey . phir sajdey ko jatey huey ( الله اكبر ( kehtey phir sajdey se sar uthatey to takbir kehtey, phir ( doosra ( sajda kartey to takbir kehtey, phir sar uthatey huey takbir kehtey, phir do rakatein padh kar baith kar uthtey to takbir kehtey aur her rakaat mein aisey hi kartey , yahan tak ke Namaz se farigh ho jatey. phir jab Namaz se phirtey to kehtey : qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! Namaz ke maamley mein main tum sab se ziyada Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mushabeh hun. aap (Aleh.) ki yehi Namaz thi , yahan tak ke aap is duniya se wafaat farma gaey . Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Malik aur Zubaidi waghaira ne in aakhiri jumlon ko Zohri ke wastey Janab Ali-bin-Husain-bin-Ali-bin-Abi Talib se riwayat kiya hai. jabkey abdul-A'alaa ne ba-waasta Maamer Shoaib-bin-Abi Hamza ki muwaafiqat ki hai. (jaisey ke Muallif (writer/lekhak) ne zikr kiya hai.)"
837,Janab ibne-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Abza apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi aur aap sab takbeerein na kehtey they. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha ke uskey maani ye hain ke rukoo se sar utha kar sajdey ko jatey huey aur sajdon se qiyam kartey huey takbir nahin kahi.
838,Hazrat Wayal-bin-Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap jab sajda kartey to apney ghutney apney haathon se pehley rakhtey they aur jab uthtey to apney haath ghutnon se pehley uthatey they.
839,Janab Abdul-Jabbaar-bin-Wayal apney walid se hadeese-darood bayan kartey huey farmatey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab sajda kiya to unke ghutney zameen par haathon se pehley pahunchey. Hammam ne kaha ke Shaqiq ne Aasim-bin-kulaib Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sanad se iski jaisi bayan kiya hai. aur Muhammad-bin-Hajaada ya Shaqiq mein se kisi eik ki riwayat mein hai. aur ghaaliban Muhammad-bin-Hajaada ki riwayat mein hai ke aap jab uthtey to apney ghutnon par uthtey aur apni raanon ka sahara letey they.
840,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi sajda karey to aisey na baithey jaisey ke oont baithta hai, chahiye ke apney haath ghutnon se pehley rakhey.''"
841,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(kya) tum mein se koi eik apni Namaz mein is tarah baithney ka qasad (irada) karta hai jis tarah oont baithta hai. ''
842,"Janab Abu-Qulaba bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Sulaiman Malik-bin-Huwairis (Raziallahu anhu) hamari masjid mein tashrif laye aur kaha : qasam Allah ki ! main tumhen Namaz padhaaun ga , halanke Namaz ka irada nahin. sirf ye chahta hun ke tumhen dikhaon ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kis tarah Namaz padhtey dekha hai. ( Ayub ne kaha : ( maine Abu-Qulaba se puchha unhoney kaisey Namaz padhi? kaha : hamarey is Shaikh ki manind . . . . yani Amr-bin-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ki manind jo wahan unke Imam they. ... aur bayan kiya ke jab wo pehli rakaat ke doosrey sajdey se sar uthatey to baith jatey they, phir ( uskey baad) uthtey they."
843,"Janab abu-Qulaba bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Sulaiman Malik-bin-Huwairis (Raziallahu anhu) hamari masjid mein tashrif laye aur kaha : qasam Allah ki ! main Namaz padhunga aur Namaz ka irada nahin, magar main ye chahta hun ke tumhen dikhaoon ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kis tarah Namaz padhtey dekha hai (Abu-Qulaba ne) kaha : chunanche wo pehli rakaat mein doosra sajda kerney ke baad baith gaey (aur phir uthey)."
844,Janab Abu-Qulaba Hazrat Malik-bin-Huwairis (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha tha jab aap apni Namaz ki taaq rakaat mein hotey to us waqt tak khadey na hotey they jab tak ke durust ho kar baith na jatey.
845,Janab Taaus farmatey they ke ham ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se do sajdon ke darmiyan ediyon par baithney ke mutalliq puchha : to unhoney kaha : ye sunnat hai. ham ne kaha : ham to usey paon par bojh ya aadmi ke liye baaise mashaqqat khayal kartey hain. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : ye aap ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat hai.
846,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abi-Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab rukoo se apna sar uthatey to kehtey they : (سَمِعَ اللَّهُ لِمَنْ حَمِدَهُ اللَّهُمَّ رَبَّنَا لَكَ الْحَمْدُ مِلْءُ السَّمَوَاتِ وَمِلْءُ الْأَرْضِ وَمِلْءُ مَا شِئْتَ مِنْ شَيْءٍ بَعْدُ) ''sun liya Allah ne usko , jisney uski tareef ki ! aey Allah ! aey hamarey Rab ! teri hi tareef hai (is qadr ke) us se sab aasman bhar jayen , zameen bhar jayen aur inke alawa jo to chahey, uskey bharney ke barabar.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Sufiyan Sauri aur Shoba-bin-Hajjaj ne Ubaid-Abul-Hasan se bayan kiya ke is hadees mein ''rukoo ke baad'' ka zikr nahin hai. Sufiyan kehtey hain ke ham ne iskey baad Shaikh Ubaid Abul-Hasan se mulaqat ki to unhoney is riwayat mein '' baad rukoo '' ka zikr nahin kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : jabkey Shoba ne Abu-Asma se unhoney Aamash se unhoney Ubaid se riwayat kiya hai to ( baad rukoo (ka zikr kiya hai."
847,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab (سمع الله لمن حمده) keh letey to kehtey : (اللهم ربنا لك الحمد ملء السماء) aur Maumil ke alfaz : ( مِلْءَ السَّمَوَاتِ وَمِلْءَ الْأَرْضِ . ... . الخ ) ''aey Allah ! aey hamarey Rab ! teri hi tareef hai jis se ke aasman bhar jayen , zameen bhar jayen aur inke alawa jo to chahey bhar jaey. aey wo zaat jo tareef aur buzurgi ke ehle hai ! sab se haq baat jo bandey ko kehne laaiq hai. ... aur ham sab terey hi bandey hain. ... yehi hai ke jo to inayat farma dey usey koi rok nahin sakta.'' aur Mehmood ne ziyada kiya (ولا معطي لما منعت) aur jo to rok ley koi dey nahin sakta phir ( wla ينفع ذا الجد منك الجد (aur terey muqabley mein kisi ki badai aur buzurgi faeyda nahin dey sakti ye sab ka ittifaq hai. Bishr ne ( اللهم (ke baghair ( ربنا لك الحمد ( bayan kiya hai aur Mehmood ne ( اللهم (ke baghair ( ربنا w لك الحمد ( ) izaafe k saath واو ( riwayat kiya hai. Waleed-bin-Muslim ne Saeed se riwayat kiya to kaha : ( اللهم ربنا لك الحمد (aur (ولا معطي لما منعت) ke alfaz bayan nahin kiye. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : unko sirf abu-Mushir hi ne bayan kiya hai."
848,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Imam (سمع الله لمن حمده) kahe to tum log kaho (اللهم ربنا لك الحمد) kyonkey jiskey ye kalimaat malaaika ( farishton (ke qaul ke muwaafiq ho gaey, uskey sabiqa (pichhle) gunah bakhsh diye jaeyngey.''"
849,Janab Aamir-bin-Sharaaheel Shobi ( Taabai ( kehtey hain ke logon ko Imam ke peechhey (سمع الله لمن حمده) nahin kehna chahiye. wo ( ربنا لك الحمد ( kahen.
850,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do sajdon ke darmiyan ye dua padha kartey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْلِي وَارْحَمْنِي وَعَافِنِي وَاهْدِنِي وَارْزُقْنِي ) ''aey Allah ! mujhey bakhsh dey ! mujh par rehem farma ! mujhey aafiyat dey aur hidayat dey aur mujhey rizq dey.''
851,Sayeda Asma-binte-Abi-Bakar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan karti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna ke aap aurton se farmatey they : ''jo tum mein se Allah aur qiyamat ke din par imaan rakhti hai wo apna sar ( sajdey sey) us waqt tak na uthaey jab tak ke mard na utha lein.'' Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye hukm is liye diya ke kahin unki nazar mardon ke satron par na pad jaey.
852,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka sajda , rukoo aur do sajdon ke darmiyan baithna qarib-qarib barabar hua karta tha."
853,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine kisi ke peechhey Namaz nahin padhi jiski Namaz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( ki Namaz ( se badh kar mukhtasar aur kamil ho. aap ( سَمِعَ اللَّهُ لِمَنْ حَمِدَهُ ( keh kar khadey hotey (aur is qadr lamba qiyam kartey (ke ham samajhtey shayad aap ko weham ho gaya hai. phir aap takbir kehtey aur sajda kartey. aur aap dono sajdon ke darmiyan baithtey (aur is qadr lamba bethtey (ke ham kehtey ke shayad aap ko weham ho gaya hai.
854,"Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Namaz mein badey ghaur se dekha, to maine paya ke aap ka qiyam aap ke rukoo aur sajdey ke barabar hota tha. aur aap ka rukoo se aetidaal (beech ka rasta) (qauma) aap ke sajdey ke barabar hota . aur aap ka do sajdon ke darmiyan baithna aur sajda jo salam aur phirney ke beech hota barabar hotey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Musaddad ne riwayat kiya ke aap ka rukoo , rukoo aur sajdey ke darmiyan aetidaal ( qiyam , qauma ( , phir aap ka sajda, phir salam aur phirney ke darmiyan baithna taqreeban barabar hotey they."
855,Hazrat Abu-Masood Badrii (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aadmi ki Namaz kifaayat nahin karti jab tak ke wo rukoo aur sajdey main apni kamar ko barabar na kar ley.''
856,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein tashrif laye aur eik aadmi masjid mein dakhil hua , usney Namaz padhi , phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur salam kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey salam ka jawab diya aur farmaya : ''jao Namaz padho ! tum ne Namaz nahin padhi.'' chunanche wo gaya aur Namaz padhi jaisey ke (pehley) padhi thi. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur salam kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''( walaikum Assalam) jao, Namaz padho ! tum ne Namaz nahin padhi.'' yahan tak ke usney teen baar aisey hi kiya. bil-aakhir usney kaha : qasam us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja (bheja) hai ! main is se umda nahin padh sakta , mujhey sikha dijiye . aapney farmaya : ''jab tum Namaz ke liye khadey ho to ( Allahu-Akbar) kaho . phir tumharey liye jo aasan ho Quran se padho . phir rukoo karo, yahan tak ke rukoo mein khoob itminan kar lo . phir sar uthao , yahan tak ke durust andaz mein khadey ho jao . phir sajda karo, yahan tak ke sajdey mein khoob itminan kar lo . phir baitho , yahan tak ke tasalli se baith jao aur phir aisey hi puri Namaz mein kiya karo . Qaanabi ne isey ba-waasta Saeed-bin-abi-Saeed Maqbari , Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai to uskey aakhir mein kaha hai : ''agar tum ne aisey hi kiya to tumhari Namaz kamil hogi aur agar is mein kuch kami ki to apni Namaz mein kami ki .'' mazeed is riwayat mein ye bhi hai ke aapney farmaya : . ... .'' jab Namaz ke liye utho to wuzu kamil karo.''"
857,"Ali-bin-Yahya-bin-Khallaad ( Yahya ke) chacha ( Rifaa ( se riwayat kartey hain ke eik shakhs masjid mein dakhil hua , aur mazkura baala hadees ke misl zikr kiya. is mein hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi shakhs ki Namaz us waqt tak kamil nahin ho sakti jab tak ke wo wuzu na kar ley aur wuzu ke angon ko theek theek na dho ley . phir takbir kahe aur Allah ki hamd aur sanaa kare aur kuchh Quran padhey jo usey aasan lagey. phir ( Allahu-akbar)  kahe aur rukoo kare, yahan tak ke uske jod itminan se tik jaeyn phir kahe (سمع اللہ لمن حمدہ) aur itminan se sidha khada ho jaey, phir kahe ( Allahu-akbar)  aur sajda karey, yahan tak ke uskey jod itminan se tik jaeyn . phir ( Allahu-akbar) kahe aur apna sar uthaey aur theek tarah se baith jaey. phir ( Allahu-akbar) kahe aur sajda kare, yahan tak ke uske jod itminan se tik jaeyn . phir apna sar uthaey aur takbir kahe . jab is tarah kerega to uski Namaz kamil hogi.''"
858,"Janab Ali-bin-Yahya-bin-Khallaad ne apney walid se unhoney apney chacha Rifa'a-bin-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya. . . . . . us mein hai ke tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi ki Namaz us waqt tak kamil nahin ho sakti jab tak ke wuzu kamil na karey jaisey ke Allah taala ne usey hukm diya hai. isliye apna chehra dhoey kohniyon tak dono haath dhoey , sar ka masah karey aur takhnon tak dono paon dhoey. phir ( Allahu-akbar ( kahe (aur Namaz shuru karey (aur Shan wale Allah ki hamd aur sanaa karey. phir Quran se qirat karey jaisey ke usey hukm diya gaya hai aur jo aasan lagey.'' phir Hammad ki hadees ki manind riwayat kiya. aur kaha : ''phir takbir kahe aur sajda karey aur apna chehra zameen par tikaa de.'' Hammam ne is maqam par kabhi-kabhi (جبھتہ من الارض) ka lafz istimal kiya hai yani apni peshani zameen par tikaaey yahan tak ke uskey jod itminan aur sukoon se tik jaeyn. phir takbir kahe aur durust ho kar sireen par baith jaey aur kamar ko sidhi rakhey. ''الغرض ! isi andaz mein Namaz ka tariqa bayan farmaya yahan tak ke chaaron rak'aat se farigh ho jaey.'' kisi shakhs ki Namaz kamil nahin ho sakti, yahan tak ke aisey hi karey.''"
859,"Janab Ali-bin-Yahya-bin-Khallaad ne Hazrat Rifa'a-bin-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) se ye qissa bayan kiya kaha : ''jab tum (Namaz ke liye ( khadey ho kar qible ki taraf rukh karo, to ( Allahu-Akbar) kaho phir Ummul-Quran (Faatiha) aur Quran se kuch padho jo Allah taufiq dey . jab rukoo karo to apni hatheliyon ko apney ghutnon par rakho aur kamar ko lamba rakho.'' aur farmaya : ''jab sajda karo to itminan se tik kar sajda karo aur jab sajdey se utho to apni baain raan par baith jao.''"
860,"Janab Ali-bin-Yahya-bin-Khallaad-bin-Raafe apney walid se wo apney chacha Rifa'a-bin-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye waqia bayan kartey hain. Aapney farmaya : ''jab tum apni Namaz ke liye khadey ho to Shan wale Allah ki takbir kaho , phir jo tumhen Quran se aasan lagey wo padho.'' is riwayat mein mazeed farmaya : ''jab tum Namaz ke dauran mein baitho to itminan se baitho aur apni baain raan bichha lo, phir tashahud padho , phir jab khadey ho to pehley ki tarah karo, yahan tak ke apni Namaz se farigh ho jao.''"
861,"Janab Yahya-bin-Ali-bin-Yahya-bin-Khallaad-bin-Raafe-Zarqi apney walid sey, wo apney dada sey, wo Hazrat Rifa'a-bin-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya. ... aur yehi hadees bayan ki . is mein kaha . ... '' phir wuzu karo jaisey ke tum ko Allah ne hukm diya hai aur) baad wuzu ( kalima shahadat padho. phir iqaamat kaho. phir ( الله اكبر ( kaho (aur Namaz shuru karo). agar tumhen Quran yaad ho padho warna Allah taala ki tahmeed , takbir aur tahleel karo.'' is riwayat mein mazeed farmaya hai, agar tum ne us se kuch kam kiya to apni Namaz se kam kiya.''"
862,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Shibl (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne manaa farmaya hai ke) Namaz mein) kowey ki tarah thongein maari jaeyn ya darindey ki manind phail kar baitha jaey ya koi shakhs masjid mein) apney liye ( jagah khas kar ley jaisey ke oont khas kar leta hai. aur ye lafz Quteba ke hain."
863,"Janab Salim Baraad bayan kartey hain ke ham Hazrat abu-Masood Aqba-bin-Amr Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur un se kaha ke hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ke mutalliq bataaiye. wo hamare samney masjid mein khadey ho gaey aur (Allahu-Akbar) kaha (aur Namaz shuru ki) jab rukoo kiya to haathon ko apney ghutnon par rakha aur ungliyon ko in ( ghutnon ( se nichey kiya aur kohniyon ko) pahluon sey) door rakha , yahan tak ke har har jod apni jagah par tik gaya. phir (سمع اللہ لمن حمدہ) kaha aur khadey ho gaey yahan tak ke her har uzu (ang) apni-apni jagah par tik gaya. phir takbir kahi aur sajda kiya aur haathon ko zameen par rakha . phir kohniyon ko pahluon se door kiya, yahan tak ke her uzu apni jagah par tik gaya phir ( sajdey sey) apna sar uthaya aur baithey , yahan tak ke har-har uzu apni jagah par tik gaya. phir ( doosrey sajdey mein) bhi aisey hi kiya. phir isi tarah chaar rakatein padhein aur apni Namaz puri ki, phir farmaya : ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aisey hi Namaz padhtey huey dekha tha."
864,"Anas-bin-Hakim-Zabi se marwi (bayan) hai, kaha ke wo Ziyad ya ibne-Ziyaad ke khauf se Madina aa gaya aur yahan Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat ho gaee . unhoney mujh se mera nasab maloom kiya to maine unhen bata diya. phir unhoney farmaya : aey jawan ! kya main tumhen eik hadees na sunaun? maine kaha : kyon nahin. Allah aap par rehem farmaai ! ( ustaad ( Yunus kehtey hain : mera khayal hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kiya ke aapney farmaya : ''qiyamat ke roz logon ke aamaal mein se jis amal ka sab se pehley hisab hoga wo unki Namaz hogi. hamara Shan wala Rab farishton se farmaeyga halanke wo ( pehley hi ( khoob janney wala hai, merey bandey ki Namaz dekho ! kya usney usko pura kiya hai ya us mein koi kami hai? chunanche wo agar kamil hui to puri ki puri likh di jaeygi aur agar us mein koi kami hui to farmaeyga ke dekho ! kya merey bandey ke kuch nawaafil bhi hain? agar nafl huey to wo farmaeyga ke merey bandey ke farzon ko uskey naflon se pura kar do . phir isi andaz se deegar aamaal liye jaeyngey.''"
865,Bani-saleet ke eik shakhs ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se usi (mazkura baala hadees ( ki manind riwayat kiya.
866,"Janab Zurara-bin-Aufa ne Hazrat Tameem Daari (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi ke ham-maani bayan kiya. kaha '' phir Zakat ka muhaasba hoga. phir baqi aamaal isi andaz se liye jaeyngey .''"
867,Janab Musab-bin-Saad bayan kartey hain ke maine apney Abba jaan (Hazrat Saad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) ke pehlu mein Namaz padhi. aur maine apney haathon ko (rukoo mein) apney ghutnon ke darmiyan rakha to unhoney mujhey is se manaa farmaya. maine phir waise hi kiya to unhone kaha : aisey mat karo. ham ( Sahaba Rasool ( ye kiya kartey they magar hamein us se rok diya gaya tha aur hukm diya gaya ke ham apney haathon ko ghutnon par rakha karen.''
868,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : jab tum mein se koi rukoo karey, to apney baazuon ko apni raanon par bichha liya kare aur apni hatheliyon ko eik dusri mein dey liya kare, goya ke main dekh raha hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ungliyan eik dusri ke andar hain."
869,Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab ( { فَسَبِّحْ بِاسْمِ رَبِّكَ الْعَظِيمِ } ( nazil hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isey apney rukoo mein karo.'' (yani (سبحان ربي العظيم) kaha karo) aur jab (سبح اسم ربك الأعلى) nazil hui to farmaya : ''isey apney sajdon mein karo.'' (yani (سبحان ربی الأعلى) kaha karo.'')
870,Janab Ayub-bin-Musa ya Musa-bin-Ayub ne apni qaum ke eik aadmi se unhoney Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se uskey ham-maani riwayat kiya hai. aur izafa kiya hai ke (in aayaat ke utarney par) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab rukoo kartey to kehtey : '' (سبحان ربي العظيم وبحمده) teen baar aur jab sajda kartey to kehtey : (سبحان ربي الأعلى وبحمده) teen baar. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ke hamarey khayal mein ye izafa mehfooz nahin hai. aur ehale-Misr in dono ahadis ko (hadees Rabeea aur hadees Ahmed-bin-Yunus ko) se bayan kerney mein munfarid (alag) hain.
871,Janab Shoba bayan kartey hain ke maine Sulaiman-bin-Mahraan Aamash se puchha : kya main Namaz mein takhweef ki aayaat padhtey waqt dua kar liya karun? to unhoney mujhey ba-sanad Saad-bin-Ubaida se bayan kiya ke Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi to wo rukoo mein (سبحان ربي العظيم) aur sajdey mein (سبحان ربي الأعلى) padhtey they. aur asnaaey (beech) qirat mein jis kisi aayate-rehmat se guzartey to wahan rukte aur sawal kartey aur jis kisi aayate-azab se guzartey to wahan rukte aur panah maangte.
872,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney sajde aur rukoo mein ye dua padha kartey they ( سُبُّوحٌ قُدُّوسٌ رَبُّ الْمَلَائِكَةِ وَالرُّوحِ ( ''mera Rab sharaakat , saajhey daari aur deegar tamam naqaayis aur kamiyon se bilkul paak hai. farishton ka Rab hai aur rooh ka bhi.''"
873,"Hazrat Auf-bin-Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke maine eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath qiyam kiya, aapney qiyam (namaz ka ( kiya to Sura-Baqra ki tilawat farmaai. aap jis kisi aayate-rehmat se guzartey to wahan rukte aur dua kartey aur jis kisi aayate-azab se guzartey to wahan rukte aur panah mangte. phir aapne rukoo kiya, is qadr lamba jitna ke aap ka qiyam tha. aap apney rukoo mein ye dua padhtey they : ( سُبْحَانَ ذِي الْجَبَرُوتِ . ... الخ ( ''paak hai wo zaat jo ghalba aur quwwat , milkiyat , badhai aur azmat wali hai.'' phir aapney sajda kiya, is qadr lamba jitna ke aap ka qiyam tha. aur aap apney sajdey mein bhi wohi dua padhtey rahey. phir khadey huey aur Sura-Aale-Imran ki qirat farmaee. phir eik surat padhi , ( baad iske eik aur) surat padhi.''"
874,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko raat mein Namaz padhtey huey dekha . aap kehtey they ( الله اكبر ( teen baar ( ذُو الْمَلَكُوتِ وَالْجَبَرُوتِ وَالْكِبْرِيَاءِ وَالْعَظَمَةِ ( ''Allah sab se bada hai, kamil milkiyat wala, ghalbey wala, badai aur azmat wala.'' phir aapney sanaa padhi . phir sura baqara ki qirat ki. phir rukoo kiya aur aap ka rukoo aap ke qiyam jaisa tha, aap rukoo mein ye dua padhtey they ( سبحان ربي العظيم سبحان ربي العظيم) phir rukoo se sar uthaya . aap ka ye qiyam pehley qiyam ki manind (lamba ( tha. aap yahan padhtey they (لربي الحمد) ''mere Rab ki hamd hai.'' phir sajda kiya to aap ka sajda bhi aap ke qiyam ki manind tha. aur aap sajdey mein kehtey they :(سبحان ربي الأعلى) ''paak hai mera rab jo sab se buland aur baala hai.'' phir aapney sajdey se sar uthaya , aur sajdon ke darmiyan baithey, itni der jitni ke sajdey mein lagai aur is dauran mein kehtey they : (رب اغفرلي رب اغفرلي) chunanche aapney chaar rakatein padhein aur in mein Sura-Baqara , Aale-Imran , Nisaa aur Maayda ya Anaam ki tilawat ki. Shoba ko shak hua hai."
875,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sajdey ki haalat mein banda apney Rab se sab se ziyada qarib hota hai, lihaza sajdey mein bahut ziyada dua kiya karo.''"
876,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul (naqal) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( apney marze-wafat ke dinon mein) parda hataaya jabke log Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey safein banaey huey they. aapne farmaya : ''logo ! nabuwat ki khushkhabriyon mein se sirf achcha khuwab hi baqi reh gaya hai jisey musalman dekh leta hai ya ( kisi ke liye ( usey dikha diya jata hai aur mujhe rukoo ya sajde ki haalat mein Quran padhney se mana kiya gaya hai. rukoo mein Rab taala ki azmat aur sajdey mein dua khoob kiya karo. ye is laaiq hoti hai ke qubul kar li jaey.''
877,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney rukoo aur sajdey mein kasrat se ye dua padha kartey they : ( سُبْحَانَكَ اللَّهُمَّ رَبَّنَا وَبِحَمْدِكَ اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْلِي ) ''paak hai to aey Allah ! aey hamarey Rab ! aur apni hamd ke sath . aey Allah ! mujhey bakhsh dey.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is dua se Qur'aani taaleem par amal farmatey they.
878,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney sajdon mein ye dua padha kartey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْلِي ذَنْبِي كُلَّهُ , دِقَّهُ , وَجِلَّهُ وَ أَوَّلَهُ وَ آخِرَهُ ( ibne-Sarah ne mazeed ye alfaz bhi bayan kiye :( عَلَانِيَتَهُ , وَسِرَّهُ ( ''aey Allah ! merey sab hi gunah maaf farma de, chhote-badey , pehle-pichhle aur jo zahir ya chhupey huey hain.''"
879,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke eik raat maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (unke bistar sey) gum paya to maine unhen unke musalley par tatola to paya ke aap sajdey mein they. aap ke paon khadey they aur aap ye kalimaat padh rahey they ( أَعُوذُ بِرِضَاكَ . . . . . الخ). ''(aey Allah !) main teri narazi se teri razamandi ki aur teri pakad se teri maafi ki panah chahta hun. main tujh se (dar kar) teri hi panah mein aata hun. main teri taareefaat-shumari nahin kar sakta. to waisa hi hai jaise ke to ne khud apni sanaa bayan ki hai.''
880,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni Namaz mein ye dua kartey they : (اللهم إني أعوذبك من عذاب القبر . .  الخ) ''aey Allah ! main azabe-qabr sey, teri panah chahta hun, mujhey Masih dajjaal ke fitne se mehfooz rakh , mujhey zindagi aur maut ke fitnon se mehfooz farma. aey Allah ! mujhey gunah ke kamon aur qarzey se bachaey rakh.'' kisi ne kaha ke aap qarzey se bahut panah maangtey hain? (is ki kya wajeh hai?) aapney farmaya : ''banda jab qarza ley leta hai, to baat karta hai to jhoot boltaa hai aur wada karta hai to pura nahin karta.''"
881,"Janab Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Laila apney walid se bayan kartey hain, kaha ke maine ( eik baar ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke pehlu mein khadey ho kar nafl Namaz padhi. maine aap ko suna kehtey they : (أعوذ بالله من النار ، ويل لأهل النار) ''aag se Allah ki panah. halakat hai dozakhiyon ke liye.''"
882,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz mein khadey huey aur ham bhi aap ke sath khadey ho gaey to eik badwi (dehati) ne Namaz mein yun kiya : (اللهم ارحمني و محمدا wla ترحم معنا أحدا) ''aey Allah ! mujh par rehem farma aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par , aur hamare sath kisi par rehem na farma.'' jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne salam phera to us badwi se kaha : ''tu ne wasee chiz ko tang kar diya.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ishara , Shan wale Allah  ki rehmat ki taraf tha."
883,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab (سبح اسم ربك الأعلى) ''apney Rab Aa'laa ki tasbih bayan kijiye.'' ki tilawat kartey to ( jawaaban ( farmatey : (سبحان ربي الأعلى) ''paak hai mera Rab jo sab se buland aur baala hai.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is hadees mein Wakee ki mukhalifat ki gaee hai. Abu-Wakee'e aur Shoba ne isey b-waasta Abu-Is'haq an Saeed-bin-Jubair an ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) mauqufan bayan kiya hai."
884,"Janab Musa-bin-abi-Aaisha (Taabai) bayan kartey hain ke (Sahaba mein sey) eik sahab apney ghar ki chhat par Namaz padhatey they. to jab wo (Sura-Qiyama ki aakhiri aayat) (أليس ذلك بقادر على أن يحيي الموتى) ''kya Allah qudrat nahin rakhta ke wo mardon ko zinda kar dey?'' padhtey to (jawab mein) kehtey (سبحانك فبلى) ''aey Allah ! to paak hai, to yaqinan qudrat rakhta hai.'' logon ne un se uskey baarey mein puchha , to unhoney kaha : maine isey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Imam Ahmed ka kehna hai ke mujhey ye baat ziyada pasand hai ke farz namazon mein Qur'aani duayen ki jaeyn ."
885,"Janab Saeed Jurairi , Sa'di se, wo apney walid ya chacha se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko unki Namaz mein bade ghaur se dekha hai. aap apne rukoo aur sajde mein itni der rukte they ke (سبحان الله وبحمده) teen baar keh lein."
886,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi rukoo kare to teen dafa kahe : ( سبحان ربي العظيم) aur ye kam se kam tadaad hai. aur jab sajda kare to kahe (سبحان ربي الأعلى) teen baar . aur ye kam se kam tadaad hai. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke ye hadees mursal (munqata'/silsile se kati hui) hai. Aun ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko nahin paya hai."
887,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo tum mein sura ( والتين والزيتون ( padhey aur uskey aakhir mein) أَلَيْسَ اللَّهُ بِأَحْكَمِ الْحَاكِمِينَ ( ''kya Allah sab haakimon se bada haakim nahin hai?'' par pahunchey to kahey ( بَلَى ! وَأَنَا عَلَى ذَلِكَ مِنْ الشَّاهِدِينَ ( '' kyon nahin ! aur main uski gawahi dene walon mein se hun'' aur jo Sura (القیامہ) padhey aur uskey aakhir mein) أَلَيْسَ ذَلِكَ بِقَادِرٍ عَلَى أَنْ يُحْيِيَ الْمَوْتَى ( ''kya wo is par qadir nahin ke mardon ko zinda kar sakey?'' to chahiye ke kahe : (بلى) ''kyon nahin, wo qadir hai.'' aur jo shakhs Sura (المرسلات) padhte huey is aayat par pahunche ( فَبِأَيِّ حَدِيثٍ بَعْدَهُ يُؤْمِنُونَ ( ''ye log iskey baad kis baat par imaan laeyn gey?''  to chahiye ke kahe : (aamna billaah) ''ham Allah par Imaan laye.'' Ismael kehtey hain ke main us ea'raab (dehaati) ke paas dobara gaya taake us se ye hadees dobara sunoon aur dekhun kahin wo ( bhoolaa to nahin) to usney kaha : aey bhatijey ! tumhara kya khayal hai ke maine is hadees ko yaad nahin rakha hoga? halanke maine saath (60) hajj kiye hain aur her hajj mein main jis jis oont par Sawar hota raha hun wo sab mujhey yaad hain."
888,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baad kisi ke peechhey Namaz nahin padhi ke uski Namaz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz se bahut ziyada mushabeh ho. siwaye us jawan ke yani Umar-bin-Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) ke . chunanche ham ne andaza lagaya ke wo apney rukoo aur sajdey mein das-das tasbeehaat kehtey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Ahmed-bin-Saleh kehtey hain ke maine apney Shaikh se puchha ke raawi ka naam manus (noon ke sath) hai ya maaboos (baa ke sath)? to unhoney kaha ke abdur-Razzaaq ne maaboos (baa ke sath) bayan kiya hai, magar mujhey manus (noon ke sath) yaad hai aur ye ibne-Raafe ke lafz hain. Ahmed ne apni riwayat mein عنعنہ ka istimal kartey huey ''عن(an) Saeed-bin-Jubair an (an) Anas-bin-Malik'' kaha. ( jabkey ibne-Raafe ne samaa, ki tasreeh (wazahat) ki hai.)"
889,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, Aapney farmaya : ''mujhey hukm diya gaya hai. ... ''  Hammad ke alfaz hain. . . . . . tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hukm diya gaya hai ke ''saat (aa'zaa / angon) par sajda keren aur is dauran mein apney baalon ya kapdon ko na sameten.''"
890,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karte hain ke Aapne farmaya : ''mujhey hukm diya gaya hai.'' aur kabhi-kabhi kehte, tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hukm diya gaya hai ke ''saat aaza par sajda karen.''"
891,"Hazrat Abbas-bin-Abdul-Muttalib se marwi (bayan) hai, unhone Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmate suna : ''banda jab sajda karta hai to uske sath saat aaza sajda karte hain : chehra , dono haath , dono ghutney aur dono paon.''"
892,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) marfooan bayan kartey hain : '' haath bhi sajda kartey hain jaisey ke chehra sajda karta hai. jab tum mein se koi ( sajdey mein zameen par) apna chehra rakhey to haath bhi (zameen par) rakhey aur jab (chehra) uthae to unhen bhi utha le.''
893,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum Namaz ke liye aao aur ham sajdey mein hon to tum bhi sajda karo aur usey kuch shumar na karo. aur jisney rakaat ko pa liya usney Namaz ko pa liya.''"
894,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne logon ko eik Namaz padhaai to us mein dekha gaya ke aap ki peshani aur naak ke baanse par keechad ka nishan tha.
895,Muhammad-bin-Yahya ba-waasta Abdur-Razzaaq Maamer se usi ki manind riwayat kartey hain.
896,"Janab Abu-Is'haq bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamen sajda karkey dikhaya . yun ke unhoney (pehley) apney haath rakhey , apney ghutnon par tek lagai aur apni sireen (peeth) ko ooncha kiya aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is tarah sajda kiya karte the."
897,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sajda sahih tarah ( sukoon ( se kiya karo . aur tum mein se koi kuttey ki tarah apne haath na phailaey.''
898,"Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) bayan farmati hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab sajda karte to apne haathon ko apne pahluon se door rakhte the yahan tak ke agar bakri ka bachcha aap ke haathon ke nichey se guzarnaa chahta , to guzar sakta tha."
899,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhe se aaya (jabke aap sajde mein the) to maine aap ki baghlon ki safedi dekhi. Aapney apni kamar ko uthaya hua tha, pet zameen se ooncha tha aur bazu pahluon se door the."
900,Hazrat Ahmar-bin-Juz (Raziallahu anhu) sahabi Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab sajda karte to apne haathon ko apney pahluon se (is qadr ( door rakhtey the ke hamein (aap ki mashaqqat ko dekhtey huey) aap par taras aata.
901,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karte hain ke Aapne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi sajda kare to apne haathon ko (zameen par) kutte ki tarah na phailaey aur apni raanon ko mila kar rakhe.''
902,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karte hain ke Sahaba kiram ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se shikayat ki ke jab wo sajde mein apney baazuon ko khola karte hain to us se bahut mashaqqat hoti hai, to Aapne farmaya : ''apne ghutnon se madad ley liya karo.''"
903,"Janab Ziyad-bin-Sabeeh Hanfi bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath khadey ho kar Namaz padhi , maine us dauran mein apne haath apne pahluon ( کوکھوں ( par rakh liye . jab wo Namaz se farigh hue to farmaya : ye keyfiyat Namaz mein saleeb (masloob/diye jane) se mushaabihat hai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us se mana farmaya kartey the."
904,Janab mutrif apney walid se bayan karte hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha Aap Namaz padh rahe the aur aap ke seene se rone ki wajeh se aise aawaz aa rahi thi jaise koi chakki si chal rahi ho.
905,Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs wuzu kare aur achcha wuzu kare (yani sunnat ke mutabiq) phir do rakatein padhe aur un mein ghaflat ka shikar na ho to uske sabiqa (pichhle) gunah maaf kar diye jate hain.''
906,"Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi wuzu kare aur achcha wuzu kare phir do rakatein padhe aur wo apne dil aur chehre se un hi par mutawajjeh rahe, to uske liye jannat wajib ho gaee.''"
907,"Hazrat Miswar-bin-Yazid maaliki (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, Aapne Namaz mein qirat farmaee aur is mein se kuch aayaat chhoot gaeen jinhen Aapne tilawat nahin farmaya, to eik aadmi ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Aapney falan falan aayat chhod di hai. aapne farmaya : '' to to ne mujhey yaad kyon na kara di? '' Sulaiman ne apni riwayat mein kaha ke is aadmi ne kaha : main samjha shayad ye mansookh ho gaee hain. Sulaiman ne is sanad ko yun bayan kiya. . . . . . (حدثنا يحيى بن كثير الأسدي قال : حدثنی المسور بن يزيد الأسدی المالكي ) (yani wazahate tahdees aur wazahate nasab ke sath) . (B) Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik Namaz padhi aur us mein qirat ki, to kuch khalt-malt ho gaya. jab farigh huey to Hazrat Ubai (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''kya tum ne hamarey sath Namaz padhi hai? '' unhone kaha : ji haan . aapne farmaya : '' to tumhen kis chiz ne roka tha (ke mujhey bata detey).''"
908,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Ali ! Imam ko Namaz mein luqma mat do. Imam Abu-Dawud kehte hain ke Abu-Is'haq ne Haris se sirf chaar ahadis suni hain aur ye un mein se nahin hai.
909,Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''banda jab Namaz mein hota hai to Shan wala Allah uski taraf barabar mutawajjeh rehta hai jab tak ke wo idhar-udhar na dekhe. jab wo idhar-udhar dekhne lag jaey to Allah bhi us se munh mod leta hai.''
910,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, wo kehti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha ke aadmi ka Namaz ke dauran mein idhar-udhar dekhna kaisa hai? aapney farmaya : ''ye uchakna hai.'' is tarah se shaitan bandey ki Namaz se uchak leta hai."
911,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul (naqal ki gaee) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha gaya ke aapney logon ko Namaz padhaai to aap ki peshani aur naak ke baanse par keechad ka nishan tha. Abu-Ali kehte hain ki Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne jab chauthi baar apni ye kitab talaamiza (shagird) par padhi to us mein ye hadees na thi.
912,Hazrat Jabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se manqool (naqal ki gaee) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein tashrif laye aur dekha ke kuch log Namaz padh rahe hain aur apne haath aasman ki taraf uthaey huey hain to Aapney farmaya : '' ya to log Namaz main apni nazren aasman ki taraf uthane se baaz aa jaeyn ya unki nazren unki taraf wapis nahin lautengi.''
913,Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logon ko kya hua hai ke apni namazon ke dauran nazren utha lete hain?'' Aap ka farman is baare mein bada sakht ho gaya aur farmaya : ''ye log apney is amal se baaz aa jaeyn warna unki nazren uchak li jaeyngi.''
914,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik ooni chadar mein Namaz padhi , us mein kuch naqsh aur nigaar they. Aapney farmaya : ''mujhey iske nuqoosh uljhaane lage the. ise Abu-Jahim ke paas le jao aur mere paas anbijani chadar le aao.'' (yani jis mein naqsh nahin hote.)"
915,Janab Hisham ne apney walid se unhone Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se ye hadees bayan ki . Aapne Abu-Jahim ki (chaadaron mein sey) kurdi chadar le li. Aap se kaha gaya ke ooni (munaqqash) chadar is kurdi se umda thi.
916,Hazrat Sehal-bin-Hanzala (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karte hain ke Namaze-Fajr ki iqaamat kahi gaee aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padhaane lage aur aap us dauran main eik ghaati ki taraf dekh rahe the. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya ke aapne eik shehsawaar ko us ghaati ki taraf raat mein pehrey ke liye bheja tha.
917,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul (naqal ki gaee) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (kabhi-kabhi apni nawaasi) Umaama-binte-Zainab (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko utha kar Namaz padhatey they. jab sajda kartey to usey bitha detey aur jab khadey hotey to usey utha letey.
918,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik baar ham masjid mein baithey huey the ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye. Aap Umaama-binte-abi-al-Aas-bin-Rabeea ko uthaey huey the. aur uski walida Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki saahibzaadi Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) thin, ye chhoti bachchi thi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey apney kandhey par uthaya hua tha. Aapne Namaz padhaai aur ye aap ke kandhe par thi , aap jab rukoo karte to usey neeche bitha dete aur jab khade hote to usey utha lete. Aapne (isi tarah) Namaz mukammal ki aur is dauran mein usey uthate aur bithaate rahe."
919,Hazrat Abu-Qatada Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) farmate hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap logon ko Namaz padhaane ke dauran mein Umaama dukhtar abi-al-Aas ko apni gardan (yani kandhe) par uthae huey the. aap jab sajda karte to usey neeche bitha dete. Imam Abu-Dawud farmate hain ke Janab Makhrima ne apne walid ( Bukair-bin-Abdullah-bin-Ash'aj) se eik hi hadees suni hai.
920,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada sahabi Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marwi (bayan) hai, wo kehte hain ke eik baar ham Namaz ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka intizar kar rahe the, Namaze-Zohar ki thi ya Asr ki. aur Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap ko Namaz ke liye bulaya . jab aap tashrif laye to Umaama-binte-abi-al-Aas yani aap ki saahibzaadi ( Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ( ki beti aap ki gardan par thi. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apne musalle par khade huey aur ham bhi aap ke peeche khade ho gaey jabke wo bachchi apni usi jagah par thi (yani aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki gardan par.) Aapne takbir kahi to ham ne bhi takbir kahi. yahan tak ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rukoo karna chaha to usey pakad kar bitha diya, phir rukoo kiya aur sajda kiya. jab Aap apney sajdey se farigh huey aur khade huey to usey phir gardan (kandhe) par bitha liya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her rakaat mein aise hi karte rahe, yahan tak ke apni Namaz se farigh ho gaey."
921,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Namaz padhtey huey bhi do kaale janwaron ko qatl kar do yani saanp aur bichho.''
922,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padh rahey hotey , main aati aur darwaza khulwaati to aap chal kar darwaza khol detey aur phir apney musalley par lot aatey. aur (Urwa ne) zikr kiya ke darwaza qibla rukh tha."
923,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko salam kehtey they jabkey aap Namaz mein hotey to aap hamein salam ka jawab detey . isliye jab ham ( hijrate-habsha ke baad) Najashi ke paas se wapis aaye aur ham ne aap ko salam kiya to aapney hamein jawab na diya aur farmaya : ''Namaz main eik aur hi mashghooliyat hai.''
924,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham Namaz mein salam kaha kartey they aur apni zarurat ki baat bhi logon se kar letey they, phir main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya, jabke aap Namaz padh rahey they, maine aap ko salam kiya, lekin aapney merey salam ka jawab nahin diya. us se mujhey bahut gham laahiq hua aur agley pichhley andeshon ne aa liya. phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz mukammal kar li to farmaya : ''Shan wala Allah apney ehkam mein jo chahta hai tabdeeli karta hai. usney ab ye hukm diya hai ke Namaz ke dauran mein baat cheet na kiya karo.'' tab aapney merey salam ka jawab diya."
925,Hazrat Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se guzra jabke aap Namaz padh rahey they. maine aap ko salam kaha to aapney isharey se jawab diya.Naabil kehtey hain jahan tak main janta hun Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye kaha tha : apni ungli se ishara kiya. ye alfaz Janab Quteba ki riwayat ke hain.
926,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey qabeela-bani-mustaliq ki taraf bheja. main aaya to aap apney oont par Namaz padh rahey they. maine aap se baat karna chahi to aapney mujhey apney haath se yun ishara kiya. maine phir baat ki to aapney mujhey apney haath se yun ishara kiya. main aap ko sun raha tha ke aap qirat kar rahey they aur (rukoo' sajde ke liye) apney sar se ishara kar rahey they. jab farigh huey to farmaya : ''jis kaam ke liye maine tumhen bheja tha uska tum ne kya kiya ? aur tum se baat na karney ki wajeh ye thi ke main Namaz padh raha tha.''
927,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (masjid) qubaa mein Namaz padhney ke liye tashrif ley gaey. (us beech mein aap ke paas) ansaar aagey . wo aap ko salam kehtey they jabkey aap Namaz padh rahey they. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kis tarah jawab detey huey dekha, jabke aap Namaz padh rahey they aur wo log aap ko salam kehtey they? unhoney kaha : is tarah aur apni hatheli phailai. (Husain-bin-Esa ne apney shaikh Jaafar-bin-Aun se uski wazahat yun naqal ki hai ke) Jaafar-bin-Aun ne apney haath ki hatheli ko nichey kiya aur uski pusht ko ooper ki taraf."
928,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : '' Namaz aur salam mein nuqs nahin.'' (yani kami na rakho. Imam Ahmed farmatey hain : main samajhta hun ke aap salam karen, na aap par salam kiya jaey. aur Namaz mein insan ka kami karna yun hai ke insan Namaz se farigh ho jaey halanke usey is mein shak ho."
929,Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Muawiya ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke unhoney marfoo bayan kiya. ''salam mein aur Namaz mein nuqs nahin.'' Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain : ibne-Fuzail ne ibne-Mehdi ki (sabiqa riwayat) ki manind riwayat kiya aur marfoo nahin kiya.
930,"Hazrat Muaawiya-bin-Hakam Salma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi aur qaum mein se eik aadmi ne chheenk maari , to maine kaha (يرحمك الله) ''Allah tum par rehem farmaey.'' is par logon ne mujhey tez nazron se dekha to maine kaha : afsos meri maa ka mujhey gum karna ! tumhen kya hua hai ke mujhey is tarah dekh rahey ho? (us par) un logon ne apney haath apni raanon par maarney shuru kar diye, tab mujhey maloom hua ke ye mujhey khamosh kara rahey hain. (ustaad) Usman ne bayan kiya ke jab maine unhen dekha ke ye log mujhey khamosh kara rahey hain (to mujhey ghussa to aaya) magar main khamosh raha. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz padh li, merey maa-baap aap par qurban ! aapney mujhey maara na daantaa , na sakht sust kaha, balke farmaya : ''ye Namaz hai, is mein logon ki si aam baat cheet jayez nahin hai. is mein tasbih hoti hai, takbir hoti hai aur Quran majeed padha jata hai.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne isi qisam ki baat farmaee. maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham log naey-naey jahiliyat se bahir aaye hain aur Allah ne hamein Islam ( ki nemat ( se nawaza hai. to ham mein kuch log hain jo kaahinon ke paas jatey hain. aapney farmaya : ''tum unke paas na jaya karo.'' maine arz kiya : ham mein kuch log ( parindon waghaira sey) badshaguni letey hain. aapney farmaya : ''ye unke dilon ke auhaam hain. ye chizen unke liye rukawat nahin ban-ni chaahiyen.'' maine arz kiya : ham mein kuch log hain jo lakeerein khinchtey hain. aapney farmaya : '' sabiqa anbiya mein se eik Nabi they jo lakeerein khincha kartey they, to jiski lakeerein unke muwaafiq hon wo to sahih ho sakti hain.'' (lekin ab ye jan-na mushkil hai.) maine kaha : meri eik londi hai jo uhud aur jawaaniya ki atraaf (aas-pas) mein meri kuch bakriyan charaaya karti thi. maine eik baar us par chhaapa maara to dekha ke bhediya un mein se eik bakri ley gaya hai aur main bhi Adam ki aulad mein se hun, jis tarah unhen afsos hota hai mujhey bhi hua to maine usey thappad dey maara, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko mere liye bada bhari aur bura amal jana. maine kaha : kya main usey azad na kar dun? aapney farmaya : ''usey merey paas lao.'' chunanche main usey aap ki khidmat mein ley aaya. aapney us se puchha : ''Allah kahan hai? '' usney kaha : aasman mein. aapney farmaya : ''main kaun hun?'' usney kaha : aap Allah ke Rasool hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isko azad kar do bila-shuba ye momina hai.''"
931,"Hazrat Muaawiya-bin-Hakam Salma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Islam ke kuch ehkam jaan liye . un mein se eik ye bhi jana ke mujhey kaha gaya : jab tumhen chheenk aaye to ( الحمد الله ( kaho aur jab koi doosra chheenk maarey aur) الحمد الله ( kahe , to tum usey (يرحمك الله ( se jawab do. chunanche main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz mein khada tha ke eik shakhs ne chheenk maari aur usney ( الحمد الله ( kaha, maine kaha : ( يرحمك الله (aur oonchi aawaz se kaha, to logon ne mujhey tez nazron se dekha . us se mujhey ghussa aaya aur maine kaha : tumhen kya hua hai ke mujhey ghoor-ghoor ke dekh rahey ho? is par unhoney (Subhan-Allah) kaha . phir jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz mukammal kar li to farmaya : '' baaten kaun kar raha tha? ''kaha gaya ke ye badwi (dehati). to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey bulaya aur mujh se farmaya : '' Namaz mein Quran majeed ki tilawat hoti hai aur Allah ka zikr , to jab tum Namaz mein hua karo to tumhara yehi kaam hona chahiye.'' gharz maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se badh kar koi shafiq muallim nahin dekha."
932,Hazrat Wayal-bin-Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab (Sura Fatiha ke aakhir mein) (ولا الضالين) kehtey to (aameen  kehtey aur uskey sath apni aawaz ko buland kartey.
933,"Hazrat Wayal-bin-Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padhi to aapney oonchi aawaz se ( aameen ( kahi . aur) jab Namaz se farigh huey to ( daeyn, baeyn janib salam phera, yahan tak ke maine aap ke rukhsaaron ki safedi dekhi."
934,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab (غير المغضوب عليهم wla الضالين) padhtey to ( aameen ( kehtey yahan tak ke saf awwal ke log jo aap se qarib hotey aap ki aawaz sun letey.
935,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain aapney farmaya : ''jab Imam (غير المغضوب عليهم wla الضالين) kahe , to tum (aameen) kaho kyonkey jis ka ye qaul malaaika ke qaul ke muwaafiq ho gaya uskey sabiqa gunah bakhsh diye jaeyngey .''"
936,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jab Imam ( aameen ( kahe to tum bhi) aameen ( kaho kyonkey jiski ( aameen ( farishton ki) aameen (ke muwaafiq ho gaee uskey pichley gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey.'' ibne-Shahab kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( aameen ( kaha kartey they.
937,Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ( aameen ( kehney mein mujh se jaldi na farmaiye.
938,"Abu-Musabbih Maqrai bayan kartey hain ke ham Hazrat Abu-Zuhair Numairi ki majlis mein baitha kartey they aur ye Sahaba mein se they aur badi achhi-achhi hadise bayan kartey they to ham mein se jab koi dua karta to farmaya kartey ke isey ( aameen ( ki mohar lagao .) aameen ( mohar ki manind hai jo kisi khat par laga di jati hai. Abu-Zuhair ne farmaya : main tumhen uskey mutalliq batata hun, ham eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath nikley aur eik shakhs par pahunchey jabke wo bahut lagaaw aur mubaalghe se dua kar raha tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ruk gaey aur uski dua suntey rahey . phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uski dua qubul ho gaee ba-sharte-ke mohar kar dey.'' sathiyon mein se eik ne puchha : kis chiz se mohar karey? aapney farmaya : '' ( aameen ( se bila-shuba agar usney apni dua ( aameen ( se khatam ki) ya mohar lagai ( to qubul ho gaee.'' chunanche wo jisney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye puchha tha, is dua kerney waley ke paas gaya aur usey kaha : aey falan ! apni dua ko) aameen ( se mohar kar do aur khushkhabri qubul karo . ye alfaz Mehmood ke hain. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke ''maqrai '' himyer ka eik matahat qabeela hai."
939,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tasbih ( Subhan-Allah kehna ( mardon ke liye hai aur taali bajana aurton ke liye.''
940,"Hazrat Sahal-bin-Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qabeela bani-Amr-bin-Auf (qubaa) mein suleh karaney ke liye tashrif ley gaey. Namaz ka waqt ho gaya, to muazzan Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur kaha : kya aap Namaz padhaein gey , to main iqaamat kahun? unhoney kaha : haan . chunanche Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Namaz shuru ki aur udhar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye aur chaltey aaye , yahan tak ke saf mein khadey ho gaey, logon ne taliyan bajaani shuru kar di. aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz mein idhar-udhar na dekhtey they ( mutawajjeh na hotey they ( lekin jab logon ne bahut ziyada taliyan bajaain to aap mutawajjeh huey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekh liya . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen ishara kya ke apni jagah par thehrey raho. to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apney dono haath ooper uthaey . aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo unhen hukm diya tha us par Allah ki hamd ki aur phir peechhey hatt aaye , yahan tak ke saf mein barabar ho gaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aagey badh gaey aur Namaz padhaai . jab Namaz se farigh huey to farmaya : ''aey Abu-Bakar ! tumhen kya rukawat thi ke tum rukey rehtey jab maine tumhen keh diya tha?'' Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : ibne-Abi-Quhaafa ko zeb na deta tha ke Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke aagey ho kar Namaz padhaaey . phir aapney farmaya : ''tum logon ko kya hua tha ke is qadr taliyan bajaney lagey they? jisey Namaz mein koi masla ho wo (Subhan-Allah) kaha karey. jab wo (Subhan-Allah) kahega to uski taraf tawajjoh ki jaeygi . taliyan to aurton ke liye hain. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke ye farz Namaz mein hai."
941,"Hazrat Sahal-bin-Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke qabeela bani-Amr-bin-Auf mein koi jhagda ho gaya tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khabar pahunchi to aap Zohar ke baad un mein suleh karaney ke liye tashrif ley gaey aur Bilal se farma gaey : ''agar namaze-Asr ka waqt ho jaey aur main na pahunch sakoon to Abu-Bakar se kehna ke logon ko Namaz padha den.'' chunanche jab Asr ka waqt hua Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Azan kahi , phir iqaamat kahi aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se Namaz padhaaney ko kaha, wo aagey badh gaey. is riwayat ke aakhir mein hai : ''jab tumhen Namaz mein koi masla pesh aa jaey to mard (Subhan-Allah) kaha keren aur aurten taali bajaaein.''"
942,Janab Esa-bin-Ayub bayan kartey hain ke aurton ka taali bajana yun hai ke wo apney daain haath ki do ungliyan apni baain hatheli par maaren .
943,Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz mein ishara kar diya kartey they.
944,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(Subhan-Allah) kehna mardon ke liye hai.'' yani Namaz mein .''aur taali bajana aurton ke liye hai. aur jisney apni Namaz mein koi aisa ishara kiya jo koi mafhoom rakhta ho to wo apni Namaz dohraaey . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye hadees weham hai.
945,Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain : ''jab tum mein se koi Namaz ke liye khada hota hai to ( Allah ki) rehmat uskey rubaru hoti hai lihaza kankariyaan na chhua karey.''
946,Hazrat Muaiqeeb (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Namaz padhtey huey kankariyaan mat chhuo. agar aisa karna hi hai to eik baar barabar kar lo.''
947,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz ke dauran mein pahluon par haath rakhney se mana farmaya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : ( الاختصار في الصلاة (ka maani hai apney pahluon (yani kokhon) par haath rakhna.
948,"Janab Hilal-bin-Yasaaf kehtey hain ke main ( shaam ke ilaaqe ( ruqa mein aaya to merey doston ne mujhey kaha : kya tum kisi sahabi Rasool se milna chahtey ho? maine kaha : ( kyon nahin) ye to ghanimat hai. chunanche ham Hazrat Wabisa (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein pahunchey. maine apney sathi se kaha : pehley to ham unki zahiri waza' qata' dekhtey hain. to ham ne dekha ke aap ke sar par topi hai sar se chipki hui aur kanon wali , aur khaz ( resham (ka jubba tha matyaaley rang ka aur aap Namaz padh rahey they aur apni lathi ka sahara liye huey they. salam ke baad ham ne ( ye masla ( puchha to farmaya : mujh se Umme-Qais-binte-Mohsin (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab badi umr ke ho gaey aur kuch farba bhi , to aap ki jaey Namaz ke paas eik sutoon tha aap uska sahara liya kartey they."
949,Hazrat Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke) ibtadaaey Islam mein) hamara eik sathi Namaz ke dauran mein apney sath waley se baat kar liya karta tha. yahan tak ke aayate-kareema (وقُومُوا للہ قَانِتِينَ) nazil hui . ''yani Allah ke huzur khamosh ba-adab ho ke khadey hua karo.'' chunanche hamen khamoshi ka hukm diya gaya aur baat cheet se rok diya gaya.
950,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain, mujh se bayan kiya gaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aadmi ka baith kar Namaz padhna aadhi Namaz hai.'' main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap ko paya ke aap baith kar Namaz padh rahey they. maine apney sar par haath rakh liya to aapney daryaft farmaya : ''Abdullah-bin-Amr ! kya baat hai?'' maine arz kiya : ''aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey bataya gaya hai ke aapney farmaya hai : '' aadmi ka baith kar Namaz padhna aadhi Namaz hai aur aap baith kar Namaz padh rahey hain?'' aapney farmaya : ''haan , lekin main tumhari tarah nahin hun.''"
951,Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se baith kar Namaz padhney ke mutalliq sawal kiya to aapney farmaya : ''khadey ho kar Namaz padhna baith kar Namaz padhney ki nisbat afzal hai. aur baithney waley ki Namaz khadey ho kar padhney waley ke muqabley mein aadhi hoti hai. aur let kar padhney waley ki Namaz baith kar padhney waley ki nisbat aadhi hoti hai.''
952,"Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke mujhey naasoor tha. isliye is baarey mein maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se maloom kiya to aapney farmaya : ''Namaz khadey ho kar padho , agar himmat na ho to baith kar aur agar uski bhi taqat na ho to pehlu ke bal let kar.''"
953,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko budhapa aaney se pehley maine kabhi nahin dekha tha ke raat ki Namaz mein aapney baith kar qirat ki ho, magar jab boodhey ho gaey to baith kar qirat kiya kartey they, yahan tak ke jab tees ya chaalis aayaten baqi reh jatin to unhen khadey ho kar padhtey, phir sajda kartey."
954,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baith kar Namaz padhtey they aur isi haalat mein qirat kartey rehtey yahan tak ke jab aap ki qirat mein se tees ya chaalis aayaten baqi hotin to khadey ho jatey aur qirat kartey, phir rukoo aur sajda kartey. iskey baad dusri rakaat mein bhi aisey hi kartey. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke is hadees ko Alqama-bin-Waqas ne bhi Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se isi ki manind riwayat kiya hai."
955,Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ka lamba hissey khadey ho kar Namaz padhtey aur eik lamba hissey baith kar padhtey. aur jab khadey ho kar padhtey to rukoo bhi khadey ho kar kartey aur jab baith kar padhtey to rukoo bhi baith kar kartey.
956,Janab Abdullah-bin-Shaqiq bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik rakat mein) eik se zayed ( suraten padha kartey they? unhoney kaha : ( haan ( hissey mufassal se. ( Sura Qaaf se aakhir Quran tak ki soorton ko mufassal kaha jata hai.) maine puchha : kya aap baith kar Namaz padha kartey they? unhoney kaha : ( haan ( jab logon ne aap ko thakaa diya tha.
957,"Hazrat Wayal-bin-Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine kaha main bil-zaroor dekhun ga ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz kaisey padhtey hain? bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huey aur qibley ki taraf rukh kiya, ( الله اكبر ( kaha aur apney dono haath uthaey , yahan tak ke aap ke kanon ke barabar aagey . phir aapney apney baeyn haath ko apney daain se pakad liya . phir jab rukoo ka irada kiya to apney dono haathon ko isi tarah uthaya . bayan kiya ke phir aap baith gaey aur apna baayan paon bichha liya aur apna baayan haath baain raan par rakh liya aur daain haath ki kohni ke kinarey ko apni daain raan par rakha aur do ungliyon ko band karkey halqa bana liya . maine aap ko dekha ke aap is tarah kartey they. ... Janab Bishr ne angoothey aur beech ki ungli se halqa banaya aur shahadat ki ungli se ishara karkey dikhaya."
958,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan farmatey hain ke Namaz mein sunnat ye hai ke aap apney daain paon ko khada kar lein aur baeyn paon ko bichha kar baithein.
959,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey they ke tumhara apney baeyn paon ko bichha lena aur daain ko khada karkey baithna Namaz ki sunnaton mein se hai.
960,Usman-bin-abi-Sheba ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ki manind bayan kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Yahya ki sanad mein (من السنة) ka lafz kaha hai jaisey ke Jarir ne kaha hai.
961,Janab Yahya-bin-Saeed kehtey hain ke Qasim-bin-Muhammad ne unko tashahud mein baithney ki kaifiyat dikhlaai aur hadees zikr ki.
962,Janab Ibrahim (bin-Yazid Nakhai Faqeeh ehale koofa) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Namaz mein baithtey to apney baeyn paon ko bichha liya kartey they. (aur musalsal is tarah kerney sey) unke paon ki pusht siyah ho gaee thi.
963,"Hazrat Abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne as-haabe-Rasul (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki das afrad ki jamaat mein bayan kiya, in mein Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. Hazrat Abu-Humaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main tum mein se sab se ziyada Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ke mutalliq janta hun. unhoney kaha : bayan karo . to unhoney hadees bayan ki aur kaha : aur sajdey mein apney paon ki ungliyan ( qibla rukh ( mod letey , phir ( الله اكبر ( keh kar apna sar uthatey aur apna baayan paon tedha ( mod ( karkey us par baith jatey. phir dusri rakaat mein aisey hi kartey. aur hadees tafsil se zikr ki aur bayan kiya ke jab us rakaat mein hotey jis mein salam hota hai, to apney baeyn paon ko eik taraf nikal letey aur apney baeyn hissey par baith jatey Ahmed ne is qadr izafa kiya ke in Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ne ( Hazrat Abu-Humaid sey) kaha : aapney sach aur sahih kaha hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisey hi Namaz padha kartey they. aur Imam Ahmed-bin-Hanbal (Rahimahullah) aur Musaddad ne do rakaaton par baithney ki kaifiyat bayan nahin ki."
964,Janab Muhammad-bin-Amr-bin-Ata bayan kartey hain ke wo chand shaaba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath baithey huey they. yehi (mazkura ( hadees bayan ki . unhoney (yani Esa-bin-Ibrahim ne) Abu-Qatada ka zikr nahin kiya. kaha ke jab aap do rakaaton par baithtey to apney baeyn paon par baithtey aur jab aakhiri rakaat hoti to apney baeyn paon ko eik taraf nikal detey aur apni peeth (peeth) par baith jatey ( jisey tawar-ruk kaha jata hai) .
965,"Janab Muhammad-bin-Amr Aamiri bayan kartey hain ke main us majlis mein mojud tha ( jis mein ke das as-haab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baithey they aur Hazrat Abu-Humaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko Namaz padh kar dikhai thi ( unhoney is mein bayan kiya : jab aap do rakaaton ke baad baithtey , to apney baeyn paon ke talwey par baithtey aur daain ko khada kar letey they. aur jab chauthi rakaat hoti to apni baain peeth ko zameen par rakh letey aur apney dono paon ko eik janib nikal letey."
966,"Janab Abbas (ya Ayash (bin Sehal Saaidi bayan kartey hain ke wo bhi is majlis mein maujud they jis mein unke walid hazir they. is mein bayan kiya ke . . . . isliye sajda kiya aur jab uthey to apni dono hatheliyon , ghutnon aur apney paon ke panjon par uthey, is dauraan haalanki aap baithey huey they. phir aapney tawar-ruk kiya (yani apni peeth par baithey) aur doosrey paon ko khada kar liya . phir takbir kahi aur sajda kiya. phir takbir kahi aur khadey ho gaey aur tawar-ruk na kiya. aur dusri rakaat padhi aur isi tarah takbir kahi, phir baith gaey . do rakaaton ke baad . yahan tak ke jab khadey honey ka irada kiya to takbir keh kar khadey ho gaey aur phir dusri do rak'atein padhein aur jab salam kiya to apni daain aur baeyn janib salam kiya. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke Esa-bin-Abdullah ne wo kuch zikr nahin kiya jo kuch ke Abdul-Humaid ne tawar-ruk aur do rakaaton se uthtey waqt raful-yadain ka zikr kiya hai."
967,"Janab Abbas-bin-Sahal kehtey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Humaid , Abu-Usaid , Sahal-bin-Saad aur Muhammad-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ikhattey huey . . . . . aur ye hadees bayan ki . aur is mein do rakaaton se uth kar raful-yadain aur baithney ka zikr nahin kiya. kaha yahan tak ke jab aakhir mein pahunchey to baith gaey, baeyn paon ko bichha liya aur apney daain paon ke panjey ko qibley ki taraf kar liya."
968,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz mein baitha kartey they to kaha kartey they (السلام على الله قبل عباده) ''Allah par uskey bandon se pehley (ya uskey bandon ki taraf sey) salam ho, salam ho falan par , salam ho falan par.''  to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah par salam mat kaha karo, Allah to khud sarapa salam hai.'' lekin jab tum mein se koi baithey to yun kaha karey : (التَّحِيَّاتُ لِلَّهِ . ... الخ ( '' tamam tarah ki zabani aur maali ibadaten Allah hi ke liye khas hain. salam ho aap par aey Nabi ! aur Allah ki rahmatein aur barkaten. salam ho ham par aur Allah ke nek saleh bandon par.'' tum log jab ye kaho gey to tumhari ye dua aasman aur zameen aur unke darmiyan sab saleh bandon ke liye hogi. (iskey baad ye kaha karo.) (أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله . .  الخ) ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ki Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain.'' phir chahiye ke dua karey jo uskey nazdik sab se ziyada pasandida ho.''"
969,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham nahin jantey they ke Namaz mein jab baithen to kya padhein aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sikhaya gaya tha. phir unhoney mazkura baala hadees ki manind bayan kiya.  Janab shareek ne ( اخبرنا Jaame يعني ibn Shaddad , an (an) abi Wayl , an (an) Abdullah ( (Raziallahu anhu) usi ki jaisi bayan kiya. kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen kaee tarah ke kalimaat sikhatey they, magar jis ehtimam se kalimaate tashahud taaleem farmatey they, deegar mein aisey na hota tha. (ghair tashahud ke azkaar mein se ye bhi hai) (اللَّهُمَّ أَلِّفْ بَيْنَ قُلُوبِنَا وَأَصْلِحْ ذَاتَ بَيْنِنَا . ... الخ ( ''aey Allah ! hamarey dilon mein (eik doosrey ki) ulfat paida farma dey aur hamarey aapas ke rawaabit ko umda bana dey. hamen salamti ke raaston ki rehnumai farma aur andheron se bacha kar Noor mein pahuncha dey aur tamam tarah ki zahiri aur chupi badkaariyon se mehfooz rakh . hamarey kanon , aakhon , dilon , ghar waaliyon ( biwiyon (aur bachchon mein barkaten ata farma .) aey Allah ! (aur ham par ruju farma ( hamari tauba qubul kar) bila-shuba to bahut ziyada tauba qubul kerney wala aur rehmat kerney wala hai hamein apni nematon ka shukr kerney wala bana dey aur ye ke ham inka jaisa haq tha aetiraaf keren aur inhen bar-mahal istimal mein laeyn aur in nematon ko ham par kamil farma dey.''"
970,"Qasim-bin-Mukhaimira kehtey hain ke Janab Alqama ne mera haath pakda aur bayan kiya ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne mera haath pakda aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ka haath pakda aur unhen Namaz mein tashahud ke kalimaat taaleem farmaai . aur hadees Aamash ki dua ke manind bayan kiya. aur kaha : ''jab tum ye keh lo , ya farmaya : pura kar lo , to tum ne apni Namaz puri kar li . agar chaho to uth jao aur agar chaho to baithey raho.''"
971,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se tashahud ke ye kalimaat bayan kartey hain : ( التَّحِيَّاتُ لِلَّهِ , الصَّلَوَاتُ الطَّيِّبَاتُ , السَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ أَيُّهَا النَّبِيُّ وَرَحْمَةُ اللَّهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهُ ) ''tamam tarah ki azmatein Allah ke liye hain. (ibadat ka mustahiq bhi wohi hai.) pakizah kalimaat , azkaar aur duaeyn Allah ke liye , salamti ho aap par aey Allah ke Nabi ! aur uski rahmatein aur barkaten.'' Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke) وبركاته (ka lafz meri taraf se izafa hai. ( السَّلَامُ عَلَيْنَا وَعَلَى عِبَادِ اللَّهِ الصَّالِحِينَ . أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا الله وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ ) ''salamti ho ham par aur Allah ke saleh bandon par . main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud nahin. wo akela hai, uska koi sajhi aur shareek nahin. aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain.'' Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha ke (وحده لا شريك له) ke lafz meri taraf se izafa hain."
972,"Janab Hittaan-bin-Abdullah Raqaashi bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Namaz padhaai . Namaz ke aakhir mein jab baithey to qaum mein se eik aadmi ne kaha : Namaz neki aur pakizgi ke sath barqarar ki gaee . jab Hazrat Abu-Musa Namaz se phirey to kaha : kis ne ye ye alfaz kahe hain? log khamosh rahey . aapney dobara puchha ke ye alfaz kis ne kahe hain? log khamosh rahey . to unhoney Hitaan se kaha : aey Hitaan shayad tum ne ye kahe hain? maine kaha : maine nahin kahe aur mujhey andesha tha ke aap mujhey hi daantengey. tab eik shakhs ne kaha : maine ye alfaz kahe hain aur khair hi ka irada kiya hai. to Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : kya tum nahin jantey ke apni Namaz main tumhen kya aur kaisey kehna hai? bila-shuba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein khutba diya aur hamein taaleem farmaee aur hamein hamari Namaz ka tariqa sikhaya. aapney farmaya : ''jab tum Namaz ke liye khadey ho to apni safon ko durust banao.'' tum mein se koi eik tumhari jamaat kiraaey , jab takbir kahe to tum takbir kaho aur jab wo (غير المغضوب عليهم wla الضالين) kahe to tum aameen pukaro, Allah tum se mohabbat kerega . aur jab wo ( Imam ( takbir kahe aur rukoo karey to tum bhi takbir kaho aur rukoo karo. Imam tum se pehley rukoo kerega aur tum se pehley uthey ga.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye uskey badley mein hai aur jab wo (سمع الله لمن حمده) kahe to tum kaho ( اللهم ربنا لك الحمد ( Allah tumhari suney ga aur qubul kerega . bila-shuba Shan wale Allah ne apney Nabi ki zaban se kahlwaaya hai ke ''Allah sunta hai aur qubul karta hai uski jo uski hamd karey.'' aur jab wo takbir kahe aur sajdey ko jaey to tum bhi takbir kaho aur sajdey mein chaley jao . Imam tum se pehley sajda karta aur tum se pehley sar uthata hai.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''ye uskey badley mein hai. aur jab q'ada  karey (tashahud mein baithey) to tumharey awwaleen alfaz ye honey chaahiyen : (التَّحِيَّاتُ الطَّيِّبَاتُ الصَّلَوَاتُ لِلَّهِ , السَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ أَيُّهَا النَّبِيُّ وَرَحْمَةُ اللَّهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهُ , السَّلَامُ عَلَيْنَا وَعَلَى عِبَادِ اللَّهِ الصَّالِحِينَ , أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ ( ''Janab Ahmed ne ( وبركاته (aur ( أشهد (ke alfaz bayan nahin kiye balke ( وأن محمدا ( kaha."
973,Janab Abu-Ghallaab ne Hittaan-bin-Abdullah-Raqaashi se ye hadees bayan ki aur izafa kiya ke Imam jab qirat karey to khamosh raho. ... aur tashahud mein (أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله) ke baad (وحده لا شريك له) ka izafa kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke) فأنصتوا ( (yani khamosh raho (ke lafz mehfooz nahin hain. is hadees mein sirf Sulaiman Taimi hi isko riwayat karta hai.
974,"Saiyedna Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein tashahud is ehtimam se sikhatey they jaisey ke Quran aur aap ke alfaz ye hotey they :( لتَّحِيَّاتُ الْمُبَارَكَاتُ الصَّلَوَاتُ الطَّيِّبَاتُ لِلَّهِ السَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ أَيُّهَا النَّبِيُّ وَرَحْمَةُ اللَّهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهُ السَّلَامُ عَلَيْنَا وَعَلَى عِبَادِ اللَّهِ الصَّالِحِينَ وأَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ , وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ("
975,"Hazrat Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya hai ke jab Namaz ki darmiyani Q'adaa ho ya uski inteha to salam kehney se pehley ( tashahud se ibtida (shuruat) karo aur) kaha karo : (التحياتُ الطيباتُ , والصلواتُ والملكُ لله ). '' tamam pakizah taazeemaat , azkaar aur mulk Allah hi ke liye hai.'' phir daain taraf salam karo . phir apney qaari (padhne-wale) aur apney aap par salam karo . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Sulaiman-bin-Musa asal mein kufa ke hain aur dimashq mein muqeem they. aur ye saheefa daleel hai ke Hasan Basri ne Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se suna hai."
976,"Hazrat Kab-bin-Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham ne kaha ya deegar Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney hamein hukm diya hai ke ham aap par durood aur salam bhejen. salam bhejna to ham ne jaan liya hai, to durood kaisey padhen? aapney farmaya : kaha karo ! ( اللَّهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ وَآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ . ... الخ ( ''aey Allah ! Muhammad aur aale-Muhammad par apni rahmatein nazil farma , jaisey ke to ne Ibrahim par rahmatein nazil farmaeyn aur Muhammad aur aal Muhammad par apni barkaten nazil farma jaisey ke to ney aal Ibrahim par apni barkaten nazil farmayin. be-shak to tareef kiya hua , badi shaan wala hai.''"
977,Janab Shoba ne ye hadees bayan ki aur kaha : (صل على محمد وعلى آل محمد کما صليت على ال إبراهيم) .
978,Hakm ne apni sanad se isey riwayat kiya aur kaha : (اللَّهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ وَعَلَى آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ كَمَا صَلَّيْتَ عَلَى إِبْرَاهِيمَ إِنَّكَ حَمِيدٌ مَجِيدٌ ، اللَّهُمَّ بَارِكْ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ وَعَلَى آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ كَمَا بَارَكْتَ عَلَى آلِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ إِنَّكَ حَمِيدٌ مَجِيدٌ) . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Zubair-bin-Adi ne ibne-Abi Laila se isi tarah riwayat kya hai jaisey ke Mis'ar ne usey riwayat kiya. farq sirf itna hai ke unhoney kaha hai : (كما صليت على آل إبراهيم إنك حميد مجيد وبارك على محمد) aur sabiqa riwayat ke misl (jaise) bayan kiya.
979,Hazrat Abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham aap par durood kaisey padhen? aapney farmaya : kaha karo : (اللَّهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ وَأَزْوَاجِهِ وَ ذُرِّيَّتِهِ ، كَمَا صَلَّيْتَ عَلَى آلِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ ، وَ بَارِكْ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ وَ أَزْوَاجِهِ وَ ذُرِّيَّتِهِ كَمَا بَارَكْتَ عَلَى آلِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ إِنَّكَ حَمِيدٌ مَجِيدٌ)
980,"Hazrat Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne riwayat kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan Saad-bin-Ibaada (Raziallahu anhu) ki majlis mein tashrif laye to Hazrat Basheer-bin-Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Allah taala ne hamein hukm diya hai ke ham aap par durood padhein. to ye kis tarah padhein . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh ho gaey, (aur der tak khamosh rahey ( yahan tak ke ham ne chaha ke kash wo sawal hi na kiya hota. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' yun kaha karo.'' aur Kab-bin-Ajra ki hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya aur uskey aakhir mein) فِي الْعَالَمِينَ إِنَّكَ حَمِيدٌ مَجِيدٌ ( ziyada kiya."
981,Muhammad-bin-Abdullah-bin-Zaid ne Janab Aqba-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadees naqal ki ke kaha karo (صَلِّ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ النَّبِيِّ الْأُمِّيِّ وَعَلَى آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ).
982,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''jis ka ji chahta hai ke usey uski meezaan (taraazu) khoob bhari hui miley to chahiye ke jab ham ehale-bait par durood padhey to yun kaha karey : (اللَّهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلَى مُحَمَّدٍ النَّبِيِّ وَ أَزْوَاجِهِ أُمَّهَاتِ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ وَ ذُرِّيَّتِهِ وَ أَهْلِ بَيْتِهِ كَمَا صَلَّيْتَ عَلَى آلِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ إِنَّكَ حَمِيدٌ مَجِيدٌ).''"
983,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi aakhiri tashahud se farigh ho jaey to usey chahiye ke Allah se chaar chizon ki panah talab karey. yani azabe-jahannam, azabe-qabr, zindagi aur maut ke fitney aur Masih dajjaal ke shar se.''"
984,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap tashahud ke baad ye dua kartey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ عَذَابِ جَهَنَّمَ وَأَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ عَذَابِ الْقَبْرِ , وَأَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ فِتْنَةِ الدَّجَّالِ وَأَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ فِتْنَةِ الْمَحْيَا وَالْمَمَاتِ )."
985,"Hazrat Mihjana-bin-Adraa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein tashrif laye, aapney eik shakhs ko dekha jisney apni Namaz mukammal kar li thi aur wo tashahud padh raha tha aur keh raha tha : ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَسْأَلُكَ يَا أَللَّهُ الْأَحَدُ الصَّمَدُ الَّذِي لَمْ يَلِدْ وَلَمْ يُولَدْ وَلَمْ يَكُنْ لَهُ كُفُوًا أَحَدٌ , أَنْ تَغْفِرَلِي ذُنُوبِي , إِنَّكَ أَنْتَ الْغَفُورُ الرَّحِيمُ (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey bakhsh diya gaya , usey bakhsh diya gaya.''  teen baar farmaya. (dua ka tarjama hai :) main tujh se sawal karta hun aey Allah ! akeley , be-niyaz, na jisney janaa, na janaa gaya , aur koi uskey barabar nahin ! ye ke merey gunah maaf farma dey . be-shak to bahut hi bakhshney wala rehem kerney wala hai.''"
986,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhoney kaha : ke sunnat ye hai ke tashahud ko khamoshi se padha jaey.
987,Janab Ali-bin-Abdur-Rehman Al-Muaawi bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey dekha ke main Namaz ke dauran mein kankariyon se khel raha tha jab wo farigh huey to unhoney mujhey is se mana farmaya aur kaha : aisey kiya karo jaisey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kiya kartey they. maine kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kaisey kiya kartey they? unhoney farmaya : jab aap Namaz mein baithtey to apney daain haath ko apni daain raan par rakh letey aur sari ungliyan band kar letey aur angoothey ke sath wali (shahadat wali) ungli se ishara kartey aur apney baeyn haath ko apni baain raan par rakhtey they.
988,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Namaz mein baitha kartey to apney baeyn paon ko apni daain raan aur pindli ke nichey kar letey aur apney daain paon ko bichha letey aur baayan haath apney baeyn ghutney par aur daayan haath daain raan par rakhtey aur apni ungli se ishara kartey. aur Abdul-Waahid ne ham ko dikhaya aur angusht (ungli) shahadat se ishara kiya.
989,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne zikr kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab dua kartey to apni ungli se ishara kartey aur isey harkat na detey they. ibne-Juraij ne kaha ke Amr-bin-Dinar ne mazeed kaha ke mujhey Aamir ne apney walid se bayan kiya ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha tha ke aap is tarah ishara kiya kartey they. aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apna baayan haath apni baain raan par rakha kartey they.
990,Janab Aamir-bin-Abdullah-bin-Zubair apney walid se unhoney ye hadees bayan ki aur kaha : aap ki nazar aap ke isharay se aagey na badhti thi. aur Hajjaj ki hadees is se ziyada kamil hai.
991,"Janab Malik-bin-Numair Khuzaae apney walid se riwayat kartey hain unhoney kaha ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha : aap apney dahiney dastey (haath) ko apni daain raan par rakhey huey they, shahadat ki ungli uthaey huey they aur usey kuch tedha sa bhi kiye huey they."
992,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai. Imam Ahmed-bin-Hanbal (Rahimahullah) ke alfaz hain ke aadmi Namaz mein is haal mein baithey ke wo apney haath ka sahara liye huey ho. aur ibne-Shabuyaa ne kaha : manaa farmaya is baat se ke aadmi Namaz mein apney haath ka sahara ley. aur ibne-Raafe ne kaha : manaa farmaya is se ke aadmi Namaz padhey aur wo apney haath ka sahara ley . aur is hadees ko sajdon se uthney ke baab mein zikr kiya. ibn- Abdul-Malik ne kaha : manaa farmaya is se ke aadmi jab Namaz mein uthney lagey to apney haathon ka sahara ley.
993,Janab Ismail-bin-Umayya kehtey hain ke maine Naafe se puchha ke agar koi aadmi Namaz ke dauran mein tashbeek kiye huey ho to? (yani dono haathon ki ungliyan eik doosrey mein diye huey ho?) unhoney kaha : ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) farmatey hain ke ye (مغضوب عليهم) (yani yahudiyon) ki Namaz hai.
994,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne eik shakhs ko dekha ke wo Namaz mein baithey huey apney baeyn haath ka sahara liye huey tha. (yani zameen par rakhey huey tha) Harun-bin-Zaid ne kaha wo apni baain janib par gira hua tha. . . . . . phir dono (raawi) in alfaz mein muttafiq hain. ... to ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne is se kaha : aisey mat baitho is tarah wo log baithtey hain jinhen azab diya jaeyga .
995,Janab Abu-Ubaida apney walid se raawi hain wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mutalliq bayan kartey hain ke aap pehli do rakaaton ke baad) jab baithtey to) aisey hotey goya garm pathar par baithey hon. ham ne kaha : yahan tak ke khadey ho jatey kaha : yahan tak ke khadey ho jatey.
996,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( Namaz ke ikhtitaam par) apni daain aur baeyn taraf salam kiya kartey they, yahan tak ke aap ke rukhsaaron ki safedi dekhi jati thi. (aur kehtey they )  (السلام عليكم ورحمة الله , Assalamualaikum ورحمة الله). Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : ye alfaz Sufiyan ki hadees ke hain. aur Israel ki hadees mein iski wazahat nahin hai. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain : aur is riwayat ko Zuhair ne Abu-Is'haq se aur Yahya-bin-Adam ne Israel sey, unhoney Abu-Is'haq sey, unhoney Abdur-Rehman-bin-Aswad sey, unhoney apney walid aur Alqama se unhoney Hazrat Abdullah se riwayat kiya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud ne ( ye bhi) kaha ke Shoba Abu-Is'haq ki is hadees ke marfoo honey ka inkar kartey they."
997,Janab Alqama bin Waael apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi . aap apni daain taraf salam phertey to ( Assalamualaikum ورحمة الله وبركاته ( kehtey aur apni baain taraf ( Assalamualaikum ورحمة الله ( kehtey .
998,Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechey Namaz padhtey to salam kehtey huey apney haath se daain aur baaeyn ishara kartey they. jab aapney Namaz padh li to farmaya : '' tumhen kya hua hai ke apney haathon se yun isharay kartey ho goya sarkash ghodon ki dumein hon? tumhen yehi kafi hai.'' ya farmaya : ''kya tumharey eik ke liye ye kafi nahin hai ke yun karey aur apney ungli se ishara kya. apney bhai par daain aur baain janib salam kahiye.''
999,Musaair ne sabiqa sanad aur maani ke mutabiq riwayat kya kaha : ''kya tumhen . . . . . ya farmaya. . . . . unhen ye kafi nahin ke apna haath apni raan par rakhen aur apney bhai par salam kahen jo uski daain aur baain taraf hai.''
1000,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur log apney haath uthaey huey they. Zuhair ne kaha . ... mera khayal hai ke Shekh ne kaha tha ke Namaz mein . ... to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey kya hai ke main tumhen dekh raha hun, tum apney haath uthatey ho jaisey ke sarkash ghodon ki dumein hon. Namaz mein sukoon ikhtiyar kya karo.''"
1001,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen hukm farmaya ke Imam ko (uskey salam ka ( jawab den, aur ye ke aapas mein mohabbat rakhen aur eik doosrey ko salam kya karen."
1002,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ka khatam hona takbir (Allahu-Akbar kehney ki aawaz) se jana jata tha.
1003,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne khabar di , farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein log jab farz Namaz se farigh hotey to zikr kartey huey apni aawazen buland kya kartey they. ibne-Abbas farmatey hain ke mujhey unka Namaz se farigh hona usi se maloom hota tha aur main unka zikr sunta tha."
1004,"Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain : maine abu-Umair Esa bin Yunus Fakhoori Ramli ko suna, wo bayan kartey they ke Faryabi jab Makka se wapis lotey to unhoney is hadees ko marfoo bayan karna chhod diya tha aur kaha ke mujhey Imam Ahmed bin Hambal (Rahimahullah) ne is hadees ko marfoo bayan kerney se roka hai."
1005,"Hazrat Ali bin Talaq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi Namaz mein phuski maarey, (hawa khaarij karey) to chahiye ke Namaz tod dey aur wuzu karey aur apni Namaz dohraaey .''"
1006,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum is baat se aajiz ho ke (farzon ke baad) aagey-peechey ya daeyn-baeyn ho jao, yani nafl padhney ke liye .''"
1007,"Janab Azraq bin Qais kehtey hain ke hamen hamarey Imam ne jinka naam abu-Ramsa tha, Namaz padhaai . unhoney kaha ke maine ye Namaz ya usi tarah ki koi aur Namaz Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath padhi , aur Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) safe-awwal mein aapki daain janib khadey they. wahan eik aur aadmi bhi tha jo takbire-aula mein pahuncha tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz padhaai phir apni daain-baain janib salam phera, yahan tak ke ham ne aap ke rukhsaaron ki safedi dekhi. phir wahan se phirey jaisey ke main phira hun. to wo aadmi jo takbire-aula mein shamil hua tha, nafl padhney ke liye uth khada hua. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) jaldi se uski taraf uthey aur usey kandhey se pakad kar jhinjhoda aur kaha : beth jao, ehle-kitab ki halakat ka baais yehi tha ke unki namazon mein koi farq fasla na hota tha. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unki taraf apni nazar uthai aur farmaya : ''aey ibn khitab ! Allah ne tumhen sahih baat kehney ki tofiq di hai. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Imam ka naam abu-Ramsa ki bajaey abu-Umaiya bhi bayan kya gaya hai."
1008,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ham ko pichhley pahar ki eik Namaz padhaai Zohar ya Asr . aapney hamein do rakatein padha kar salam pher diya. phir aap masjid ke samney eik lakdi ke paas khadey huey aur apney dono haath us par rakh liye . aap ka eik haath doosrey ke ooper tha. aur aap ke chehrey par narazi ke aasaar numaya they. phir jald baaz log (masjid sey) nikal aaye aur wo keh rahey they : Namaz kam kar di gaee ! Namaz kam kar di gaee ! logon mein Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bhi they, magar heybiyat ke baais wo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se baat na kar rahey they, to eik aadmi khada hua , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey Zul-Yadain (haathon wala) kaha kartey they. wo kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap bhool gaey hain ya Namaz kam kar di gaee hai? aapney farmaya : ''main bhoolaa hun na Namaz kam ki gaee hai.'' kehney laga : balke aap bhool gaey hain aey Allah ke Rasool ! tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) logon ki taraf mutawajjeh huey aur puchha : ''kya Zul-Yadain theek keh raha hai? '' unhoney ishara kiya ke haan . tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni jagah par tashrif laye aur baqiiya do rakatein padhaein , phir aapney salam phera , phir aapney takbir kahi aur sajda kiya apney sajdey ki manind ya us se kuch lamba . phir sar uthaya aur takbir kahi aur) doosra ( sajda kiya apney ( pehley ( sajdey ki manind ya us se kuch lamba . phir aapney sar uthaya aur takbir kahi . Muhammad-bin-Sirin se kaha gaya : kya aapney sajda saho ke baad salam phera tha? unhoney jawab diya : mujhey ye baat Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se yaad nahin hai, magar mujhey bataya gaya hai ke Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya hai ke phir aapney salam phera."
1009,"Muhammad (bin-Sirin) se riwayat hai aur Hammad ki riwayat ziyada kamil hai. unhoney ( Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) sey) bayan kiya, ke phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz padhi. ye nahin kaha ke hamein Namaz padhaai . aur na ye kaha ke logon ne ishara kiya. balke kaha : ke logon ne kaha : haan . (yani aap bhool gaey hain.) phir bayan kiya ke aapney sar uthaya . magar takbir ka zikr nahin kiya. phir takbir kahi aur sajda kiya apney pehley sajdey ki manind ya us se kuch lamba , phir sar uthaya . (yani yahan bhi takbir ka zikr nahin) aur yahan tak uski riwayat puri ho gaee hai. aur iskey baad aakhir tak ke alfaz bhi bayan nahin kiye. aur) فأومئوا ( ''logon ne ishara kya.''  ka lafz siwaye Hammad-bin-Zaid ke kisi aur ne zikr nahin kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke jisney bhi ye riwayat zikr ki hai usney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki takbir aur aap ke laut aaney ka zikr nahin kiya hai."
1010,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein Namaz padhaai . ... aakhir tak riwayat Hammad ki manind ke mujhey bataya gaya hai ke Imran-bin-Husain ne kaha ke phir aapney salam phera , ( Salma ne ( kaha : maine puchha : aur tashahud ? unhoney kaha : tashahud ke baarey mein maine kuch nahin suna, magar mujhey tashahud padhna ziyada pasand hai. ( Salma ne ye ( zikr nahin kiya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us shakhs ko Zul-Yadain kaha kartey they, aur na logon ke isharay aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki narazi ka zikr kiya. aur Hammad ki hadees ziyada kamil hai jo Ayub se marwi (bayan) hai."
1011,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se Zul-Yadain ke qissey mein bayan kartey hain ke aapney takbir kahi aur sajda kiya. jabkey Hisham-bin-Hassaan ne riwayat kiya ke aapney takbir kahi (yani tahreema) phir (الله اكبر) kaha aur sajda kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke is hadees ko Habib-bin-Shahid , Humaid , Yunus aur Aasim Ahwal ( chaaron ( ne Muhammad-bin-Sirin se aur wo Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain aur in mein se kisi ne bhi wo baat zikr nahin ki jo Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Hisham se bayan ki hai ke aapney takbir (tahreema) kahi phir takbir kahi aur sajda kiya. usi tarah Hammad-bin-Salma aur Abu-Bakar-bin-Ayash bhi Hisham se ye riwayat zikr kartey hain to unhoney bhi Hamma-bin-Zaid wali ye baat zikr nahin ki ke aapney takbir (tahreema) kahi phir takbir kahi."
1012,"Saeed-bin-Musaiyab, Abu-Salma aur Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah (teeno) Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se ye qissa bayan kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sahoo ke sajdey nahin kiye yahan tak ke Allah ne aap ko iska yaqeen dila diya."
1013,"Ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai ke Abu-Bakar-bin-Sulaiman-bin-abi-Hasma (Taabai) ne un se bayan kiya ke unko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye khabar pahunchi hai. unhoney kaha ke aapney shak ki bina par kiye janey waley sajdey us waqt tak nahin kiye jab tak ke logon ne mil kar nahin bataya. ibne-Shahab kehtey hain ke mujhey ye hadees Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan ki (iske alawa) kaha ke mujhey Abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman, Abu-Bakar-bin-Haris-bin-Hisham aur Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah (ne bhi Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : aur Zubaidi ne Zohri sey, wo Abu-Bakar-bin-Sulaiman-bin-abi-Hasma sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain aur is mein kaha ke aapney sahoo (ghalti) ke dono sajdey nahin kiye."
1014,Abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zohar ki Namaz padhaai to aapney do rakaaton par salam pher diya. aap se kaha gaya : ( kya ( Namaz kam ho gaee hai? tab aapney do rakatein ( mazeed ( padhaein phir do sajdey kiye.
1015,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik farz Namaz mein do rakaaton par salam pher diya to eik shakhs ne aap se kaha : kya Namaz kam ho gaee hai, aey Allah ke Rasool ! ya aap bhool gaey hain? aapney farmaya : ''un mein se kuch bhi nahin hua.'' to logon ne kaha : tehqiq aapney aisa kiya hai aey Allah ke Rasool ! tab aapney do rakatein mazeed padhaein , phir aap paltey aur sahoo ke do sajdey nahin kiye. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : is riwayat ko Dawud-bin-Husain ne ba-waasta Abu-Sufiyaan maula-ibne-abi-Ahmed, Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye qissa bayan kiya to kaha : phir aapney do sajdey kiye jabkey aap salam ke baad baithey huey they."
1016,Zamzam-bin-jaus Hiffaani ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se ye khabar bayan ki . kaha ke phir aapney salam ke baad sahoo ke do sajdey kiye.
1017,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein Namaz padhaai to do rakaaton par salam pher diya. aur ibne-Sirin ki hadees ki manind bayan kiya jo Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai. aur kaha : phir aapney salam phera , phir sahoo ke do sajdey kiye."
1018,"Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Asr ki Namaz mein teen rak'aat par salam pher diya. phir aap apney hujuraat mein tashrif ley gaey, to eik aadmi jis ka naam Khirbaaq tha aap ki taraf gaya aur ye lambey haathon wala tha, kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya Namaz kam kar di gaee hai? to aap ghussay mein chadar ghaseet'tey huey bahir tashrif laye aur kaha : ''kya ye sach kehta hai? '' logon ne kaha : haan ! tab aapney wo rakaat padhaai , phir salam phera , phir do sajdey kiye , phir salam phera."
1019,Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke (eik baar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein Zohar ki paanch rakatein padha di. to aap se kaha gaya : kya Namaz mein izafa kar diya gaya hai? aapney farmaya : ''kya hua?'' kehney lagey ke aapney paanch rakatein padhaai hain. tab aapney do sajdey kiye jabkey aap salam pher chukey they.
1020,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah ne Namaz padhaai , Ibrahim ne kaha maloom nahin is mein koi kami kar di ya beshi . ... jab salam phera to aap se kaha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya Namaz ke mutalliq koi naya hukm aaya hai? aapney farmaya : ''kya hua?'' kehney lagey ke aapney aisey aisey Namaz padhaai hai. to aapney apna paon moda , qibla rukh huey aur unhen do sajdey kiraaey , phir salam phera . jab phirey to hamari taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : ''bila-shuba agar Namaz ke mutalliq koi naya hukm aata to main tumhen batla deta , lekin main insan hun, waisey hi bhoolta hun jaisey tum bhooltey ho. jab main bhool jaun to mujhey yaad kara diya karo.'' aur farmaya : ''jab kisi ko Namaz mein shak ho jaey to chahiye ke ghaur karey ke theek kiya hai aur usi par apni Namaz ko mukammal karey, phir salam pherey phir do sajdey karey.''"
1021,Alqama ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se yehi khabar bayan ki . aapney farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi bhool jaey to do sajdey karey.'' phir aap mudey aur aapney do sajdey kiye. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Husain ne Aamash ki manind riwayat kiya hai.
1022,"Alqama se riwayat hai unhoney bayan kiya ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein paanch rakatein padha di. jab aap phirey to log aapas mein chupkey chupkey se baaten kerney lagey . aapney puchha : ''kya baat hai? '' kehney lagey : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya Namaz mein izafa kar diya gaya hai? farmaya : '' nahin .'' unhoney kaha : aapney paanch rak'aat padhaai hain, to aap mudey aur do sajdey kiye phir salam phera aur farmaya : ''bila-shuba main insan hun, bhool jata hun jaisey tum bhool jatey ho.''"
1023,"Janab suwaid-bin-Qais, Hazrat Muaawiya-bin-Hudaij (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain ke eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz padhaai aur salam pher diya halanke eik rakat baqi thi. to eik aadmi aap se ja kar mila aur kaha ki aap Namaz main eik rakat bhool gaey hain. to aap wapis tashrif laye aur masjid mein dakhil huey aur Bilal ko hukm diya to unhoney Namaz ki iqaamat kahi aur aapney logon ko eik rakat padhaai. maine logon ko (baad mein) is (waqiey) ki khabar di to unhoney mujhey kaha, kya tum us aadmi ko jantey ho? maine kaha : nahin, lekin agar dekh lun to pehchan jaunga . chunanche wo merey paas se guzra to maine kaha : yehi wo shakhs hai. to unhoney bataya ke ye Talha-bin-Ubaidullah hain."
1024,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko apni Namaz mein shak ho jaey to chahiye ke shak ko door karey aur yaqeen ko buniyad banaey . jab yaqeen par Namaz mukammal kar ley to do sajdey karey. agar uski Namaz (darasal) puri hui to uski zayed rakaat aur dono sajdey nafl hongey. aur agar naqis hui to ye rakaat uski Namaz ki takmil hogi aur do sajdey shaitan ki zillat ka baais hongey. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : usey Hisham-bin-Saad aur Muhammad-bin-mutrif ne Zaid sey, unhoney Ata bin Yasar sey, unhoney Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya hai aur Abu-Khalid ki hadees ziyada bharpoor hai."
1025,Janab Ikrima Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se raawi hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sahoo ke sajdon ko shaitan ke liye zillat ka baais bayan farmaya.
1026,"Janab Ata-bin-Yasar ( Taabai ( bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko apni Namaz mein shak ho jaey aur maloom na rahey ke kitni Namaz padhi hai, teen ya chaar ? to usey chahiye ke eik rakat padhey aur do sajdey karey jabkey wo baitha hua ho, salam se pehley . agar uski ye rakaat paanchwin hui to un sajdon ke sath mil kar dogaana ho jaeygi aur agar chauthi hi hui to ye sajdey shaitan ki ruswai ka baais hongey.''"
1027,"Zaid-bin-Aslam ne Malik ki sabiqa sanad se bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko apni Namaz mein shak ho to agar usey yaqeen ho ke usney teen rak'aat padhi hain to chahiye ke khada ho aur eik rakat sajdon samet puri karey, phir baith jaey aur tashahud padhey . jab farigh ho jaey aur sirf salam kehna baqi ho to chahiye ke do sajdey karey phir salam kahe.'' phir Malik ki hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is riwayat ko ibne-Wahab ne malik, Hafs-bin-Maisraa , Dawud-bin-Qais aur Hisham-bin-Saad se usi tarah ( mursal ( riwayat kiya hai, magar Hisham ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se mausoolan bayan ki hai."
1028,"Abu-Ubaida-bin-Abdullah apney walid sey, wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jab tum Namaz mein ho aur teen ya chaar rak'aat mein shak ho jaey aur tumhara ghalib guman chaar ka ho to tashahud padho phir do sajdey karo jabkey tum baithey huey ho, salam se pehley, phir tashahud padho phir salam phero.''  Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke is riwayat ko abdul-Waahid ne Khusaif se riwayat kiya hai magar usey marfoo bayan nahin kiya. Sufiyan , Shareek aur Israel ne bhi Abdul-Waahid ki muwaafiqat ki hai. aur matn hadees ke alfaz mein ikhtilaf hai. aur in logon ne isey musnad (marfoo) bayan nahin kiya hai."
1029,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi Namaz padhey aur usey maloom na rahey ke ziyada padhi hai ya kam , to usey chahiye ke jab wo baitha hua ho to do sajdey kar ley . aur jab shaitan uskey paas aaye aur kahe ke to be-wuzu ho gaya hai to usey chahiye ke kahe to ne jhoot kaha hai, siwaey iske ke naak se boo mehsoos karey ya kaan se aawaz suney.'' aur ye lafz Aban ki riwayat ke hain. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Maamer aur Ali-bin-Mubarak ne (raawi ka naam) ayaaz-bin-Hilal kaha hai, jabkey Auzaai , Ayaaz-bin-Abi-Zuhair kehtey hain."
1030,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak tum mein se koi jab Namaz padhney khada hota hai to shaitan uskey paas aata hai aur is par khalt-malt kar deta hai (yani bhulwaa deta hai) yahan tak ke usey maloom nahin rehta ke kis qadr Namaz padhi hai, to tum mein se koi jab ye keyfiyat mehsoos karey to chahiye ke baithe-baithe do sajdey kar ley. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke ibne-Uena , Maamer aur Leis ne bhi aisey hi riwayat kiya hai."
1031,"Janab Zohri ka bhatija (Muhammad-bin-Abdullah ( raawi hai ke Muhammad-bin-Muslim ( Zohri ( ne apni sanad se ye hadees bayan ki aur kaha ke) sajdey karey ( ''jabkey wo baitha hua ho, salam se pehley.''"
1032,"ibne Is-haq raawi hain ke Muhammad-bin-Muslim Zohri ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya aur kaha : ''salam se pehley do sajdey karey, phir salam pherey.''"
1033,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisey apni Namaz mein shak ho, usey chahiye ke salam ke baad do sajdey karey.''"
1034,"Hazrat Abdullah-ibne-Buhaina (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein do rakatein padhaein aur khadey ho gaey, baithey nahin. isliye log bhi aap ke sath khadey ho gaey, jab aapney apni Namaz mukammal farmaai aur hamein aap ke salam kehney ka intizar tha, aapney takbir kahi aur do sajdey kiye jabkey aap  (tashahud mein) baithey huey they, salam se pehley. unke baad salam phera.''"
1035,"Shoaib ne Zohri se mazkura baala sanad aur hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya aur mazeed kaha : (ke jab Sahaba kiram teesri rakaat mein khadey ho gaey to ( kuch log ham mein se qiyam mein tashahud padh rahey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke aisey hi Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi do sajdey kiye jabkey wo do rakaaton par khadey ho gaey they, ye sajdey salam se pehley kiye aur Zohri ka qaul bhi yehi hai."
1036,Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Imam do rakaaton par khada ho jaey aur sahih sidha khada honey se pehley hi usey yaad aa jaey to chahiye ke baith jaey (aur tashahud padhey (aur agar sidha khada ho jaey to na baithey balke sahoo ke do sajdey karey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke meri kitab mein Jabir-Jo'afi se sirf yehi hadees riwayat hui hai.
1037,"Ziyad-bin-Ilaaqa bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Namaz padhaai to wo do rakaaton ke baad khadey ho gaey . ham ne Subhanallah kaha . unhoney bhi Subhanallah kaha aur khadey rahey jab Namaz puri ki aur salam pher liya to sahoo ke do sajdey kiye. jab Namaz se phirey to kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aapney aisey hi kiya tha jaisey ke maine kiya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : ibne-Abi-Laila ne ba-waasta Sha'bi Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se aisey hi marfoo bayan kiya hai. (isliye) Abu-Umais ne Sabit-bin-Ubaid se Ziyad-bin-Ilaaqa ki manind riwayat kiya hai, kaha ke ham ko Mughira-bin-Shoba ne Namaz padhaai . Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Abu-Umais , Masoodi ka bhai hai. Hazrat Saad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi aisey hi kiya tha jaisey ke Janab Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kiya. aur Imran-bin-Husain Suhaak-bin-Qais aur Muaawiya-bin-Abi-Sufiyan (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ne bhi isi tarah kiya. aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka yehi fatwa hai aur Umar-bi- Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) ka bhi . Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke ye hadees un logon ke liye hai jo do rakaaton par khadey ho jaeyn . phir wo salam ke baad sajdey karen."
1038,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : '' her saho ke liye salam ke baad do sajdey hain.'' (Imam Abu-Dawud ke Shekh Amr bin Usman ki sanad mein Abdur-Rehman bin Jubair bin Nafair apney walid sey, wo Soban se riwayat kartey hain.) aur walid ka ye zikr Amr ke ilawa kisi aur ki sanad mein nahin hai."
1039,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko Namaz padhaai aur bhool gaey to do sajdey kiye phir tashahud padha aur salam phera.
1040,ummul-momenin Sayeda umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab salam keh letey to thodi der rukey rehtey. aur Sahaba samajhtey they ke ye is liye hota tha ke aurten mardon se pehley lot jaeyn .
1041,Janab Qabisa bin Halab Taai apney walid Halab (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi to aap apni dono atraaf se (muqtadiyon ki taraf) phira kartey they. (yani kabhi daain janib se aur kabhi baain janib se. (
1042,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tum mein se koi apni Namaz mein shetan ka hissa na rakhey . yun ke sirf daain janib se phirney hi ko ikhtiyar kar ley. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko baaraha dekha ke aap apni baain janib se bhi phira kartey they. Imaara bayan kartey hain ke iskey baad main Madiney aaya to dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke makanaat aap (ke musalley) se baain janib they.
1043,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apni Namaz ka kuch hissey apney gharon mein bhi padha karo aur unhen qabristaan na bana chhodo.''
1044,Janab Basar bin Saeed Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se raawi hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri is masjid mein Namaz padhney ke muqabley mein insan ka apney ghar mein Namaz padhna ziyada afzal hai siwaye farz Namaz ke .''
1045,Saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke Sahaba baitul-Maqdis ki taraf munh karkey Namaz padha kartey they. to jab ye aayat kareema nazil hui (فَوَلِّ وَجْهَكَ شَطْرَ الْمَسْجِدِ الْحَرَامِ وَحَيْثُ مَا كُنْتُمْ فَوَلُّوا وُجُوهَكُمْ شَطْرَهُ ) ''chunanche aap apna rukh masjide-haram ki janib kar liijiye aur tum jahan bhi ho apney chehrey uski taraf kar lo.'' to eik shakhs banu-Salma ke afrad ke paas se guzra jabke wo Fajr ki Namaz mein rukoo mein they aur baitul-Maqdis ki taraf munh karkey Namaz padh rahey they to usney unhen pukar kar kaha : khabrdar! qibla Kaaba ki janib tabdeel kar diya gaya hai. usney do baar ye aawaaz lagaai. chunanche wo log apni usi rukoo ki haalat mein Kaaba ki janib phir gaey.
1046,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''behtareen din jis mein Suraj tulu hota hai, Jumey ka din hai. us mein Adam paida kiye gaey, usi mein unko zameen par utaara gaya, usi mein unki tauba qubul ki gaee, isi din unki wafat hui aur isi din qiyamat qaaim hogi. Juma ke din subh hotey hi tamam janwer qiyamat ke dar se kaan lagaey huey hotey hain yahan tak ke Suraj tulu ho jaey, siwaye jinnon aur insanon ke . us din main eik ghadi aisi hai jisey koi musalman banda pa ley jabkey wo Namaz padh raha ho aur Allah azz-w-jall se apni kisi zarurat ka sawal kar raha ho to Allah taala usey zarur inayat farma deta hai.'' Janab Kab (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : aisa saal main eik din hota hai? to maine kaha : ( nahin) balke her Jumey ko hota hai. tab Kab ne Torah padhi aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sach farmaya. Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main baad mein Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) se mila aur unko Janab Kab (Rahimahullah) se apni majlis ka bataya to Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : mujhey maloom hai ke ye ghadi kis waqt hoti hai. Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : maine un se kaha : mujhey ( bhi) ye bata dijiye . to Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye Juma ke din aakhiri ghadi hoti hai. maine ( un sey) kaha : ye aakhiri ghadi kaisey ho sakti hai? halanke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : '' musalman banda usey paey jabkey wo Namaz padh raha ho.'' aur us waqt mein Namaz nahin padhi jati . to Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye nahin farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi jagah betha Namaz ka intizar kar raha ho to wo Namaz hi mein hota hai yahan tak ke Namaz padh ley.'' maine kaha : haan ! kehney lagey ke bas yehi hai."
1047,"Hazrat Aus bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumharey afzal dinon mein se Jumey ka din hai. us mein Adam paida kiye gaey, usi mein unki rooh qabz ki gaee , usi mein) nafakh (dusri dafa Soor phoonkna) hai aur usi mein) Saaqa hai (pehli dafa Soor phoonkna, jis se tamam bani-Adam halak ho jaeyngey.) so us din mein mujh par ziyada durood padha karo kyonkey tumhara durood mujh par pesh kya jata hai.'' Sahaba ne puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamara durood aap par kyon kar pesh kya jaeyga halaanki aap boseedah ho chukey hongey. (yani aap ka jism .) to aapney farmaya : ''Allah azz-w-jall ne zameen par anbiya ke jism haram kar diye hain.''"
1048,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) raawi hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Jume ke din mein 12 ghadiyaan hain. jo bhi musalman is haalat mein paya jaey ke Allah taala se koi sawal karta ho to Allah taala usey wo chiz inayat farma deta hai, lihaza usey Asr ke baad ki aakhiri ghadi mein talash karo.''"
1049,Janab abu-Barda bin abi Musa Ash-ari bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne mujh se puchha : kya aapney apney walid se Juma ke baarey mein kuch suna hai wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se hadees riwayat kartey they yani qubuliyat ki ghadi kon si hai? maine kaha : haan maine unko suna hai wo kehtey they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna aap farmatey they : ''ye ghadi Imam ke) member par) beth janey se lekar Namaz mukammal honey tak ke beech hai.'' Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : yani member par) beth janey sey) .
1050,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs wuzu karey aur achcha wuzu karey phir Juma ke liye aaye aur ghor se suney aur khamosh rahey to uskey Jumey se Jumey tak ke aur mazeed teen din ke gunah bakhsh diye jatey hain aur jo ( khutbey ke doran mein) kankariyon se khelaa usney laghw kaam kya. ''
1051,"maula Umme- Usman ( zauja Ata ( se riwayat hai, kaha maine Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko masjid koofa ke member par suna, wo farma rahey they : ''jab Jumey ka din aata hai to shayateen apney jhandey lekar bazar jatey hain aur logon ko mukhtalif mashaaghil mein uljha detey hain aur unhen Jumey se takheer kara detey hain. aur farishtey aa kar masaajid ke darwazon par beth jatey aur pehli ghadi mein pahunchney walon ke naam likhtey hain aur dusri ghadi mein aaney walon ke naam likhtey hain yahan tak ke Imam aa jata hai. pas jab koi shakhs kisi munasib jagah beth jata hai ke sahih taur par) khutba ( sun sakey , Imam ko dekh sakey , aur khamosh rahey aur laghw baat (ya kaam ( na karey to aisey shakhs ko do hissey ajr milta hai aur agar koi shakhs door ho aur aisi jagah bethey ke wahan se sun na sakta ho, lekin khamosh rahey aur laghw baat (ya kaam ( na karey to usko eik hissey ajr milta hai. aur agar kisi aisi jagah bethey jahan se wo sahih taur par sun sakta ho aur Imam ko dekh sakta ho lekin kis laghw kaam mein mashghool ho rahey aur khamosh na rahey to usko gunah ka eik hissey milta hai. aur agar kisi ne apney sathi ko doran Juma mein) khamosh karaney ke liye ( ''chup raho'' bhi keh diya, to usney laghw kaam kya. aur jisney laghw kaam kya uskey liye us Juma mein se kuch nahin hai.'' Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne uskey aakhir mein kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye sab farmatey huey suna hai. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain usey Waleed bin Muslim ne ibne-Jabir se riwayat kya to lafz ( ربائث ( zikr kya hai. aisey hi (مولى امرأته أم عثمان بن عطاء) kaha ."
1052,Hazrat abul-Jaad Zamri (Raziallahu anhu) . ... sahabi . ... se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ghaflat aur susti se teen Jumey chhod dey Allah taala uskey dil par mohar laga deta hai.''
1053,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : '' jisney kisi uzr ke baghair Juma chhod diya ho wo eik Dinar sadqa karey, agar na paey to aadha deenar.'' Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : Khalid bin Qais ne aisey hi riwayat kya hai magar sanad mein ikhtilaf kya hai aur matn mein muwaafiqat ki hai."
1054,"Qudama bin Wabra se riwayat hai kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs se baghair kisi uzr ke eik Juma reh gaya ho, to wo eik dirham ya aadha dirham ya eik saa ya aadha saa gehun sadqa karey. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke usko Saeed bin Bashir ne Qatada ( raawi ( se aisey hi riwayat kya hai magar usney eik mud ya aadha mud kaha hai aur Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain : maine Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahimahullah) se suna, un se is hadees mein ikhtilaf ke baarey mein sawal kya gaya tha, to unhoney kaha : merey nazdik Ayub yani abul-Ala ki nisbat Hammam Ahfaz hai. (yani ziyada yaad rakhney wala hai. ("
1055,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke log apney deron se aur Madina key oopri hissey (awaali) se Juma ke liye aaya kartey they.
1056,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : '' her us shakhs par Juma hai jo Azan suney . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is hadees ko eik jamaat ne Sufiyan se riwayat kya hai aur wo sab usey Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) par moquf kartey hain, sirf Qabisa ne usey marfoo bayan kya hai."
1057,"abu-Maleeh apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke jang Hunain ke din barish thi , to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney manadi ( muazzan ( ko hukm diya ke) aelan karey ke) Namaz apney apney padaaw hi par padhein ."
1058,abu-Maleeh se riwayat hai kehtey hain ke ye Jumey ke din ka waqia hai.
1059,abu-Maleeh apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke wo Hudebiya ke dino mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan hazir they. Jumey ka din tha aur barish ho gaee . itni ke unke jooton ke talwey bhi na bheegey to aapney unko hukm diya ke apney apney padaaw hi par namazein padhein .
1060,"Janab Naafe se riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne (eik safar mein) Zajnan maqam par thandi raat mein padaaw kya. to unhoney muazzan ko hukm diya, usney aelan kya ke Namaz apney apney khemon mein padhein . Ayub bayan kartey hain ke Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab koi raat thandi ya barish wali hoti to muazzan ko hukm farmatey aur wo aelan karta ke) الصلاة في الرحال ( yani apney apney deron mein Namaz padho ."
1061,"Janab Naafe bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne maqame-Zajnan mein Namaz ke liye Azan kahi phir kaha ( صلوا في رحالكم ( ''apney padaaw aur khemon mein Namaz padho.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye bayan kiya ke aap muazzan ko hukm detey , wo Azan deta phir aelan karta ke ''apney apney padaaw mein Namaz padho.'' jabkey raat ko sardi hoti , barish hoti aur safar mein hotey . Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain : is hadees ko Hammad-bin-Salma ne Ayub aur Ubaidullah se bayan kiya to is mein kaha : aap safar mein (aisa aelan karwaatey) jabkey raat ko sardi hoti ya barish hoti."
1062,"Janab Naafe se riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne maqame-Zajnan mein Namaz ke liye Azan kahi , raat thandi thi aur hawa chal rahi thi. aapney apni Azan ke aakhir mein kaha ( ألا صلوا في رحالكم , ألا صلوا في رحالكم ( ''khabrdar ! apney apney padaaw mein Namaz padho . khabrdar apney apney padaaw mein Namaz padho.'' phir bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) safar ke dauran mein jab raat sard hoti ya barish wali hoti to muazzan ko hukm detey ke yun kahe ( ألا صلوا في رحالكم ( ''khabrdar ! apney apney maqam par Namaz padho.''"
1063,"Janab Naafe se riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne eik raat jabke sardi thi aur hawa chal rahi thi , Azan kahi to kaha : ( ألا صلوا في رحالكم ( phir bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , jab raat thandi hoti ya barish wali hoti to muazzan ko hukm detey ke yun kahe ( ألا صلوا في رحالكم ( ."
1064,Janab Naafe Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se raawi hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke muazzan ne ye aelan Madiney mein kiya jabkey raat barish wali thi aur subh thandi thi. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke Yahya-bin-Saeed Ansari is khabar ko Qasim se wo Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain to is mein kaha ke ye ''safar'' ka waqia hai.
1065,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath safar mein they to barish ho gaee . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jo chahey apney padaaw mein Namaz padh ley.''
1066,"Janab Abdullah-bin-Haris , Muhammad-bin-Sirin ke chacherey bhai bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne eik barish waley din mein apney muazzan se kaha ke jab tum ( أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله ( keh lo to phir ( حي على الصلاة ( na kehna , balke (صلوا في بيوتكم) ''apney gharon mein Namaz padh lo.''  kehna . logon ne is amal ko kuch ajeeb jana to unhoney kaha : ye kaam us zaat ne kiya hai jo mujh se afzal thi. bila-shuba Juma wajib hai, magar mujhey ye baat napasand hai ke main tumhen mashaqqat mein dalun aur tum keechad aur barish mein chal kar aao."
1067,"Hazrat Taariq-bin-Shahaab (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : '' Juma her musalman par jamaat ke sath laaziman farz hai, siwaye chaar qism ke logon ke . ghulam mamlook , aurat , bachcha aur mareez . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Taariq-bin-Shahaab ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha hai magar aap se kuch suna nahin hai."
1068,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Islam mein Madina Munawwara ki masjide-Nabawi ke baad sab se pehley jahan Juma qaaim kiya gaya wo bahreen ki eik basti juwasa thi. (ustaad) Usman-bin-abi-Sheba ne wazahat ki ke ye Abdul-Qais ki bastiyon mein se thi.
1069,"Janab Abdur-Rehman-bin-Kaab-bin-Malik . ... ye apney walid ke na-bina honey ke baad unke qaaid they. ... apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Jume ke roz jab wo Jumey ki Azan suntey to Asad-bin-Zurara (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye rehmat ki dua kartey. maine un se kaha : aap jab bhi Azan suntey hain to Asad-bin-Zurara ke liye rehmat ki dua kartey hain? unhoney kaha : is liye ke harra-bani-biyaaza mein '' ھرمالنبیت '' ke andar unhoney hi sab se pehley hamein Juma padhaya tha, eik naqeea' mein jisey '' naqeea' الخضمات '' kaha jata tha - (yani nashebi jagah jahan pani jama ho jata tha. ( maine un se puchha ke aap logon ki tadaad kitni thi ? unhoney kaha : chaalis afrad."
1070,"Janab Ayaas-bin-abi-Ramla Shami se riwayat hai, kehtey hain ke main Hazrat Muaawiya-bin-Abi-Sufiyan (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke yahan hazir tha aur wo Hazrat-Zaid-bin-Raaqim (Raziallahu anhu) se daryaft kar rahey they ke kya tumharey hotey huey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein kabhi do eidein ( Juma aur eid ( eik hi din mein ikatthi hui hai? unhoney kaha : haan ! puchha ke tab aapney kaisey kya? unhoney kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eid ki Namaz padhi phir Jume ke baarey mein rukhsat (chhoot) de-di aur farmaya : ''jo padhnaa chahta hai padh ley.''"
1071,"Janab Ata-bin-abi-Ribah bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne ham ko Jume ke roz eid ke din , din ke pehley hissey mein Namaz padhaai , phir ham Jume ke liye gaey magar wo na aaye aur ham ne akeley hi Namaz padhi. aur Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) taaif mein they, wo jab aaye to ham ne un se uska zikr kiya to farmaya ke unhoney sunnat par amal kiya hai."
1072,"Janab Ata-bin-abi-Ribah ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat ibne-Zubair ke daure-khilaafat mein Juma aur eidul-fitr eik hi din aa gaey, to unhoney kaha : do eidein eik hi din mein ikatthi ho gaee hain. phir unhoney un dono ko jama kar diya aur pehley pahar do rakatein padhaaien , is par kuch izafa na kiya, yahan tak ke Asr padhi."
1073,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''tumharey is din mein do eidein jama ho gaee hain, to jo chahey uskey liye ye (Namaze-Eid) Jume ke badley kafi hai aur ham Juma padhengey . ''Umar-bin-Hafs ki sanad mein عنعنہ hai - (yani isney  an (an) Shoba , kaha hai)"
1074,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jume ke roz Fajr ki Namaz mein sura Alif-Lam-Mim tanazzul Sajda aur) هَلْ أَتَى عَلَى الْإِنْسَانِ حِينٌ مِنَ الدَّهْرِ ( padha kartey they.
1075,Shoba ne Mukhawwal se mazkura sanad aur usi ke ham-maani bayan kiya aur mazeed ye kaha ke Namaze-Juma mein aap sura Juma aur munaafiqun padha kartey they.
1076,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik reshmi libas dekha jo masjid ke darwazey ke paas bechaa ja raha tha to unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! agar aap usey kharida lein aur Jume ke din pahna karen ya jab aap ke paas wafad ayen to unke istaqbal ke liye pehna keren (to achhaa hoga) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye wo log pehantey hain jinka aakhirat mein koi hissey nahin .'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas usi qism ke mazeed jodey aaye to aapney un mein se eik umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi inayat farmaya. unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap mujhey ye dey rahey hain halanke utaarid ke jodey ke baarey mein is se pehley aap jo kuch farma chukey hain, farma chukey hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine tumhen ye is liye nahin diya hai ke tum khud isey pahno.'' chunanche Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye joda apney bhai ko dey diya jo ke mushrik tha aur makkey mein rehta tha."
1077,Janab Salim apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik reshmi joda dekha jo baazar mein bechaa ja raha tha wo unhoney liya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas laye aur kaha : aap isey kharia lein taake eid aur wafad ke istaqbal ke mauqe par zeenat ke liye pahna karen. ... phir hadees bayan ki . . . . .) taaham ( pehli riwayat ziyada kamil hai.
1078,Janab Muhammad-bin-Yahya-bin-Hibbaan ( Taabai ( ne riwayat kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar mumkin ho to Jume ke liye apney kaam kaaj ke kapdon ke ilawa do kapdey aur bana rakhney mein kya harj hai? '' Amr ne ba-sand ibne-abi-Habib-ibne-Salam (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kiya ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member par ye kehtey huey suna tha. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain (is ki eik sanad yun bhi hai) ke usey Wahab-bin-Jarir apney walid se wo Yahya bin Ayub se wo Yazid bin abi Habib se wo Musa bin Saad se wo Yusuf bin Abdullah bin Salam se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain.
1079,Amr bin Shuaib apney walid ( Shuaib ( se aur wo apney dada Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne masjid mein kharid aur farokht se mana farmaya aur is se bhi ke gumshuda chiz ka us mein aelan kiya jaey ya she'r padhey jaeyn . aur is se bhi mana farmaya hai ke Jume ke roz Namaz se pehley halqa bana kar baitha jaey.
1080,"Janab Abu-Haazim bin Dinar bayan kartey hain ke kuch log Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye aur wo member nabawi ke baarey mein behes kar rahey they ke ye kis lakdi se bana tha? un logon ne un se uskey baarey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : qasam Allah ki ! main khoob janta hun ke wo kis chiz se bana tha aur maine usey pehley hi din jab wo rakha gaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us par baithey they, dekha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne falan aurat ke yahan paigham bheja . ... Sehal ne us aurat ka naam bhi zikr kiya. ... ke ''apney badhai ghulam se kaho ke mujhey kuch lakdiyan jod dey , jab main logon se khitab karun to us par baith jaya karun.'' chunanche usney apney ghulam se kaha to wo usey (طرفاء الغابة) (jangal ki eik lakdi, jhaoo) se bana kar ley aaya. us aurat ne isey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhej diya. aapney hukm diya to isey yahan rakh diya gaya. phir maine aap ko dekha ke aapney is par Namaz padhi. is par khadey ho kar takbire-tahreema kahi , phir rukoo kiya aur aap isi ke ooper they, phir aap pichley paon nichey utar aaye aur member ki jad mein nichey sajda kiya. phir aap member par chadh gaey . jab aap farigh huey to logon ki taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : ''logo ! maine ye is liye kiya hai taake tum meri iqtidaa karo aur meri Namaz seekh lo.''"
1081,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi qadr bhari ho gaey to Janab Tameem Daari (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya main aap ke liye member na bana laun , jo aap ki haddiyon ( wajood-at'har ( ko uthaya karey ? (yani aap us par tashrif farma hua keren ( aapney farmaya : '' haan  '' chunanche wo do sidhiyon wala member bana laye."
1082,Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke member aur) masjid ki) deewar ke darmiyan itna fasla tha ke us mein se bakri guzar jaey.
1083,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aap nisfun-nahaar (zawal) ke waqt Namaz padhna makruh samajhtey they, siwaye Jume ke din ke. aur aapney farmaya : '' be-shak (is waqt) jahannam bhadkai jati hai, siwaye Jume ke din ke. Imam Abu-Dawood farmatey hain ke ye riwayat mursal hai aur Mujahid , Abul-Khail se badey hain. aur Abul-Khail ne Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se nahin suna hai."
1084,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Suraj dhalney par Juma padha kartey they.
1085,"Ayaas bin Salma bin Akwa apney walid ( Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu)) se bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Juma padha kartey they, uskey baad jab wapis laut'tey to deewaron ka saya na hota tha."
1086,Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke ham log Jume ke baad hi khana khatey aur qailula kartey they.
1087,"Hazrat Saaib bin Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Jume ke roz ( Jume ki) pehli Azan Imam ke member par baithney ke waqt kahi jati thi. ehade nabuwat , khilaafate-Abi Bakr aur umr mein yehi mamool raha . jab Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilaafat aai aur log bhi bahut ho gaey to Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Jume ke roz teesri Azan ka hukm diya jo ke zauraa maqam par di jati thi aur mamla usi par qaaim raha."
1088,Hazrat Saaib bin Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Jume ke roz jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par baith jatey to aap ke samney masjid ke darwazey ke paas Azan kahi jati thi. aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke daur mein bhi aisey hi hota tha. aur) guzishta ( hadees Yunus ki manind bayan kiya.
1089,Hazrat Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka eik hi muazzan tha. yani Bilal aur) ibne Is'haq ne) sabiqa hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya.
1090,"Hazrat Saaib bin Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka eik hi muazzan tha. Saleh ne ye hadees bayan ki, magar kamil nahin hai."
1091,"Janab Ata bin abi Ribah , Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke) eik baar ( Jume ke roz jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( member par) barabar ( tashrif farma (ho gaey to farmaya : ''baith jao !'' usey Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne suna to masjid ke darwazey hi par basith gaey . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko dekha to farmaya : ''aey Abdullah bin Masood ! aagey aa jao. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is hadees ka mursal hona maroof hai. muhaddeseen ki eik jamaat isey Ata ( Taabai ( se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain. (yani darmiyan mein sahabi ka wasta tark kiya hua hai.) aur Mukhlid ''shaikh'' hai. (yani iski hadees likhi jati hai. ("
1092,"Naafe , Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do khutbey irshad farmaya kartey they. aap jab member par tashrif latey to baith jatey , yahan tak ke muazzan Azan se farigh ho jata . phir aap khadey hotey aur khutba detey , phir baith jatey aur kalam na kartey , phir khadey hotey aur (doosra) khutba detey. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do khutbey irshad farmaya kartey they. member par aaney ke baad baith jatey, yahan tak ke muazzan farigh ho jata. phir aap khadey hotey aur khutba detey. phir baith jatey aur kalam na kartey. phir khadey hotey aur khutba detey."
1093,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho kar khutba diya kartey they. (yani pehla khutba) phir baith jatey, phir (doosrey ke liye) khadey hotey aur khadey ho kar hi khutba detey aur jo shakhs tumhen ye bataey ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baith kar khutba detey they usney jhoot kaha. qasam Allah ki ! maine aap ke sath do hazar se ziyada namaazen padhi hain."
1094,Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke do khutbey hua kartey they. aap un dono ke darmiyan mein baitha kartey they. aap Quran padhtey aur logon ko waaz aur nasihat farmaya kartey they.
1095,Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke khadey ho kar khutba irshad farmatey phir mukhtasar sa baith jatey aur is dauran mein koi guftgu na kartey they aur hadees bayan ki .
1096,"Shuaib bin Razeeq Taaifi bayan kartey hain ke main eik sahab ke yahan baitha jinhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sohbat hasil thi. unhen Hakam bin Huzn Kulfi kaha jata tha. wo ham se bayan kerney lagey ke main eik wafad mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan hazir hua . main saat mein se saatwan ya nau mein se nawan fard tha. ham aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye to ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham aap ki ziyaarat ke liye aaye hain, hamarey liye duaaey khair farmaiye . aapney hamarey liye kisi qadr khajuron ka hukm diya, haalat un dino bahut kamzor thi. ham aap ke yahan kaee din muqeem rahey. hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Juma padhney ka mauqa bhi mila . aap eik lathi ya kamaan ka sahara liye huey khadey huey . aapney Allah ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki . aap ke alfaz mukhtasar , pakizah aur ba-barkat they. phir farmaya : ''logo ! jo ehkam tumhen diye jatey hain tum un sab ki taqat nahin rakhtey ho, ya unhen hergiz nahin kar saktey ho, lekin istiaqamat aur aetidaal ikhtiyar karo aur khush ho jao. ''Janab Abu-Ali (shagird Imam Abu-Dawud) kehtey hain ke maine Imam Abu-Dawud se suna, wo kehtey they ke is hadees ka kuch hissey mujhey merey sathiyon ne yaad karaya hai jo ke merey kaghaz se zaya ho gaya tha."
1097,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab (khutbey mein) tashahud padhtey , to kaha kartey :( الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ نَسْتَعِينُهُ وَنَسْتَغْفِرُهُ . ... الخ ) ''tamam tarah ki hamd aur sanaa Allah ke liye hai. ham us se madad chahtey aur maafi maangtey hain. apney nafson ki shararaton se Allah ki panah chahtey hain. jisey Allah hidayat dey usey koi gumrah nahin kar sakta aur jisey wo bhatka dey usey koi raahe-raast par nahin la sakta. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud bar-haq nahin hai. main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. Allah ne unko qiyamat se pehley haq ke sath , khushkhabri deney wala aur daraney wala bana kar bheja hai. jisney Allah aur uskey Rasool ki itaat ki wo hidayat pa gaya aur jisney in dono ki nafarmani ki wo apna hi nuqsan karta hai, Allah ka kuch nahin bigaadta.''"
1098,"Janab Yunus se riwayat hai ke unhoney ibne-Shahab se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke khutbey ke mutalliq puchha jo aap Jume ke roz padha kartey they. to usi (mazkura hadees) ki manind bayan kiya aur kaha :(مَنْ يُطِعِ اللَّهَ و َرَسُولَهُ وَمَنْ يَعْصِهِمَا) ''jisney in dono ki nafarmani ki wo bahut badey shar mein ja pada . ham apney Allah sey, jo hamara Rab hai, sawal kartey hain ke hamein un logon mein se banaey jo uski itaat kartey hain aur uskey Rasool ki, uski razamandi ke tabey hotey aur uski narazi se bachtey hain. bila-shuba ham usi ke sath hain aur usi ke liye hain.''"
1099,Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney eik khateeb ne khutba diya aur usney kaha : (مَنْ يُطِعِ اللَّهَ و َرَسُولَهُ وَمَنْ يَعْصِهِمَا) ''jisney Allah aur uskey Rasool ki itaat ki aur jisney un dono ki nafarmani ki.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khadey ho jao.''  ya farmaya : ''chaley jao tum bahut burey khateeb ho''
1100,Haris bin Nauman ki saahibzaadi bayan karti hain ke maine sura Qaaf Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke munh Mubarak se sun kar hi yaad ki hai. aap usey her Jume ke khutbe mein padha kartey they. bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka aur hamara tannur eik hi tha. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Rooh bin Ubada ne Shoba se riwayat kartey huey us khatoon ka nasab yun zikr kiya : '' binte Harisa bin Nauman'' jabkey ibne-Is'haq ne ''Umme-Hisham binte Harisa bin Nauman'' kaha .
1101,Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz aur aap ka khutba darmiyane hotey they. aap Quran karim ki chand aayaat tilawat farmatey aur logon ko waaz aur nasihat farmaya kartey they.
1102,"Umra apni behan se riwayat karti hain. uska bayan hai ke maine sura Qaaf Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke munh mubarak hi se ( sun kar) yaad ki hai. aap usey her Juma (ke khutbe mein) padha kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Yahya bin Ayub aur ibne-Abi-Rijaal ne Yahya bin Saeed sey, unhoney Umra sey, unhoney Umme- Hisham binte Harisa bin Nauman se aisey hi riwayat kiya hai."
1103,"Yahya bin Saeed , Umra sey, wo Umra binte  Abdur-Rehman ki behan sey, jo un se badi thin . uskey ham-maani riwayat hai,"
1104,Janab Husain bin Abdur-Rehman bayan kartey hain ke Umara bin Rubiya ne Bishr bin Marwan ko dekha ke wo Jume ke roz ( asnaaey (beech) khutbe mein haath utha kar) dua kar raha tha. ( haath hila raha tha ( to Umara ne kaha : Allah in dono haathon ko ruswa karey. ... zaayda kehtey hain ke Husain ne kaha : mujhey Umara ne bayan kiya. ... tehqiq maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha hai ke aap us se ziyada nahin kartey they. yani sirf shahadat ki ungli (uthaney ko kafi samjha kartey they ( jo angoothey se mili hoti hai.
1105,Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kabhi nahin dekha ke aapney member par ya uskey alawa dua kartey huey apney dono haath uthaey hon. maine aap ko dekha hai ke aap yun kartey they aur ishara karkey dikhaya ke aap angusht shahadat uthatey aur darmiyani ungli aur angoothe ka halqa bana letey.
1106,Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ham ko khutbey mukhtasar rakhney ka hukm diya.
1107,Hazrat Jabir bin Samura Suwaai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jume ke roz lambi waaz na farmaya kartey they balke chand mukhtasar se kalimaat hua kartey they.
1108,Janab Muaz bin Hisham kehtey hain ke maine apney walid ki bayaaz mein unke haath ka likha hua paya aur suna nahin. ke Qatada ne kaha Yahya bin Malik se wo Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zikr ( khutba aur waaz ( mein hazir hua karo aur Imam ke qarib baitha karo . insan ( agar khair ke maqamat sey) peechhey rehney ko mamool bana ley to jannat mein bhi peechhey kar diya jaeyga agar-che us mein dakhil ho hi jaey.''
1109,"Janab Abdullah bin Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein khutba dey rahey they ke (is beech mein) Hazrat Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) surkh qameesen pehney huey aaye . wo girtey they aur uthtey they. to aap member se utar padey , unko pakda aur un dono ko lekar member par tashrif laye, phir farmaya : ''sach farmaya Shan wale Allah ne : ( { إِنَّمَا أَمْوَالُكُمْ وَ أَوْلَادُكُمْ فِتْنَةٌ } ) ''bila-shuba tumharey amwaal (maal) aur tumhari aulad aazmaish hain.'' maine in dono ko dekha to sabr na kar saka. uskey baad aapney phir khutba dena shuru kar diya."
1110,Sehal bin Muaz bin Anas apney walid se raawi hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Jume ke roz jab Imam khutba dey raha ho حبوة (baithney ki eik soorat ( se mana farmaya hai.
1111,"Janab Y'alaa bin Shaddad bin Aus kehtey hain ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath baitul-Maqdis mein hazir tha. unhoney hamein Juma padhaya. maine dekha ke masjid mein haazirin ki aksariyat as-haabe Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki thi. maine unhen dekha ke Imam khutba dey raha tha aur wo ''ihtiba'a'' ki haalat mein baithey huey they. Imam Abu-Dawood farmatey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) asnaaey (beech) khutbe mein ''ihtiba'a'' ki haalat mein baitha kartey they. Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) aur Shureh , Sa'sa' bin Suhaan , Saeed bin Musaiyab , Ibrahim Nakhai , Makhool , Ismail bin Muhammad bin Saad aur Naeem bin Sulama ka kehna hai ke is mein koi harj nahin. Imam Abu-Dawood kehtey hain ke Janab Ubaada bin Nasee (Rahimahullah) ( Taabai (ke alawa mujhey kisi ke mutalliq maloom nahin hua ke unhoney is tarah baithney ko makruh kaha ho."
1112,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum ye kaho ke khamosh ho jao aur Imam khutba dey raha ho to tum ne laghu (fuzul aur bekar) kaam kiya. ''
1113,"Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : '' Jume mein teen tarah ke afrad aatey hain. eik wo shakhs jo laghu (fuzul aur bekar) kaam karta hai uska yehi hissey hai. doosra dua ke liye aata hai, ye dua karta hai Allah chahey to ata farmaai aur chahey to mehroom rakhey . aur teesra wo shakhs jo khamoshi se sunta aur sukoot ikhtiyar karta hai. kisi musalman ki gardan phalaangtaa hai na kisi ko eza (takleef) deta hai. is aadmi ke liye ye Juma aainda Jume tak ke liye aur mazeed teen din ke liye kaffara hai. aur ye is liye ke Shan wale Allah ne farmaya : ( { مَنْ جَاءَ بِالْحَسَنَةِ فَلَهُ عَشْرُ أَمْثَالِهَا } ) ''jo eik neki lata hai uskey liye uska das guna (ajr) hai.''"
1114,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jab koi apni Namaz mein be-wuzu ho jaey, to chahiye ke apni naak par haath rakhey aur chala jaey. Imam Abu-Dawood farmatey hain ke is riwayat ko Hammad bin Salma aur Abu-Usama ne an Hisham an Abih aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sanad se riwayat kiya hai. is mein hai ke ''jab koi aaye aur Imam khutba dey raha ho.'' unhoney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke wasta zikr nahin kiya."
1115,Saiyedna Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Jume ke din eik shakhs aaya aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba dey rahey they. aapney us se farmaya : ''aey falan ! kya tum ne Namaz padhi hai? usney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : '' khadey ho jao aur Namaz padho.''
1116,"Janab Aamash, Abu-Sufiyaan sey, wo Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey, isliye Aamash , Abu-Saaleh sey, wo Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se dono ka bayan hai ke Sulaik Ghatfaani  (Raziallahu anhu) aaye jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba dey rahey they, aapney un se kaha : ''kya tum ne koi Namaz padhi hai? '' unhoney kaha : nahin : aapney farmaya : ''mukhtasar si do rakatein padh lo.''"
1117,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kar rahey they ke Janab Sulaik aaye . aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind zikr kiya. mazeed ye kaha ke phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) logon ki taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi aaye aur Imam khutba dey raha ho to usey chahiye ke mukhtasar si do rakatein padhey.
1118,"Abul-Zahiriya bayan kartey hain ke eik ( baar ( Jume ke din ham Hazrat Abdullah bin Basar (Raziallahu anhu) Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sahabi sath they. eik shakhs logon ki gardanen phalaangtaa hua aaya, to Hazrat Abdullah ne bayan kiya ke Jume ke roz eik aad kaee logon ki gardanen phalaangtaa hua aaya jabke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba dey rahey they, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se kaha : ''baith jao tum ne aziyat di.''"
1119,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''jab kisi ko ungh aaney lagey aur wo masjid mein ho to chahiye ke apni jagah badal kar kisi aur jagah baith jaey.''"
1120,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member se utartey aur koi shakhs apni zarurat se aap ke paas aa jata to aap uskey sath khadey ho jatey, yahan tak ke wo apni zarurat puri kar leta , phir aap ( musalley par) khadey hotey aur Namaz padhatey. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke Sabit se ye hadees maroof nahin hai. Jarir bin Hazim is bayan mein munfarid (bilkul alag) hai."
1121,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney Namaz se eik rakat pa li usney Namaz pa li.''
1122,Hazrat Nauman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidain aur Jume ki Namaz mein surat (سبح اسم ربك الأعلى) aur) هل أتاك حديث الغاشية ( tilawat farmaya kartey they. bayan kiya ke kabhi-kabhi eid aur Juma ikhattey ho jatey to bhi yehi suraten padhtey.
1123,Janab Zuhaak bin Qais ne Hazrat Nauman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jume ke roz sura Juma ki tilawat ke baad kon si surat padha kartey they. kaha ke) هل أتاك حديث الغاشية ( (yani dusri rakaat mein) padhtey they.
1124,ibne-Abi Raafe bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat  Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Juma padhaya to unhoney Sura-Juma aur dusri rakaat mein) إذا جاءك المنافقون ( ki tilawat ki . ibne-Abi Raafe kehtey hain ke Namaz ke baad main Hazrat Abu-Huraira se mila aur kaha ke aapney jo suraten tilawat ki hain Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bhi koofa mein yehi padha kartey they. to Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna hai ke aap bhi Jume ke roz ( Namaze Juma mein) ye suraten padha kartey they.
1125,Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaze Juma mein (سبح اسم ربك الأعلى) aur) هل أتاك حديث الغاشية ( padha kartey they.
1126,Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney hujre (aetikaf) mein Namaz padhi aur log hujre se bahir aap ki iqtidaa kar rahey they.
1127,"Janab Naafe (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne eik shakhs ko dekha ke Jume ke roz (Jume ke baad) usi jagah do rakatein padh raha tha, to aapney usey hata diya aur kaha : kya to Jume ki chaar rakatein padhta hai? Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) Jume ke roz ( Jume ke baad) apney ghar mein do rakatein padha kartey they aur farmatey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisey hi kiya hai."
1128,Janab Naafe ka bayan hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) Jume se pehley lambi Namaz padha kartey they aur Jume ke baad ghar ja kar do rakatein padhtey aur bayan kartey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) yehi kiya kartey they.
1129,"Janab umr bin Ata bin Abi khawaar se riwayat hai ke Janab Naafe bin Jubair ne unko Namir ke bhaanjey Janab Saaib bin Yazid ke paas bheja , ye poochhney ke liye ke wo kya baat thi jo Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se Namaz mein dekhi thi. to unhoney kaha : maine Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath mein unke maqsoora mein Jume ki Namaz padhi , salam ke baad main apni jagah par khada ho gaya aur Namaz padhi. jab wo apni manzil mein aaye to mujhey bulwaya aur kaha : jo kuch tum ne kiya hai aisey phir mat karna , jab tum Juma padho to usey Namaz ke sath mat milaao , yahan tak ke baat kar lo ya wahan se chaley jao. bila-shuba Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne iska hukm diya hai ke eik Namaz ko dusri Namaz ke sath na milaayaa jaey, yahan tak ke tum koi baat kar lo ya wahan se nikal jao."
1130,"Janab Ata Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se raawi hain ke wo jab makkey mein hotey , aur Juma padhtey to aagey badh kar do rakatein padhtey , phir aagey badhtey aur chaar rakatein padhtey aur jab Madiney mein hotey aur Juma padhtey to uskey baad ghar lot jatey aur do rakatein ada kartey aur masjid mein na padhtey. aap se uskey mutalliq puchha gaya to kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisey hi kiya kartey they."
1131,"Suhail apney walid Abu-Saaleh sey, wo Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain. unhoney kaha (ibne Sabaah ke alfaz hain) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Jumey ke baad Namaz padhna chahey to chaar rakaat padhey.'' aur ibne Sabaah ki hadees mukammal hui.  Ahmed bin Yunus ki hadees ke alfaz hain :) ''jab tum Juma padh lo to uskey baad chaar rakatein padho.'' merey walid (Abu-Saaleh) ne mujh se kaha : bete ! agar masjid mein padho to do rakaat padho, phir jab ghar aao to do rakatein aur padho."
1132,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jume ke baad apney ghar mein do rakatein padha kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Abdullah bin Dinar ne bhi Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se aisey hi riwayat kiya hai.
1133,"Ata (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke unhoney Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko dekha ke wo Jume ke baad Namaz padhtey to apni us jagah sey, jahan unhoney Juma padha hota kuch hatt jatey aur do rakatein padhtey aur phir us se thoda sa aur hatt jatey aur chaar rak'aat padhtey. maine Ata se puchha : aapney Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko aisa kartey huey kitni baar dekha hai? unhoney kaha : kaee baar. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain is riwayat ko Abdul-Malik bin Abi Sulaiman ne bhi riwayat kiya hai magar mukammal bayan nahin kiya."
1134,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina mein tashrif laye aur un logon ke yahan do din they ke wo un mein khel-kood kiya kartey they. aapney puchha : ''ye do din kya hain? ''unhoney kaha ke ham daure-jahiliyat mein un dino mein khel kood kiya kartey they. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah taala ne tumhen unke badley un se achchhey din diye hain. Azhaa (qurbani) ka din aur Fitr ka din.''
1135,"Janab Yazid bin khumair Rahabi bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Basar (Raziallahu anhu) sahibe-Rasool logon ke sath eid-ul-fitr ya eid-ul-azhaa ke liye tashrif laye to Imam ke takheer kar deney ko unhoney napasand kiya aur kaha : ham to us waqt farigh ho chukey hotey they, yani ishraaq ke waqt."
1136,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Sirin, Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya ke pardey mein baithi hui aurton ko bhi eid ke din sath ley jaeyn . puchha gaya jo dinon mein hon? aapney farmaya : ''wo bhi khair aur musalmanon ki dua mein shareek hon.'' eik aurat kehney lagi : aey Allah ke Rasool ! agar kisi ke paas ( pardey ke liye ( chadar na ho to wo kaisey karey? aapney farmaya : ''uski sahaili usey apni chadar ka eik hissey odhaa dey.''"
1137,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) ne yehi hadees bayan ki) Muhammad bin Sirin ne ( kaha aur dinon wali khawatin Namaz ke maqam se alag rahen . aur kapdey ka zikr nahin kiya. aur) Hammad ne ba-waasta Ayub ( Hafsa binte Sirin sey, unhoney eik khatoon sey, unhoney eik dusri khatoon se riwayat kiya, kaha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aur kapdey ke baarey mein Musa-bin-Ismail ki riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kiya."
1138,Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke hamein hukm diya jata tha. aur ye hadees bayan ki . aur kaha ke haiz waliyan logon ke peechhey hon aur logon ke sath takbeeren kahen .
1139,"Ismail bin Abdur-Rehman bin Atiya apni daadi Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Madiney mein tashrif laye to ansaar ki khawatin ko eik ghar mein jama kiya aur Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko hamari taraf bheja . wo darwazey par khadey huey, ham ko salam kiya, ham ne salam ka jawab diya, phir unhoney kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka firistaada (bheja hua) hun. aapney mujhey tumhari taraf bheja hai. aapney hamein ( aurton ko) Eidon ke baarey mein hukm diya ke dinon waaliyon aur naukhez (nai-naweli) ladkiyon ko bhi eid gaah ley ke chalen. Juma ham par nahin hai aur janaazon mein janey se hamein mana farmaya."
1140,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Marwan ne eid ke roz member nikalwaayaa aur Namaz se pehley khutba dena shuru kiya. eik shakhs khada hua aur usney kaha : aey Marwan ! tum ne sunnat ki mukhalifat ki hai. eid ke roz member nikalwaayaa hai jabke is din ye na nikala jata tha aur Namaz se pehley khutbey se ibtida (shuruat) ki hai. Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha : ye kon hai? logon ne kaha : ye falan bin falan hai. unhoney kaha : usney apna fariza ada kar diya. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna hai aap farma rahey they : ''(tum mein sey) jo koi burai dekhey aur usey apney haath se door kar sakta ho to haath se door karey. agar uski istataat (taqat) na ho to zaban se ye kaam karey, agar uski bhi istataat na ho to dil se bura janey. aur ye kamzor tareen Imaan hai.''"
1141,"Janab Ata , Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se raawi hain ke maine unko suna bayan kartey they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidul-fitr ke roz khadey huey aur Namaz padhaai . aapney khutbey se pehley Namaz se ibtida (shuruat) farmae phir logon ko khutba diya. jab Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farigh huey to utrey aur aurton ke paas aaye aur unhen waaz aur nasihat farmaee , aap Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke haath ka sahara liye huey they aur Bilal apna kapda phailaey huey they. aurten us mein apney sadqaat daalti jati thin. koi apni anguthi daalti thi , koi kuch aur koi kuch. ibne Bakr ne ( فتخها ( ki bajaey ( ) فتختها (ka lafz istimal kiya. (yani anguthi)"
1142,"Janab Ata se riwayat hai wo kehtey hain : main Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) par shahadat deta hun aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par shahadat di ke aap eidul-fitr ke din nikley , Namaz padhaai , phir khutba diya, uskey baad aurton ke paas aaye aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke sath they. ibne Kaseer ne kaha : Shoba ka ghalib guman hai ke (Ayub ne ye jumla bhi kaha tha ke) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un khawatin ko sadqa kerney ka hukm diya to wo (apney sadqaat Bilal ke kapdey mein) dalney lagin ."
1143,"Ayub ne Ata se unhoney Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya. ibne-Abbas kehtey hain ke aap ko khayal hua ke aurton ne (aap ka khutba ( nahin suna hai to aap unki taraf chaley aur Bilal aap ke sath they. aapney unhen waaz farmaya aur sadqa kerney ka hukm diya, to koi Bilal ke kapdey main apni baali dal rahi thi to koi apni anguthi."
1144,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne is hadees mein bayan kiya ke koi aurat apni baali deney lagi aur koi apni anguthi aur Bilal unhen apney kapdey mein jama kartey jatey they. phir aapney us maal ko faqeer musalmanon mein taqseem kar diya.
1145,Janab Yazid bin Bara apney walid se raawi hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eid ke roz kamaan di gaee to aapney uskey saharey khutba diya.
1146,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin Aabis kehtey hain ke eik shakhs ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se puchha : kya aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eid mein hazir rahey hain? unhoney kaha : haan agar mujhey aap ke sath talluq aur martaba hasil na hota to bachpane ke baais main aap ke qarib na ho sakta tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us nishan ke paas aaye jo Kaseer bin Salat ke ghar ke paas hai, aapney Namaz padhaai , phir khutba diya aur) Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne ( kisi Azan aur iqaamat ka zikr nahin kiya. phir aapney sadqa kerney ka hukm diya to aurten apney kanon aur apni gardanon ki taraf ishara karney lagin. bayan kiya ke aapney Bilal ko hukm diya to wo un ( aurton (ke paas gaey aur phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas laut aaye."
1147,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) raawi hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eid ( ki Namaz ( Azan aur iqaamat ke baghair padhaai. aur) aisey hi ( Abu-Bakar aur umr ya Usman ne bhi . Yahya ko shak hua hai.
1148,Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine eik do baar nahin balke kaee baar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eidain ki Namaz padhi hai. Azan aur iqaamat ke baghair.
1149,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidul fitr aur eidul azhaa mein pehli rakaat mein saat aur dusri mein paanch takbeeren kaha kartey they.
1150,"Janab Khalid bin Yazid ne , ibne-Shahab se mazkura sanad ke sath aur uskey ham-maani bayan kiya, mazeed kaha ke rukoo ki takbir ke alawa."
1151,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Namaze eidul-fitr mein takbeeren pehli rakaat mein saat hain aur dusri mein paanch aur qirat un dono ke baad hai.''
1152,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid ( Shuaib ( se aur wo apney dada ( Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas ( se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidul-fitr ki Namaz mein pehli rakaat mein saat takbeeren kehtey, phir qirat kartey , phir takbir kehtey ( rukoo ke liye ( , phir (dusri rakaat mein) khadey hotey aur chaar takbeeren kehtey, phir qirat kartey phir ( iskey baad) rukoo kartey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Wakee aur ibne Mubarak ne ye hadees riwayat ki to un dono ne saat aur paanch takbeeren bayan ki hain."
1153,Janab Saeed bin al-Aas ne Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari aur Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu Anhuma) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaze eidul-azhaa aur fitr mein takbeeren kaisey kaha kartey they? to Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap chaar takbeerein kaha kartey they jaisey ke janaazey mein hoti hain. Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : unhoney sach kaha hai. Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : main jab Basra mein logon par ameer tha to aisey hi takbeeren kaha karta tha. aur Abu-Aaysha ne kaha ke main Saeed bin Al-Aas ke paas hazir tha.
1154,Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Abu Waqid Laisi (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidul-azhaa aur eidul-fitr mein kya qirat kiya kartey they? kaha ke (ق والقرآن المجيد) aur (اقتربت الساعة وانشق القمر (
1155,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke main Rasulullah ke yahan eid mein hazir tha. aap jab Namaz se farigh huey to farmaya : ''ham khutba detey hain to jo pasand karey baith jaey, aur jo jana chahey chala jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke ye hadees (marfoo sahih nahin, balke) mursal hai aur Ata ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kiya hai."
1156,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul (naqal ki) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eid ko janey ke liye eik raasta ikhtiyar farmaya aur wapsi mein doosrey raastey se tashrif laye.
1157,"Janab Abu-Umair bin Anas apney chachon sey, jo ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba they, bayan kartey hain ke eik qafley waley Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur unhoney shahadat di ke ham ne kal shaam ko chaand dekha hai. to aapney logon ko hukm diya ke roza iftaar kar lein aur agley din subah ko eid gaah mein pahunchen ."
1158,"Hazrat Bakr bin Mubashshir Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main as-haabe-Rasul ke sath mein eidul-fitr aur eidul-azhaa ke roz eid gaah ko jaya karta tha. ham log wadi Bat'haan ke batan (pet) se guzartey they, yahan tak ke eid gaah mein pahunch jatey , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhtey phir usi wadi Bat'haan ke batan se guzar kar wapis apney gharon ko lot aaya kartey they."
1159,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidul-fitr ke roz nikley ( eid ki) do rakatein padhin. is se pehley ya iskey baad koi Namaz na padhi. phir aurton ki taraf aaye , aap ke sath Bilal they. aapney un (aurton) ko sadqa kerney ka hukm diya to koi apni baali utaar rahi thi aur koi apna haar."
1160,"Waleed bin Muslim kehtey hain ke hamein farwiyon mein se eik aadmi ne bayan kiya. . . . . . Rabeea ne uska naam Esa bin Abdul-A'alaa bin Abi Farwa liya hai. ... ke unhoney Abu-Yahya, Ubaidullah, Taimi ko suna, wo Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey they ke (eik dafa) eid ke roz barish ho gaee , to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen masjid hi mein Namaze-eid padhaai."
